h cac san pham duong da, nuoc hoa va my pham chat \nluong cao. \ntro thanh mot tu van \nvien cua oriflame dong nghia voi mot nguon thu nhap khong gioi han, nhung co hoi \nde tao dung su nghiep, phat trien ban than va cam giac minh thuoc ve mot cong \ndong than thien tren toan cau. \noriflame la mot cong \nty voi mot tinh than tich cuc, bo may quan ly phi tap trung va mot bau khong khi \ntre trung, nang dong. \ntuy da phat trien rat \nnhanh chong nhung cong ty chua bao gio danh mat khai niem kinh doanh nguyen thuy \ncua minh  my pham thien nhien tu thuy dien tu ban be toi ban be. \n\n@mot vai so lieu thong \nke ve oriflame \n\ndoanh so: hon \n1.1 ty euro/nam \nso luong tu van \nvien: 3 trieu \nso luong nhan \nvien: 6,200 nhan vien \nchung loai san \npham: tren 880 san pham \nso luong \ncatalogue: tren 100 trieu voi 35 ngon ngu (2006) \n@mot so thong tin thu \nvi ve oriflame \n\nmy pham oriflame \nla mot trong nhung thanh vien cua hiep hoi ban hang truc tiep the gioi (wfdsa). \nwfdsa, duoc thanh lap nam 1978, la to chuc phi chinh phu, mang tinh toan cau dai \ndien cho nganh cong nghiep ban hang truc tiep nham lien ket cac hiep hoi ban \nhang truc tiep tai cac quoc gia. \noriflame la dong \nsang lap quy nhi dong the gioi (world childhood foundation). \n\n@qua trinh hinh thanh \nva phat trien cua oriflame \n\n1967 thanh lap tai thuy dien \n\n1968 tham nhap 2 thi truong nuoc ngoai dau \ntien: dan mach va na uy. \n1986 indonesia tro thanh thi truong dau \ntien tai chau a. \n1989 chile tro thanh thi truong dau tien \ntai chau my la tinh. \n1990 sau khi buc tuong berlin sup do, \noriflame tai cong hoa sec bat dau mo rong hoat dong den vung trung au va dong \nau, tiep theo do la cac nuoc thuoc cong dong cac quoc gia doc lap (cis) va cac \nnuoc vung bantic. \n1997 ai cap tro thanh thi truong dau tien \ntai chau phi. \n2000 thanh lap trung tam ky thuat toan cau \ndanh cho cong tac nghien cuu va phat trien san pham.&nbsp;&nbsp; \n2001 oriflame dat con so 1,4 trieu tu van \nvien, hien dien tai tren 55 thi truong khap the gioi va co doanh thu thuan gan \n450 trieu euro. \n2003 khai truong tai viet nam \n\n2004 niem yet co phieu tren thi truong \nchung khoan stockholm, thuy dien. \n2006 oriflame la cong ty my pham nuoc \nngoai thu 3 duoc cap phep ban hang truc tiep tai tq. \n\n&nbsp;\nsan \npham cua oriflame - my pham thien nhien tu thuy dien\noriflame \ntin tuong rang sac dep tu nhien la dieu mong muon cua moi nguoi. ngay tu khi bat \ndau, oriflame da hieu rang tu nhien se tot hon nhung gi nhan tao. voi mong muon \nhoan thien sac dep cua phu nu thuy dien va nhan manh vao nguyen lieu va cong \nthuc thien nhien, my pham oriflame that su duoc xem mot trong nhung san pham tu \nnhien trong suot bon thap ky qua.\nnghi \nve thuy dien ban khong the khong nghi den thien nhien. voi nhung khu rung nguyen \nthuy rong lon va nhung vung dat trai rong, nhung nguon nuoc tinh khiet va bau \ntroi trong xanh. thuy dien la quoc gia khong bi o nhiem. su khac biet thoi tiet \nmanh me da lam giau chat luong cua cay co va thuc vat. dieu nay se giup ich rat \nnhieu cho suc khoe va sac dep. de ton tai trong man dem va mua dong khac nghiet, \ncac loai thuc vat deu phai thau nap cho minh nhieu khoang chat va acid. se khong \nlay lam la rang, rat nhieu thanh phan cua chung duoc lay tu trong dat thuy dien. \nvai san pham duong da dau tien da duoc lam tu thao moc nhu go birch va \ncloudberry tim thay tu tham thuc vat giau co o day.\nthien \nnhien la nguon cam hung tuyet voi va oriflame tu sau tham co su kinh trong no. \ndo la ly do tai sao tat ca cac nguyen lieu tu nhien ma oriflame dung deu co \nnguon goc co the phuc hoi duoc, va dieu do chi ra cho ban thay oriflame tiep can \nmoi truong mot cach than thien.\ndi \nsan cua thuy dien con la su ngau hung sang tao duoc the hien thong qua cach \nthiet ke san pham va bao bi cua oriflame.\nkhong \nqua kieu cach, khong qua phuc tap, tiep can tu nhien mot cach than thien do \nchinh la dau an cua tat ca san pham oriflame.\n&nbsp;\ncong ty oriflame - \nnguyen tac dao duc va tieu chi kinh doanh \n\nnguyen tac dao \nduc\n\"hoat \ndong mot cach trung thuc, hop dao duc va ro rang.\"\ncong ty my \npham oriflame co nhung quy tac dao duc dac trung va vung chac, duoc chung minh \ntrong moi khia canh cua hoat dong va duoc the hien bang nhung cach duoi \nday:\nsan xuat duoc \ntheo doi va quan ly theo cac tieu chuan cua quy dinh ve san xuat my pham \n(cosmetic good manufacturing practices-cgmp) va quy dinh ve nha cung cap cac san \npham my pham cua oriflame, de dam bao chat luong cao cho san pham. \n\ncong ty my pham \noriflame co mot moi quan he coi mo va chan that doi voi tat ca cac nha cung cap \nde dam bao giu bi mat cho nhung ky thuat va cong thuc chuyen nghiep cua ho. \n\ncong ty my pham \noriflame co cam ket rang moi hoat dong cua cong ty deu duoc tien hanh voi tieu \nchi ton trong moi truong. tat ca cac nha cung cap deu duoc mong doi co trach \nnhiem trong viec bao ve va gin giu moi truong va thuc hien nhung bien phap quan \nly moi truong triet de cung nhu tuan thu cac quy dinh cua quoc gia va dia \nphuong. \ncong ty my pham \noriflame cung coi trong cac yeu to dao duc va ton giao cua nhan dan cac quoc gia \nnoi cong ty hoat dong. \ncong ty my pham \noriflame luon bao dam rang nhung tieu chuan cua quoc gia va dia phuong ve suc \nkhoe va an toan noi lam viec, muc luong toi thieu va gio lam viec, duoc tuan \nthu. ngoai ra, cong ty cung trong doi cac nha cung cap hoat dong mot cach hop \ndao duc trong cac van de ve nhung nguoi nho tuoi va de bi ton thuong trong luc \nluong lao dong cua minh. cac phuc loi cho tre em luon luon la mot moi quan tam \nchinh yeu cua cong ty - mot thanh vien sang lap cua to chuc nhi dong the gioi. \n\ncong ty my pham \noriflame khong thu nghiem nhung san pham hoac cac thanh phan cua san pham, tren \ndong vat. san pham cua cong ty khong co thanh phan nao duoc chiet xuat tu dong \nvat chet hoac duoc khai thac theo nhung phuong cach gay hai cho dong vat. \n\ncac kiem tra ve \ndo an toan va tinh hieu qua duoc thuc hien, duoi su giam sat boi cac chuyen vien \ny te co chuyen mon, tren nhung nguoi tinh nguyen khoe manh (tren 18 \ntuoi)nhung quy dinh quoc te va dia phuong luon duoc theo doi de dam bao rang \nnguoi tieu dung cua chung toi duoc cung cap boi cac san pham an toan, co hieu \nqua va hop phap. \ntieu \nchi kinh doanh cua oriflame\n\"duoc \ntro thanh chon lua tu nhien hang dau cua khach hang, tu van vien va nhan vien \ncua chung toi.\"\nnhiem \nvu cua chung toi\nmang co \nhoi den cho tat ca moi nguoi.\nban \nhang truc tiep voi oriflame\nban hang truc \ntiep la mot trong nhung phuong phap ban hang phat trien nhanh nhat tren the \ngioi. gio day, hang trieu nguoi thuoc moi quoc gia dang duoc huong nhung loi ich \ntu phuong thuc nay so voi cach ban hang truyen thong thong qua cac cua hang ban \nle. ngay tu nhung ngay dau, oriflame da chon phuong thuc ban hang nay vi no mang \nlai nhieu thuan loi cho ca khach hang lan nhung nguoi tim kiem co hoi tang thu \nnhap.\nnhung \nthuan loi cua khach hang\nduoc tu van mien \nphi ve cac san pham phu hop \ntiet kiem thoi \ngian va thuan tien vi hang duoc giao truc tiep den nha \noriflame dam bao \n100% chat luong san pham. \nnhung \nthuan loi cua tu van vien\nco hoi tang thu \nnhap dang ke \nduoc chu dong \nchon thoi gian va khoi luong cong viec. \nkhoi nghiep ma \nkhong can von dau tu. \ngap go nhieu \nnguoi. \nco hoi phat \ntrien ban than. \nban co the tu \ntin khi ban hang vi oriflame ho tro ban dam bao 100% chat luong san pham trong \nqua trinh ban hang. trong truong hop gap di ung, khach hang cua ban co the tra \nhang lai va ban co the de nghi khach hang lua chon san pham thay the hoac tra \nlai tien. ban se lien he voi oriflame ngay lap tuc va dien vao mau khieu nai san \npham de nhan duoc san pham thay the hoac duoc tra lai tien trong vong 14 ngay ke \ntu ngay mua hang.\n&nbsp;\nour \ncore values - 3 gia tri cot loi cua oriflame \n\nday la 3 gia tri cot loi cua oriflame ton tai tu ngay thanh \nlap cho den tan bay gio. khi moi gia nhap oriflame minh cung duoc nghe noi voi \n\"3 core values\" nay nhung khong co an tuong gi dong lai nhieu. the nhung qua \nhoat dong thuc tien o cong ty dan dan minh hieu ra the nao la su doan ket \n(togetherness) o oriflame, the nao la tinh than (spirit) cua cac tu van vien \noriflame va cung nhu the nao la su nhiet huyet (passion) trong cong viec cua cac \ntu van vien oriflame.tu do minh rat thich 3 gia tri nay cua cong ty. de thanh \ncong va ngay cang thanh cong hon, hoan thien ban than va vuon toi su doc lap tai \nchinh trong qua cong viec o oriflame, minh khong the khong co 3 yeu to do. va \nnoi rong ra, du lam bat ky linh vuc gi, anh tho ho, anh tho moc, nguoi buon ban \nnho, hay la mot ky su phan mem, kien truc su, ... ai cung deu can cac yeu to nay \nde vuon len dinh cao nghe nghiep cua minh.doan ketdoan ket giup ban lam viec thong minh hon, tiet kiem duoc \nnhieu thoi gian va cong suc vi co the tan dung kinh nghiem, kien thuc cua nhieu \nnguoi. nguoi ta hay goi do la \"nhieu nguoi mat sang hon 1 nguoi\". lam viec \n\"teamwork\" thi cac diem manh diem yeu cua tung nguoi se duoc san lap cho nhau de \ntao thanh mot tap the vung chac, lao len phia truoc de cung nhau thanh cong. \ntinh thantinh than giup nguoi ta vuot qua su nan long, kien tri con \nduong da di. khong bao gio tu bo muc tieu da dat ra. tinh than giup ban tiep tuc \ndi du con duong phia truoc dau chong gai vi ban biet rang di qua khoi doan duong \nnay se la suoi mat, la bau troi bao la voi khong khi trong lanh, gio \nmat.nhiet huyetnhiet huyet giup nguoi ta chien dau voi hon 100% suc luc ma \nnguoi ta co. nguoi co nhiet huyet luon noi ve muc tieu ho dang phan dau, noi ve \ncong viec ho dang lam va ket qua mong doi cua ho. nhiet huyet can cho moi linh \nvuc. co nhiet huyet nguoi ta moi lam nen su khac biet. \n\n\n&nbsp;\ncac \ncau hoi thuong gap ve oriflame - oriflame faqs \n\noriflame duoc thanh \nlap khi nao?oriflame duoc \nthanh lap vao nam 1967. xem them lich su cong \ntytai sao lai \nco ten oriflame?nguon goc cua ten cong ty bat nguon tu lich su cua \nnuoc phap. la mot bieu tuong cua chien thang, oriflame la mot ngon co mau do \ntham ma nha vua phap duoc trao truoc khi bat dau cuoc chinh chien. nhung nguoi \nsang lap cua cong ty da y thuc rang viec gioi thieu mot phuong thuc kinh doanh \nmoi theo kieu truc tiep va xay dung cong ty dua tren phuong thuc nay se thuc su \nla mot cuoc dau tranh. ho cam thay rang cai ten oriflame se that thich hop cho \ncuoc chien dau sap toi. bieu tuong dau tien cua cong ty mang mot ve hoang gia \nvoi mot vong hoa hoang gia quanh chu o.oriflame co mat tai nhung quoc \ngia nao tren toan cau?tinh den thang 04/2008, oriflame hien dien tai 59 \nquoc gia tren toan cau va la mot trong nhung cong ty dan dau thi truong o hon 30 \nnuoc.co bao nhieu tu van vien dang lam viec cho \noriflame?oriflame co gan 2,3 trieu tu van vien doc lap tren toan cau, \nhon 6.200 nhan vien chinh thuc.toi phai dong phi gia nhap bao \nnhieu?ban khong phai dong phi gia nhap nao ca. tuy nhien, ban can dong \n79.000d de nhan bo tai lieu khoi dong.bo tai lieu khoi dong gom nhung \ngi?thu chao mung cua tong giam doc, catalogue san \npham moi nhat, sach huong dan cham soc da, quyen don dat hang cho khach, so tay, \nquyen thong tin ve co hoi oriflame, to roi ve chuong trinh chao don nguoi moi \ngia nhap, cam nang tu van vien va ban tin noi bo moi \nnhat...catalogue gia bao nhieu va lam the nao de dat mua \ncatalogue?gia ban le moi catalogue la 7.000d. ban co the dat mua si \ncatalogue theo gia ban chi tiet nhu sau:5 cuon - 29.000d20 cuon - \n89.000d50 cuon - 198.000dmua tai quay tiep tan hoac dat trong don \nhang.toi co can phai dat hang moi ky catalogue khong?khong. \nban chi dat hang cong ty khi co khach hang dat hang ban.cong ty co \nquy dinh don hang toi thieu khong?co. don hang toi thieu la 400.000d. \nneu duoi 400.000d, phai dong phi dich vu 15.000d.toi kiem tien bang \ncach nao?&gt;&gt; xem cach kiem tien voi \noriflametoi co the gia \nnhap oriflame khong khi toi chi mua hang cho ban than va gia dinh?co \nthe.chi phi van chuyen bao nhieu?don hang tren 600.000d, van \nchuyen mien phi. duoi 600, phi van chuyen la 25.000d.cach \nthanh toan tien hang nhu the nao?thanh toan bang tien mat hoac chuyen \nkhoan ngan hang.bao lau thi hang toi noi?thong thuong la 2-3 \nngay.toi can phai lam gi khi ban toi muon gia nhap \noriflame?hay huong dan lai ban cua ban cach dang ky nhu ban da lam. ban \nco the lien he mr: \nkhanh 0934225077 de duoc tro \ngiup.toi co the kiem bao nhieu tien?&gt;&gt; xem ban co the kiem bao nhieu \ntien voi oriflametoi co the \ntao website rieng cho minh khong?co the. (vidu)cac cau hoi \ncua toi khong co trong danh sach tren - toi se hoi ai?ban co the hoi \ntruc tiep mr: khanh 0934225077 de duoc giai dap.\n&nbsp;\nloi chao mung cua tong \ngiam doc oriflame viet nam \ncac tu van \nvien than men!\n\nkhi toi viet \nnhung dong nay thi tat ca chung ta dang dung truoc them nam moi 2010 \nday xan lan voi nhung du tinh cung nhung ke hoach thanh cong cho \ntuong lai. \nthoi gian \ntroi qua that nhanh va nhu vay toi da lam viec tai oriflame viet nam \nduoc vai thang. toi that su co an tuong rat tot voi tat ca cac \nban tu van vien cung nhu doi ngu nhan vien cua oriflame viet nam va tren \nhet la voi nhung thanh cong tuyet voi cua cac \nban.\ntoi tin chac \nrang cac ban dang that su co trong tay nhung co hoi tot nhat vi voi \noriflame chung ta co: \nnguon nhan luc \nday nhiet huyet va tai nang \nnhung co hoi \nde co nguon thu nhap tuyet voi \nnhung dong \nsan pham chat luong cao rat duoc uu chuong \ncac ban \nhay xac dinh cho minh day la cong viec kinh doanh nghiem tuc va lau \ndai. co nhu the ban moi that su chu dong ve nguon tai chinh cua \nminh; chu dong ve viec xay dung mot cuoc song tot dep hon cho gia \ndinh va nhung nguoi ban yeu thuong. de dat duoc nhung dieu nhu vay \nban can phai lam viec that nghiem tuc, that cham chi, day nhiet \nhuyet, trung thuc va dao duc. \ntai oriflame \nchung toi dat ra 3 tieu chi quan trong de lam thuoc do thanh cong cho \ncong viec kinh doanh cua minh; cung nhu khong ngung cai thien chung de \nphat trien ngay cang lon manh va thanh cong hon. nhung tieu chi nay \ncung se rat huu ich cho ban voi cuong vi la mot leader de xay dung \nva phat trien he thong cua minh. do chinh la: \ntuyen dung: \nla so nguoi chung ta moi gia nhap cung oriflame va dat don hang dau \ntien \nhoat dong: la \nso nguoi dat it nhat mot don hang trong thang gan \nnhat \ndoanh thu: la \ngia tri don hang cua cac tu van vien dang hoat dong trong tung thang \n\nday that ra \nchi la mot bai toan don gian, neu ban muon tang thu nhap cua minh \nhay phan dau de phat trien nhung tieu chi tren. va do chinh la cong \nviec cua tat ca chung ta!\nchung toi \nluon tao cho ban nhieu co hoi tuyen dung qua nhung chuong trinh tuyen \ndung vo cung hap dan va tat ca nhung gi ban can lam la dau tu vao \nnhung cuon catalogue hang thang de gioi thieu va tu van hieu qua hon, \nco gang moi duoc nhieu nguoi tham gia va ho tro ho hoat dong de \ndat hieu qua toi da cho he thong cua ban trong tung chuong trinh \ntuyen dung.\nben canh \ndo, chung toi con mang den cho ban nhung co hoi mua hang giam gia doc \ndao voi cac chuong trinh danh cho business class, hay nhung phan tien \nthuong hap dan cua cau lac bo leaders, cac to roi khuyen mai voi gia \ncuc soc va nhieu nhung hoat dong huu ich khac nham giup cac ban \nday manh kinh doanh cung nhu tang doanh thu cho he thong minh. ban cung \nco the thuc hien nhung hoat dong tuong tu de dong vien tuyen duoi, \ngiup ho phat trien va tu do ban co the xay dung he thong cua minh \nngay cang vung manh. \nchung toi \nluon ho tro cac ban trong viec thuc hien nhung uoc mo cua minh. cu \nthe la ho tro cac ban tro thanh cac leader; giup cac ban tuyen \ndung, huan luyen, phat trien tuyen duoi cua minh va giup ho cung \ntro thanh nhung leader nhu ban. bang cach do ban se ngay cang phat \ntrien cao hon va tien gan hon den dinh tha