ndoc oriflame viet nam\n&nbsp;\ncac tu van vien cua \noriflame viet nam thanh cong den muc nao? \ncau chuyen #1: a dream come \ntrue\na friend invited me to \njoin oriflame the very first day the company began operating in vietnam. i was \njobless at the time, and had moved from a province nearby ho chi minh city to \nlook for new opportunities.\nthe wide range of \nhigh-quality, affordable oriflame products immediately helped me. to my \nsurprise, it was easy to sell oriflame products to my neighbours and friends  \nall i had to do was show them the catalogue.\nsuddenly, for the \nfirst time in my life, i had my own income! the journey had just started, and i \ncould barely believe it when i earned something like 1,000 the first month, a \nphenomenal amount of money in vietnam.\nmy friends and family \nmust have thought id won the lottery  that is until i quickly collected gold \ndirector, sapphire director, diamond director titles, received cash awards and \nwas invited on foreign trips. then they realized that at oriflame anything is \npossible.\noriflame has changed \nmy life so much! my monthly income is now around 2,000  ten times higher than \nour entire household income before oriflame. but the company has done more than \njust raise my familys standard of living. oriflame has also made me much more \nselfconfident, partly because i can enhance my natural beauty by using oriflame \ncosmetics every day.\ntoday, im working to \nexpand my network all over the country. after all, i want to make sure that \noriflame keeps its no. 1 position in vietnam! the income is very important, \nofcourse, but i also enjoy meeting so many interesting people and making new \nfriends.\nfor me, oriflame has \nbeen a dream come true. whenever i speak about oriflame to others who are \nlooking for a new job, a new opportunity or a new career, the first thing i talk \nabout is our products, stressing the high quality and reasonable price. \nmoreover, i always make sure to tell them