t do &ndash; l&agrave; ngi l&agrave;m vic c lp kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; n v qun l&yacute; trong nhng ng&agrave;nh ngh m&agrave; ngi l&agrave;m to&agrave;n thi gian chim a s. Kh&aacute;i nim n&agrave;y &atilde; tng c Walter Scott a ra trong quyn tiu thuyt ni ting Ivanhoe  m&ocirc; t v nhng ngi l&iacute;nh &aacute;nh thu&ecirc; thi trung c...</strong></span></p>\n<p>Ngi  l&agrave;m <a title=\"Freelancer \" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">Freelancer </a>c&oacute; th nhn nhiu <a title=\"vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">vic b&aacute;n thi gian</a> kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave; t thu xp thi gian  theo c&aacute;ch ca m&igrave;nh min sao c&ocirc;ng vic t kt qu tt. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, cng  cn ph&acirc;n bit r&otilde; Freelancer vi nhng ngi c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng vic bp b&ecirc;nh, cung  cp dch v, sn phm mt c&aacute;ch ngu hng v&agrave; t&ugrave;y tin n gin v&igrave; h  kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; k hoch.</p>\n<p> nhng nc ph&aacute;t trin, ngh Freelancer  rt c tr&acirc;n trng v&igrave; nhng Freelancer thng phi l&agrave; nhng ngi rt  gii v&agrave; l&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n gia thc s. Trong khi &oacute;  nhng nc ang ph&aacute;t  trin, Freelancer thng ng ngha vi vic kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kh nng t&igrave;m kim  vic l&agrave;m n nh. Hin nay  nc ta xu hng Freelancer tp trung v&agrave;o  hai nh&oacute;m ngh ch&iacute;nh:</p>\n<p>Nh&oacute;m th nht gm nhng ngh &ograve;i hi s  &agrave;o to b&agrave;i bn chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u v&agrave; d&agrave;y dn kinh nghim, nh t vn lut, t  vn th&agrave;nh lp - t&aacute;i cu tr&uacute;c doanh nghip, k to&aacute;n, b&aacute;c s, dch thut,  lp tr&igrave;nh, IT...</p>\n<p>Nh&oacute;m th 2 thi&ecirc;n v s&aacute;ng to nh sn xut &acirc;m  nhc, o din chng tr&igrave;nh, t chc s kin, nhip nh gia, thit k  ( ha, ni tht, thi trang,..), kin tr&uacute;c s, stylist, vit b&aacute;o, PR,  copywriter...</p>\n<p><strong>Nhng thun li ca ngh Freelancer</strong></p>\n<p>Nh&igrave;n t b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i, Freelancer qu l&agrave; mt xu hng l&agrave;m vic tht l&yacute; tng vi nhng u im ni tri:</p>\n<p><img style=\"float: left; margin-left: 6px; margin-right: 6px; border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Freelancer v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" src=\"http://www.saga.vn/Saga_Gallery/ChauHa/BizKnowledge/quit.jpg\" alt=\"Freelancer v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" width=\"300\" height=\"376\" />Th  nht, bn s ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c th&aacute;o b khi nhng r&agrave;ng buc kht khe ca  cuc sng c&ocirc;ng s. Bn kh&ocirc;ng cn &uacute;ng 8h s&aacute;ng n c&ocirc;ng ty, chng phi  chu ng &aacute;nh mt kh&oacute; chu ca sp mi l&uacute;c i l&agrave;m tr, kh&ocirc;ng phi b&oacute;  cng trong b ng phc sut 8 ting ng h...</p>\n<p>Th hai, l&agrave; mt  Freelancer bn s c th sc ph&aacute;t huy sc s&aacute;ng to v&agrave; iu chnh c&aacute;c &yacute;  tng m&agrave; chng s sp can thip v&igrave; gi &acirc;y ch&iacute;nh bn &oacute;ng vai tr&ograve; l&agrave;m  sp ca m&igrave;nh.</p>\n<p>Th ba, bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th thay i phong c&aacute;ch  l&agrave;m vic thm ch&iacute; l&agrave; loi h&igrave;nh, t&iacute;nh cht c&ocirc;ng vic... sau khi &atilde; cm  thy \"ch&aacute;n\" mt dng c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;o &oacute;.</p>\n<p>Th t, khi bn &atilde; l&agrave;  mt Freelancer c bit n v&agrave; tin cy th&igrave; vic bn nm c nhng hp  ng ln, b t&uacute;i v&agrave;i ng&agrave;n &ocirc; ch trong mt th&aacute;ng s tr n&ecirc;n d d&agrave;ng.  Thc t cho thy nhiu c&ocirc;ng ty sn s&agrave;ng tr c&ocirc;ng kh&aacute; cao cho nhng  Freelancer ph&ugrave; hp vi c&ocirc;ng vic m&agrave; h ang thiu ngi. Mc thu nhp  h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng ca mt Freelancer cao gp hai, ba ln so vi c&aacute;c ng nghip  l&agrave;m to&agrave;n thi gian cng l&agrave; chuyn b&igrave;nh thng. Sau mt ln &ldquo;tr&uacute;ng qu&rdquo;  nh th, bn c&oacute; th vi vu du lch &acirc;u &oacute; c tun l ngh x hi m&agrave; chng  phi bn t&acirc;m n vic np n xin ph&eacute;p ai.</p>\n<p>Th nm, nu c&oacute; mt  nh&oacute;m bn c&ugrave;ng l&agrave;m vic theo kiu Freelancer th&igrave; tht qu&aacute; tuyt. Vic  trao i c&ocirc;ng vic, &yacute; tng, h tr nhau s t c mc ti a. Mi  ngi trong nh&oacute;m cng s ph&aacute;t huy ht kh nng v&agrave; tinh thn tr&aacute;ch nhim  ca m&igrave;nh vi c&ocirc;ng vic.</p>\n<p>u im th s&aacute;u m&agrave; ngh Freelancer mang  li &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; vic m mang c&aacute;c mi quan h, t&iacute;ch ly th&ecirc;m nhiu kinh  nghim l&agrave;m vic c lp cng nh s t gi&aacute;c ca bn</p>\n<p><strong>V&agrave;... kh&oacute; khn chng cht</strong></p>\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh nhng u im k tr&ecirc;n, Freelancer cng ng ngha vi vic bn s phi i mt vi kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t nhng kh&oacute; khn v&agrave; ri ro.</p>\n<p>Khi  &atilde; l&agrave; mt Freelancer, c&oacute; ngha l&agrave; bn c t do nhng bn phi bit  c&aacute;ch s dng s t do y t hiu qu ti a. Mi g&aacute;nh nng tr&aacute;ch nhim  u tr&uacute;t l&ecirc;n vai bn, bn va l&agrave;m ch, va l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng cho ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh, li  ki&ecirc;m th&ecirc;m k to&aacute;n thu chi v&agrave; h&agrave;ng trm vic lt vt kh&aacute;c. Nu thiu k  lut, kh&ocirc;ng kh&eacute;o qun l&yacute; v thi gian v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic, mi k hoch ca bn s b ph&aacute; sn t l&uacute;c n&agrave;o kh&ocirc;ng bit.</p>\n<p>Ri  ro tip theo l&agrave; bn kh&ocirc;ng c hng mc lng n nh c&ugrave;ng nhng ph  cp, &atilde;i ng ca c&ocirc;ng ty n&agrave;o c, hoc nu bn tht bi trong mt k  hoch g&igrave; y, kh&ocirc;ng ai kh&aacute;c ngo&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh bn phi chu tr&aacute;ch nhim tt c  thit hi, v&agrave; d nhi&ecirc;n iu n&agrave;y s nh hng kh&aacute; ln n uy t&iacute;n ca  bn. C&oacute; l v&igrave; vy m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t ngi gi Freelancer l&agrave; ngh &ldquo;kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute;  hu&rdquo;, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; s bo m cho tng lai.</p>\n<p>Nu bn l&agrave;m vic n  nh ti mt c&ocirc;ng ty ln th&igrave; thng hiu ca c&ocirc;ng ty cng ch&iacute;nh l&agrave;  thng hiu ca bn. Nhng khi l&agrave;m Freelancer, bn s phi t x&acirc;y dng thng hiu cho ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh.  Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; th nu bn cha c nhiu ngi bit n hoc cha c&oacute; nhiu  kinh nghim, kh nng t&igrave;m kim kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s tr n&ecirc;n kh&oacute; khn hn.</p>\n<p>L&agrave;m  sp ca bn th&acirc;n cng c&oacute; ngha l&agrave; bn phi quyt o&aacute;n, t gi&aacute;c v&agrave;  nghi&ecirc;m khc vi ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh. Nu bn l&agrave; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ca mt c&ocirc;ng ty, sai  lm ca bn c&oacute; th c cp tr&ecirc;n ph&aacute;t hin ra trc khi th&agrave;nh sn phm  giao cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, l&agrave;m Freelancer, bn phi tr th&agrave;nh \"tnh t&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n\"  ca ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh. Nu phm sai lm, bn c&oacute; th l&acirc;m v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh trng \" m\"  trong mt thi gian d&agrave;i.</p>\n<p>Quan trng nht, Freelancer ng ngha  vi vn sng, b d&agrave;y kinh nghim v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n s&acirc;u trong c&ocirc;ng vic.  Him ai va tt nghip &atilde; tr th&agrave;nh mt Freelancer gii. Mun vy it  nht, bn cng phi tri qua v&agrave;i nm trong mt v&agrave;i c&ocirc;ng ty ln nh, c&oacute;  nhng sn phm cht lng tt, t n  ch&iacute;n nht nh v ngh nghip,  to c bi&ecirc;n  quan h rng song song vi vic ho&agrave;n thin h&agrave;ng lot  k nng v thuyt tr&igrave;nh, &agrave;m ph&aacute;n, l&agrave;m vic nh&oacute;m vi c&aacute;c Freelancer kh&aacute;c trong c&ugrave;ng d &aacute;n...</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.saga.vn/Saga_Gallery/ChauHa/BizKnowledge/startup.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"startup.jpg\" hspace=\"6\" width=\"250\" height=\"187\" align=\"right\" />Ngay  c khi &atilde; l&agrave; nhng Freelancer d&agrave;y dn kinh nghim, s c&oacute; l&uacute;c bn cm  thy mt mi sau qu&atilde;ng thi gian \"ln ln\" vi ngh, khi th&igrave; c&ocirc;ng vic  kh&ocirc;ng xu, phi chy ua vi thi gian n mc l&agrave;m qua qu&yacute;t u t mt c  uy t&iacute;n, l&uacute;c li ngi kh&ocirc;ng, chng kim c ng n&agrave;o sut my th&aacute;ng  tri. Hn na, ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng nhiu cnh tranh trong ngh Freelancer, thm  ch&iacute; c&oacute; c chuyn ph&aacute; gi&aacute;, gi&agrave;nh mi, nhn vic vi gi&aacute; r mt...</p>\n<p>T&oacute;m  li bn th&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng vic Freelancer kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; g&igrave; sai, vn  l&agrave; la chn  ca bn c&oacute; &uacute;ng hng v&agrave; ph&ugrave; hp vi bn th&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng. Nu l&agrave; ngi th&iacute;ch  phi&ecirc;u lu v&agrave; c&aacute; t&iacute;nh mnh,  bn lnh i ph&oacute; vi nhng bin c, c&oacute; th  Freelancer s l&agrave; con ng th&iacute;ch hp vi bn. C&ograve;n nu bn mong mun  cuc sng &ecirc;m m, c&ocirc;ng vic v&agrave; thu nhp n nh, th&igrave; h&atilde;y chung thy vi  la chn &ldquo;ngi ca c&ocirc;ng ty&rdquo;. c v&agrave; mt, &aacute; hc hay hoa hng, t&ugrave;y  thuc v&agrave;o bn.</p>\n<p><strong>Nhng vn  cn lu &yacute; khi tr th&agrave;nh Freelancer</strong></p>\n<p><strong>T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh (Finances):</strong> &acirc;y l&agrave; mt trong nhng vn  quan trng h&agrave;ng u m&agrave; bn cn phi quan  t&acirc;m khi bt u quyt nh tr th&agrave;nh mt Freelancer. Bn phi chc chn  lu&ocirc;n c&oacute;  tin trong t&agrave;i khon  c&oacute; th gi&uacute;p bn tr vng khi \" m\".</p>\n<p><strong>M&ocirc;i trng l&agrave;m vic (Working Environment):</strong> Nu bn c&oacute; mt m&ocirc;i trng l&agrave;m vic thoi m&aacute;i  nh&agrave; th&igrave; &oacute;&nbsp;l&agrave; tt nht.  Tuy nhi&ecirc;n s tht tin li nu ngo&agrave;i nh&agrave; ra bn c&ograve;n c&oacute; th tn dng bt  c ni &acirc;u l&agrave;m th&agrave;nh vn ph&ograve;ng l&agrave;m vic.</p>\n<p><strong>Portfolio:</strong> Khi l&agrave; mt Freelancer, tp portfolio s th hin bn v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic ca  bn. Nu l&agrave; mt ngi ph&aacute;t trin phn mm th&igrave; n&oacute; li c&agrave;ng cn thit phi  c&oacute; trong tay. N&oacute; gi&uacute;p bn nhn mnh d &aacute;n mi nht bn l&agrave;m, k thut  ca bn, ng&ocirc;n ng bn s dng, c&ocirc;ng c bn d&ugrave;ng, v&agrave; kin thc bn &atilde;  hc. H&atilde;y bo v nhng t&aacute;c phm ca m&igrave;nh, ph&aacute;t trin n&oacute; cng nh ph&aacute;t  trin k nng bn th&acirc;n m&igrave;nh.</p>\n<p><strong>C&aacute;c k ngh (Holidays):</strong> Sau khi ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh mt s d &aacute;n, h&atilde;y t&iacute;nh n thi gian  ngh ngi.  N&oacute; gi&uacute;p tinh thn bn thoi m&aacute;i tr li, ngh ra c th&ecirc;m nhng &yacute; tng  mi...</p>\n<p><strong>Ni s h&atilde;i (The Fear):</strong> Mi ngi  u s h&atilde;i  mt s vn : S s kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; thu nhp trong mt thi gian  d&agrave;i, hoc s kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; vic  l&agrave;m. Kh&ocirc;ng sao &acirc;u, nhng khong thi gian  nh vy, h&atilde;y d&agrave;nh thi gian &oacute;  ph&aacute;t trin nhng k nng mi hoc i  du lch th gi&atilde;n...</p>\n<p><em>Ngun : </em>www.saga.vn</p>\n</span></span></p>','2011-03-06 21:47:38','admin@jobbid.vn',470,1),(9,'cua-hieu-nha-hang-chat-vat-tuyen-nhan-vien','Ca hiu, nh hng cht vt tuyn nhn vin','http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/73/3f/tuyen-1.jpg','Khng yu cu cao v trnh  vy m nhiu ca hng hay nhng ki t ch, ch kinh doanh ti H Ni vn au u vi vn  tuyn dng.','<p><span style=\"font-size: small; color: #888888;\"><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/73/3f/tuyen-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" /><strong>Kh&ocirc;ng y&ecirc;u cu cao v tr&igrave;nh  vy m&agrave; nhiu ca h&agrave;ng hay  nhng ki t ch, ch kinh doanh ti H&agrave; Ni vn au u vi vn  tuyn  dng.</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ri&ecirc;ng tr&ecirc;n tuyn ng Phm Ngc Thch &ndash; Ch&ugrave;a Bc &ndash;  T&acirc;y Sn &atilde; c&oacute; ti hn hai mi ca hiu treo bin &ldquo;<a title=\"tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n</a>&rdquo;. Vn   tng t cng din ra ti nhiu nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng. C&oacute; nhng ni cn tuyn ti  10 nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n gm c chy b&agrave;n, tr&ocirc;ng xe ln nu n....</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Ch Th&uacute;y Hnh, ch mt shop thi trang tr&ecirc;n ph Phm  Ngc Thch cho hay, trc ch cng c&oacute; mt c&ocirc; b&eacute; b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng rt m&aacute;t tay.  \"Nhng ra Tt, con b&eacute; nng nc &ograve;i  nh&agrave; ly chng, tng lng th n&agrave;o  cng kh&ocirc;ng l&ecirc;n. N&oacute; k&ecirc;u con g&aacute;i c&oacute; thi, l&ecirc;n H&agrave; Ni l&agrave;m, qu&aacute; tui th&igrave; \",  ch k.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Kh hn ch Hnh, anh H&ugrave;ng, ch qu&aacute;n n sang trng  tr&ecirc;n ng Hunh Th&uacute;c Kh&aacute;ng ang au u v&igrave; lo tuyn mt l&uacute;c 5 nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n  n chy b&agrave;n. &ldquo;My c&ocirc; y b v khu c&ocirc;ng nghip l&agrave;m ht ri, k&ecirc;u  &oacute;  c &oacute;ng bo him&rdquo;, anh H&ugrave;ng than th.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Theo t&igrave;m hiu ca <em>VnExpress.net</em>, hu ht c&aacute;c  ch bu&ocirc;n b&aacute;n nh u kh&ocirc;ng y&ecirc;u cu cao v tr&igrave;nh  hc vn khi tuyn  nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n. &ldquo;Ch cn a nh&igrave;n, n n&oacute;i hot b&aacute;t l&agrave; nhn. Hc vn kh&ocirc;ng quan  trng, hc ht lp my cng c, kh&eacute;o l&eacute;o v&agrave; b&aacute;n c h&agrave;ng l&agrave; tuyn&rdquo;,  ch Hnh cho bit th&ecirc;m.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/73/3f/tuyen-2.jpg\" border=\"1\" alt=\"Nhiu ca h&agrave;ng c&oacute; nhu cu tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&igrave;nh  tay ngh chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n. nh: Xu&acirc;n Ngc\" width=\"450\" height=\"360\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Image\">Nhiu ca h&agrave;ng c&oacute; nhu cu <a title=\"Tuyn Sinh Vi&ecirc;n L&agrave;m Th&ecirc;m B&aacute;n Thi Gian\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn/duan/view/91/tuyen-sinh-vien-lam-them-ban-thoi-gian\">tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng</a>. nh: <em>Xu&acirc;n Ngc</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Do c th&ugrave; c&ocirc;ng vic, nhiu ni cng ng tuyn nhng  nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; tay ngh nh bit sa qun &aacute;o, bit chnh c gi&agrave;y hay c&oacute;  kinh nghim l&agrave;m bi b&agrave;n. C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vic nh vy thng c&oacute; mc lng 3-3,5  triu ng mi th&aacute;ng, cao hn t mt triu n 1,5 triu ng so vi  nhng c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng n thun. Nu l&agrave;m b&aacute;n thi gian th&igrave; ngi lao  ng c&oacute; thu nhp bng mt na nh vy. Mc lng n&agrave;y s tng dn theo  th&acirc;m ni&ecirc;n v&agrave; th&agrave;nh qu sn phm.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Song nhng c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y vn cha thu h&uacute;t c nhiu  lao ng. Bc ra t mt ca h&agrave;ng c&oacute; nhu cu tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n, H&agrave; My,  sinh vi&ecirc;n i hc S phm tht vng cho bit, h y&ecirc;u cu l&agrave;m c ng&agrave;y n&ecirc;n  c&ocirc; kh&ocirc;ng th m ng ni. &ldquo;Ch h&agrave;ng n&oacute;i nu l&agrave;m na ng&agrave;y cng phi t  8 gi n 15 gi hoc t 15 gi n 22 gi. Thi gian vt ngang gi hc  nh vy n&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh &agrave;nh th&ocirc;i&rdquo;, H&agrave; My t&acirc;m s.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute;, vi nhiu ngi, &acirc;y ch l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic  &ldquo;chng ch&aacute;y&rdquo;. Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ca mt ki t trong ch Ng&atilde; T S chia s ch ra  trng, ang ch xin vic n&ecirc;n l&agrave;m tm  &acirc;y, kim tin tr li  H&agrave;  Ni. Khi n&agrave;o xin c v&agrave;o c&ocirc;ng ty n&agrave;o &oacute;, ch s ngh. &acirc;y cng l&agrave; l&yacute; do  khin nhiu ca h&agrave;ng li&ecirc;n tc tuyn v&agrave; thay nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C&ograve;n theo ch Hng, cu nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng vi tr&ecirc;n 5  nm kinh nghim cho hay, c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng tuy kh&ocirc;ng &ograve;i hi bng cp  nhng kh&ocirc;ng n gin. Ch Hng n&oacute;i: &ldquo;T c&aacute;ch n&oacute;i l&agrave;m sao cho lt tai  kh&aacute;ch, c&aacute;ch treo qun &aacute;o khin m&agrave;u sc c&aacute;c b t&ocirc;n l&ecirc;n cho nhau  bt  mt n c&aacute;ch ch&agrave;o hi, thm ch&iacute; lu&ocirc;n mm khen m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng b k&ecirc;u &lsquo;do  ming, x&aacute;o rng&rsquo; l&agrave; c mt qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh t&iacute;ch ly. Nhng ngi mi v&agrave;o ngh  cha quen th&igrave; kh&oacute; l&agrave;m lm. M&agrave; l&agrave;m &lsquo;thng &rsquo; pht &yacute; mt ln th&igrave; c&oacute; di  thm , h cng chng th&egrave;m lui ti na&rdquo;.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">&ldquo;&oacute; l&agrave; cha k n vic nu kh&ocirc;ng b&aacute;n c h&agrave;ng, ch  s mt nng m&agrave;y nh, ra v&agrave;o mt c&acirc;u, thm ch&iacute; c&ograve;n bo m&igrave;nh v&iacute;a nng, v&ocirc;  duy&ecirc;n. &Aacute;p lc nh vy n&ecirc;n nhiu ngi kh&ocirc;ng tr c vi vic&rdquo;, ch  Hng cho bit th&ecirc;m.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, theo ch Th&uacute;y, ch mt ca h&agrave;ng b&aacute;n gi&agrave;y  d&eacute;p, vi nhng ngi kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; bng cp th&igrave; b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic kh&aacute; l&yacute;  tng. &ldquo;L&agrave;m l&acirc;u s th&agrave;nh quen, so vi mc lng &oacute;, i l&agrave;m gi&uacute;p vic hay  b&aacute;n do ngo&agrave;i ph c&ograve;n kh hn nhiu. &acirc;y ma nng kh&ocirc;ng lo, chu kh&oacute;  hc hi kinh nghim v&agrave; cht chiu th&igrave; cng c&oacute; c hi d&agrave;nh dm vn m mt  ca h&agrave;ng nh sau n&agrave;y cho m&igrave;nh&rdquo;.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><strong>Xu&acirc;n Ngc</strong></p>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><em>(ngun VnExpress.net)</em><strong></strong></p>','2011-03-09 08:47:28','admin@jobbid.vn',180,1),(10,'13-cach-tim-hieu-cong-viec-ban-thoi-gian','13 cch tm hiu cng vic bn thi gian','http://divivu.com/uploads/work/news/eda_t1259564137_S002.jpg','Ai ni khng th giu khi lm iu mnh thch? C th lm cng vic mnh a thch theo kiu bn thi gian (part time) nh nhng sng kin sau: ','<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: small;\">\n<div id=\"ar-content-html\">\n<p><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"13 c&aacute;ch t&igrave;m hiu c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" src=\"http://divivu.com/uploads/work/news/eda_t1259564137_S002.jpg\" alt=\"13 c&aacute;ch t&igrave;m hiu c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" width=\"300\" height=\"239\" /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong>Ai n&oacute;i kh&ocirc;ng th gi&agrave;u khi l&agrave;m iu m&igrave;nh th&iacute;ch? C&oacute; th l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng vic m&igrave;nh a th&iacute;ch theo kiu <a title=\"b&aacute;n thi gian\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">b&aacute;n thi gian</a> (<a title=\"l&agrave;m vic part-time\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">part time</a>) nh nhng s&aacute;ng kin sau:</strong></span></p>\n<p>Nu bn thc c &ecirc;m  vt &oacute;c ra k hoch r&uacute;t lui hay c&aacute;ch kim th&ecirc;m  tin, th&igrave; h&atilde;y t&igrave;m mt khuynh hng c&oacute; th ph&aacute;t trin mnh, qung c&aacute;o   mi ngi bit n ri iu chnh cho ph&ugrave; hp vi s th&iacute;ch mt i tng  kh&aacute;n gi c bit. Ch&igrave;a kh&oacute;a  bin mt &yacute; tng, t&agrave;i nng hay chuy&ecirc;n  m&ocirc;n c &aacute;o th&agrave;nh c xe vng chc l&agrave; bit  &yacute; n cuc sng xung quanh,  v&igrave; &yacute; tng lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; quanh bn rt nhiu.</p>\n<p>V&iacute; d: ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng c&oacute; nhiu ph n t&igrave;m c&aacute;ch tho&aacute;t khi c&ocirc;ng vic gia  &igrave;nh. T chc c&acirc;u lc b s&aacute;ch, tic ru, trang sc hay d hi l&agrave; nhng  hot ng va vui v va c&oacute; th kim tin.</p>\n<p>Hoc dy mt k nng mi, k thut cao v&agrave; ri&ecirc;ng bit n&agrave;o &oacute;? Ai cng  c&oacute; mt lnh vc chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n  b&aacute;n cho ngi kh&aacute;c. Trung t&acirc;m gi&aacute;o dc  thng xuy&ecirc;n ca cng ng l&agrave; ni th&iacute;ch hp  bn tip th chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n  ca m&igrave;nh.</p>\n<p>Di &acirc;y l&agrave; mt s &yacute; tng gi&uacute;p bn t&igrave;m ra ch th&iacute;ch hp nht cho m&igrave;nh:</p>\n</div>\n</span></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ch&igrave;a kh&oacute;a  bin mt &yacute; tng, t&agrave;i nng hay chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n c &aacute;o th&agrave;nh c xe vng chc l&agrave; bit  &yacute; n cuc sng xung quanh...</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: small;\">\n<div id=\"ar-content-html\">\n<p><strong>1. Dch v c&aacute; nh&acirc;n:</strong> Bn c&oacute; th gi&uacute;p ngi kh&aacute;c tit  kim thi gian kh&ocirc;ng? Chy vic cho cp tr&ecirc;n, chun b th tc ho&agrave;n  thu, hay dt ch&oacute; h&agrave;ng x&oacute;m i do l&agrave; nhng dch v gi&aacute; tr.</p>\n<p><strong>2. L&agrave;m vn v&agrave; l&agrave;m p phong cnh.</strong> Th ngh n vic  trng vn. Ng&agrave;y nay nhng ch nh&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute;  thi gian hoc am m&ecirc;  trng ta vn nhn ra tm quan trng ca va h&egrave;. Thit k phong cnh,  chm s&oacute;c c&acirc;y v&agrave; l&agrave;m vn thu&ecirc; ang thnh h&agrave;nh. Nu th&iacute;ch gn gi thi&ecirc;n  nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; kh&iacute; hu trong l&agrave;nh, bn c&oacute; th chn ngh l&agrave;m vn, gm nhiu  chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n kh&aacute;c nhau nh trng c&acirc;y, chm s&oacute;c c&acirc;y thng nghip trng  trong nh&agrave; k&iacute;nh, gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c lp hc g&ocirc;n hay l&agrave;m dch v nh&agrave; t t nh&acirc;n.  Nu c ch dn b&agrave;i bn, bn s bit c&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng tia nc t&aacute;c ng n  c&acirc;y trng  c&aacute;c v&ugrave;ng kh&aacute;c nhau sao cho hiu qu nht.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Hot ng gii tr&iacute; ngo&agrave;i tri.</strong> Nhiu ngi kh&ocirc;ng  t&aacute;ch ri c&ocirc;ng vic v&agrave; vui chi. H s min cng bm ng h  dy sm  bui s&aacute;ng, hay gii hn m&igrave;nh trong ph&ograve;ng l&agrave;m vic  kim sng. Nu y&ecirc;u  t do, c&oacute; l bn mun l&agrave;m n ri&ecirc;ng vi i t&aacute;c l&agrave; t M. C&oacute; th kinh  doanh bng c&aacute;ch cung cp b&egrave; g, hng dn p xe leo n&uacute;i, i xe b&ograve; chp  h&igrave;nh, i b ng d&agrave;i, leo n&uacute;i &aacute;, hay l&agrave;m vic quanh c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh  ph.</p>\n<p><strong>4. Dch v chm s&oacute;c th&uacute; nu&ocirc;i. </strong>Kinh doanh c&oacute; th n&agrave;o  khi i t nhng ch&uacute; ch&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng? Dch v v&agrave; h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a cao cp d&agrave;nh cho th&uacute;  nu&ocirc;i ang ng&agrave;y mt th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. Theo mt nghi&ecirc;n cu mi &acirc;y ca n V  Tip Th, Hoa K t doanh thu 30 t &ocirc;la mt nm. Thc n, dch v chm  s&oacute;c, du gi, l&agrave;m p v&agrave; kh&aacute;ch sn cho th&uacute; cng l&agrave; nhng sn phm, dch  v to n&ecirc;n nn c&ocirc;ng nghip n&agrave;y. Nu bn kh&eacute;o iu khin ch&oacute; th&igrave; dy ch&oacute;  cng l&agrave; mt ng&agrave;nh n&oacute;ng em li thu nhp.</p>\n<p><strong>5. Thit k ni l&agrave;m vic. </strong>Bn c&oacute; th tr th&agrave;nh nh&agrave;  thit k kh&ocirc;ng gian l&agrave;m vic tng lai. Khi c&ocirc;ng nghip ph&aacute;t trin th&igrave;  vn ph&ograve;ng phi bt mt t m&aacute;i hi&ecirc;n, dng c n m&agrave;u sc, &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng. C&agrave;ng  ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng c&oacute; nhiu ngi cn chuy&ecirc;n gia b sung iu kin sinh h&oacute;a.  Nhng lnh vc chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n gm: ni l&agrave;m vic  khu c&ocirc;ng nghip, an to&agrave;n  ngh nghip, thit k ni tht, phn cng m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh, giao tip m&aacute;y  t&iacute;nh-con ngi,  tin cy sn phm, sn phm cho ngi ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&agrave; m&ocirc;i  trng o.</p>\n<p><strong>6. T vn phong thy. </strong>Nhng nm gn &acirc;y, s ngi  quan t&acirc;m n phong thy &atilde; gia tng. H t&igrave;m kim s tha m&atilde;n v&agrave; hiu qu  cao trong ngh nghip, kinh doanh v&agrave; cuc sng. Phong thy l&agrave; m&ocirc;n ngh  thut c xa,  cao sc khe t&acirc;m linh v&agrave; vt cht th&ocirc;ng qua vic hng  dn ngi chi hng tt nht  t vn ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; nh&agrave; ca. C&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n  gia c&oacute; tr&igrave;nh  c thu&ecirc;  &ldquo;xem&rdquo; cho khu d&acirc;n c v&agrave; khu thng mi. Ph&iacute;  tr cho c&aacute;c t vn vi&ecirc;n l&agrave; t 235 n 1.000 M kim cho hai ting t  vn, t&ugrave;y  ln ca t&agrave;i sn. Mt v&agrave;i x&iacute; nghip tr n 25 ng&agrave;n &ocirc; cho  nhng d &aacute;n ln. Hc ph&iacute; cho nhng kh&oacute;a n&agrave;y, bao gm gi l&ecirc;n lp, c vn  v&agrave; &agrave;o to c&oacute; th l&ecirc;n n 3,500 &ocirc;la.</p>\n<p><strong>7. Dch v chm s&oacute;c sc khe.</strong> Do h thng chm s&oacute;c  bo v sc khe ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng ch&uacute; trng ph&ograve;ng bnh, c&aacute;c nc T&acirc;y phng &atilde;  chp nhn nhng phng ph&aacute;p mi  cha bnh v&agrave; sng khe to&agrave;n din.  Nhng liu ph&aacute;p cha bnh nh tr liu, m&aacute;t xa, ch&acirc;m cu v&agrave; yoga c t  nh&acirc;n ln c&ocirc;ng ty y&ecirc;u cu rt nhiu. Nhng ngi quan t&acirc;m n sc khe  t&igrave;m mua loi thc phm hu c kh&ocirc;ng ng hoc cht bo qun.</p>\n<p><strong>8. Dch v l&agrave;m p. </strong>C&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh qung c&aacute;o tr&ecirc;n  TV nh &ocirc;i Mt B&iacute; n ca Ngi Ch&acirc;n Ch&iacute;nh (Queer Eye for the Straight  Guy) &atilde; khin ph&aacute;i nam ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng quan t&acirc;m n sc hp dn ca ngoi  h&igrave;nh. Trc l&agrave;n s&oacute;ng n&agrave;y, mt tr&agrave;o lu l&agrave;m p v&agrave; th gi&atilde;n d&agrave;nh ri&ecirc;ng  cho qu&iacute; &ocirc;ng &atilde; ra i v&agrave; nhanh ch&oacute;ng l&ecirc;n ng&ocirc;i. Nhng dch v n&oacute;ng nht  hin c&oacute; gm l&agrave;m s&aacute;ng da, m&aacute;t xa mt v&agrave; c th, p mt bng to bin.</p>\n<p><strong>9. T&acirc;m linh.</strong> Nhng ngi thi&ecirc;n v t&acirc;m linh cho rng  sng nh&acirc;n &aacute;i l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic c i ca h. Ng&agrave;y nay, c&oacute; rt nhiu ngh  nghip cho nhng ai ngh m&igrave;nh c&oacute; s mnh khi ngun cm hng cho ngi  kh&aacute;c. V&iacute; d, ngh s hay ngh nh&acirc;n t&ocirc;n gi&aacute;o (phc v trong nhng ca  h&agrave;ng, xng l&agrave;m nn,  kim ho&agrave;n, hp n trang, nh Gi&aacute;ng sinh v&agrave;  lu  nim Do Th&aacute;i gi&aacute;o hay C&ocirc;ng gi&aacute;o); ngi t chc cm tri, t vn vi&ecirc;n/  ngi hng dn hot ng nh&agrave; th; t&aacute;c gi t&ocirc;n gi&aacute;o (cho s&aacute;ch b&aacute;o v&agrave;  thip); v&agrave; ngi hng dn tnh t&acirc;m. H hng dn ngi kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n h&agrave;nh  tr&igrave;nh v c&ugrave;ng &iacute;ch cuc i da v&agrave;o Kinh th&aacute;nh/ lch s.</p>\n<p><strong>10. Phc v gii thng lu.</strong> ng qu&ecirc;n cuc b&ugrave;ng n  tr em sau chin tranh th gii th hai  M &atilde; sinh ra nhng li &iacute;ch  g&igrave;. n nay nh&oacute;m d&acirc;n s tr&ecirc;n nm mi tui n&agrave;y vn l&agrave; i tng th&ocirc;ng  minh v&agrave; nng ng. H cn nh&agrave; cung cp sn phm, dch v v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng tin   &aacute;p ng nhu cu gii tr&iacute;, gi&aacute;o dc v&agrave; i sng. Phc v cho nh&oacute;m d&acirc;n c  n&agrave;y c&oacute; nhiu ng&agrave;nh mang li li nhun cao, nh: t&aacute;c gi s&aacute;ch phc v  gii thng lu, ngi ph&aacute;t trin mng, c&ocirc;ng ty du lch, bo him, bt  ng sn, &agrave;o to k s m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh</p>\n<p><strong>11. Dch v vit.</strong> Nu c&oacute; khiu th hin &yacute; tng bng  c&aacute;ch vit th&igrave; bn n&ecirc;n tr th&agrave;nh nh&agrave; l&ecirc;n k hoch kinh doanh. Nhiu  doanh nghip  vut mt hp ng, qu hay kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ch v&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng gii  truyn t qua giy b&uacute;t. Ng&agrave;y nay doanh nghip cn nhng ngi gii vit   tip th, tho chin lc, vn ng v&agrave; l&ecirc;n k hoch. Ngo&agrave;i ra, nhu  cu v t&aacute;c gi t do chuy&ecirc;n vit giy t chuyn nhng, h thng nhp  xut c bn, c&ocirc;ng ngh th&ocirc;ng tin, ph&aacute;t trin kinh t v&agrave; kinh doanh tng  th cng kh&aacute; cao. Vic d &aacute;n gm y&ecirc;u cu d &aacute;n, hng dn &agrave;o to o&agrave;n  th, t&agrave;i liu m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh, bn &aacute;nh gi&aacute;, giy ph&eacute;p ng dng ca ch&iacute;nh ph,  th b&aacute;o lp ph&aacute;p v&agrave; xut nhp h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh. Ph&iacute; thp nht khong 100 &ocirc;la/  gi, cao hn t 30.000 ti 60.000 &ocirc;la/ nm.</p>\n<p><strong>12. Thit k ni tht. </strong>Nh&agrave; l&agrave; ni th hin v p  ca ngh thut. Cuc b&ugrave;ng n tr em vi thu nhp t do v&agrave; xu hng &ldquo;to  k&eacute;n&rdquo; tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc &atilde; khin ng&agrave;nh trang tr&iacute; ni tht v&agrave; dch v thit  k ph&aacute;t trin rng khp, t nh&agrave; kh&aacute;ch n nh&agrave; hu dng, nh&agrave; tnh t&acirc;m  n ph&ograve;ng tm cao cp. Tham gia v&agrave;o i ng nhng ngi say m&ecirc; l&agrave;m gi&agrave;u  n&agrave;y gm c&oacute; kin tr&uacute;c s, nh&agrave; thit k ni tht, kin tr&uacute;c phong cnh v&agrave;  ngi x&acirc;y h bi. C&aacute;c lnh vc kh&aacute;c gm chuy&ecirc;n gia qun l&yacute; d &aacute;n cho  c&ocirc;ng ty ni tht, tin nghi c&ocirc;ng s, thit k kh&aacute;ch sn, vin chm s&oacute;c  da hay nh&agrave; hu dng.</p>\n<p><strong>13. Dch v nu n.</strong> Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute;, n  nh&agrave; cng l&agrave;  mt mt mi c&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng c nhiu ngi a chung. Tic ti em li  nhiu li nhun. Nu bn c&oacute; khiu nu n th&igrave; tht tuyt, v&igrave; rt nhiu  ngi cn bn. Ngo&agrave;i vic cung cp lng thc, bn c&ograve;n c&oacute; th dy nu  n, gi&uacute;p chun b thc n hay hng dn ti nh&agrave;. Nhiu ngi mun n  ung khe mnh v&igrave; l&iacute; do sc khe ln khu v n&ecirc;n bn c&oacute; th hot ng  vi t c&aacute;ch l&agrave; bp trng t hay nh&agrave; dinh dng.</p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>Ngun ENTREPRENEUR - dch V TH MINH UY&Ecirc;N (doanhnhansaigon)</em></div>\n</span></p>','2011-03-10 12:41:09','admin@jobbid.vn',302,1),(11,'song-than-cao-10-met-ap-vao-nhat-ban','Sng thn cao 10 mt p vo Nht Bn','http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/75/5d/earthquake.jpg','Sng thn p vo b bin pha ng bc Nht Bn hm nay sau cn a chn mnh 8,9  Richter, ln nht trong vng hn 100 nm nay. Ba ngi c xc nh  thit mng trong ng t.','<h2 class=\"Lead\"><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/75/5d/earthquake.jpg\" alt=\"Xe hi, xe ti b s&oacute;ng cun tr&ocirc;i sau ng t. nh: Sky News.\" width=\"400\" height=\"187\" /><span style=\"font-size: small; color: #888888;\">S&oacute;ng thn p v&agrave;o b bin ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng bc Nht Bn h&ocirc;m nay  sau cn a chn mnh 8,9  Richter, ln nht trong v&ograve;ng hn 100 nm  nay. Ba ngi c x&aacute;c nh &atilde; thit mng trong ng t.</span><a class=\"Lead\" href=\"http://vnexpress.net/gl/the-gioi/2011/03/cac-nuoc-ban-bo-canh-bao-song-than/\"></a></h2>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Image\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">ng t xy ra l&uacute;c 14h46 chiu nay (gi Tokyo)    s&acirc;u 10 km, c&aacute;ch Tokyo 382 km v ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng bc, c quan kho s&aacute;t a cht  M cho bit v&agrave; th&ecirc;m rng ng t mnh ti 8,9  Richter. Gii chc  Nht cho bit 3 ngi &atilde; thit mng sau cn a chn d di n&agrave;y.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\"Tim bn ra khi lng ngc. Cha bao gi cm gi&aacute;c ng  t nh ln n&agrave;y\", Phm Hng Long, nghi&ecirc;n cu sinh Vit Nam ang sng   ngoi &ocirc; Tokyo, tht l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n mng x&atilde; hi facebook. \"C t&ograve;a nh&agrave; nghi&ecirc;n  cu 5 tng ca bn m&igrave;nh rung lc, k&ecirc;u rng rc\".</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"60%\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#63b1b1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Normal\" align=\"center\"><a class=\"Normal\" href=\"http://vnexpress.net/gl/the-gioi/2011/03/song-than-cao-10-met-ap-vao-nhat-ban/page_3.asp\">Video s&oacute;ng thn nh&igrave;n t tr&ecirc;n cao</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><em>AFP</em> cho hay ng t h&ocirc;m nay k&eacute;o theo nhng  t s&oacute;ng thn cao 4 m&eacute;t v&agrave;o b bin &ocirc;ng bc Nht Bn. Ti cng Sensai,  tnh Miyagi, s&oacute;ng thn c&ograve;n l&ecirc;n cao ti 10 m&eacute;t. Truyn h&igrave;nh Nht ph&aacute;t i  h&igrave;nh nh nhng ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave; b s&oacute;ng thn cun tr&ocirc;i. ng bng ti s&acirc;n bay  Sensai ngp nc trong khi h&agrave;ng chc ngi phi ng tr&ecirc;n n&oacute;c ca t&ograve;a  nh&agrave; ch. Trong khi &oacute;, h&atilde;ng tin <em>Kyodo</em> cho bit s&oacute;ng thn cao 7 m&eacute;t p v&agrave;o b bin  tnh Fukushima.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">&Iacute;t nht 10 v ha hon c ghi nhn  Tokyo, <em>AFP</em> a tin. Nhiu t&ograve;a nh&agrave; rung chuyn trong v&agrave;i ph&uacute;t. H thng t&agrave;u in  ngm ngng hot ng, ting xe c&ograve;i h&uacute; khp ni c&ograve;n d&acirc;n ch&uacute;ng s t&aacute;n khi  c&aacute;c t&ograve;a nh&agrave;.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/75/5d/tusunami-4.jpg\" border=\"1\" alt=\"Ha hon ti mt nh&agrave; m&aacute;y lc du gn Tokyo sau ng t. nh: AP.\" width=\"480\" height=\"269\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Image\">Ha hon ti mt nh&agrave; m&aacute;y lc du  &ocirc;ng Tokyo sau ng t. nh: <em>AFP</em>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\"Cha bao gi thy trn ng t ln vy. Tr&ecirc;n tng 9,  rung lc d di,  c  khp ni, m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh xp xung b&agrave;n, cc nc  cng ln\", mt nghi&ecirc;n cu sinh ngi Vit  Nht k. \"Tt c mi ngi  chui ht xung gm b&agrave;n, mt mi t&aacute;i m&eacute;t! My ngi Nht bo cha bao gi  thy trn ln th n&agrave;y\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Osamu Akiya, 46 tui, ang l&agrave;m vic trong vn ph&ograve;ng   Tokyo th&igrave; ng t xy ra. Gi&aacute; s&aacute;ch, m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh b x&ocirc; xung nn nh&agrave;. \"T&ocirc;i  &atilde; chng kin nhiu v ng t ri nhng cha bao gi thy c&oacute; v n&agrave;o  th n&agrave;y\", anh n&oacute;i. \"T&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng bit &ecirc;m nay c&oacute; v nh&agrave; c kh&ocirc;ng na\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Trc &oacute;, Nht Bn a ra cnh b&aacute;o s&oacute;ng thn  mc cao nht, cho rng s&oacute;ng c&oacute; th cao ti 6m.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Chng kho&aacute;n ch&acirc;u &Aacute; ng lot gim gi&aacute; sau th&ocirc;ng tin v  ng t v&agrave; s&oacute;ng thn  Nht khin bu kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; ca th trng vn &atilde;  m m li c&agrave;ng xu th&ecirc;m. Ch s Nikkei ca Nht v&agrave; Hansen ca Hong Kong  st im.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/75/5d/honshu-island.jpg\" border=\"1\" alt=\"nh ca C quan a cht M. T&acirc;m chn ng t (v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n )  ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng o Honshu ca Nht. nh: AFP.\" width=\"300\" height=\"416\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Image\">nh ca C quan a cht M. T&acirc;m chn ng t (v&ograve;ng tr&ograve;n )  ph&iacute;a &ocirc;ng o Honshu ca Nht. nh: AFP.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C quan cnh b&aacute;o s&oacute;ng thn Th&aacute;i B&igrave;nh Dng cng ph&aacute;t  cnh b&aacute;o i vi mt lot c&aacute;c v&ugrave;ng l&atilde;nh th nh &agrave;i Loan, Nga, qun o  Mariana, Guam, Philippines, qun o Marshall, Indonesia, Papua New  Guinea, Nauru, Micronesia v&agrave; Hawaii.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"420\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#92c9c9\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Normal\" align=\"center\"><a class=\"Normal\" href=\"http://vnexpress.net/gl/the-gioi/2011/03/song-than-cao-10-met-ap-vao-nhat-ban/page_2.asp\">Video s&oacute;ng thn p v&agrave;o cng Sendai, &ocirc;ng bc Nht Bn</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ln cui c&ugrave;ng mt trn ng t d di xy ra  Tokyo  l&agrave; v&agrave;o nm 1923 khi cn a chn Kanto V i cp i sinh mng ca  140.000 ngi, a phn l&agrave; trong c&aacute;c v ha hon. Nm 1825, ng t mang  t&ecirc;n Ansei Edo cng khin th&agrave;nh ph n&agrave;y b h hi nhiu. Gn &acirc;y nht,  trn ng t Kobe nm 1995 khin 6.400 ngi cht.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Nm 2004, hn 220.000 ngi thit mng khi a chn  mnh 9,1  Richter p n Indonesia, k&eacute;o theo s&oacute;ng thn t&agrave;n ph&aacute; c&aacute;c khu  vc quanh n  Dng.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><em>Hi Ninh (ngun vnexpress.net)</em><strong><br /></strong></p>','2011-03-11 16:37:16','admin@jobbid.vn',173,1),(12,'nghe-go-captcha-thue-tai-viet-nam','Ngh g Captcha thu ti Vit Nam','http://genk.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/09/examplesoftextcaptchasdb0.jpg','Trong cc cng vic bn thi gian kim tin trc tuyn (MMO), g Captcha thu ang thu ht mt lng khng nh c dn mng Vit Nam theo ui vi mc thu nhp trung bnh t 1,2 n 1,8 triu ng mi thng.','<div style=\"margin: 10px 0pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small; color: #888888;\"><strong> <span id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ContentNews1_lblInitial\">Trong  c&aacute;c  ngh kim tin trc tuyn (MMO), g&otilde; Captcha thu&ecirc; ang thu h&uacute;t mt  lng  kh&ocirc;ng nh c d&acirc;n mng Vit Nam theo ui vi mc thu nhp trung  b&igrave;nh t  1,2 n 1,8 triu ng mi th&aacute;ng.</span></strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">S hu &ocirc;i tay nhanh nhn, sn s&agrave;ng  ngi l trc  m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh nhiu ting ng h, bn &atilde;  t cht  tr th&agrave;nh mt  ngi g&otilde; Captcha chuy&ecirc;n nghip tr&ecirc;n mng o. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n,  c&oacute; l&agrave;m mi bit,  c&ocirc;ng vic kim tin online n&agrave;y chng d nh m.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: small;\">G&otilde; ph&iacute;m kim tin, ngh tuyt vi cho c d&acirc;n mng?</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Captcha l&agrave; h&igrave;nh nh cha on m&atilde; x&aacute;c  nhn gi&uacute;p ph&acirc;n bit i tng ang truy cp l&agrave; ngi hay m&aacute;y. C&ocirc;ng c  rt  hiu qu trong ngn chn h&agrave;nh vi lp t&agrave;i khon din &agrave;n, website,  e-mail  s lng ln nh c&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh t ng.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid; margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://genk.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/09/examplesoftextcaptchasdb0.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> vt qua r&agrave;o chn n&agrave;y, hacker buc  phi nh i  ng nhng ngi g&otilde; thu&ecirc; Captcha  x&aacute;c nhn vic lp t&agrave;i  khon, y  nhanh qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ng k&iacute; h&agrave;ng lot. Vi c th&ugrave; c&ocirc;ng vic,  y&ecirc;u cu ng  tuyn ch &ograve;i hi tc  g&otilde; ph&iacute;m nhanh, thi gian online  nhiu.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Mt cha n mt gi&acirc;y vi t kh&oacute;a <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">&ldquo;g&otilde; Capcha kim tin&rdquo;</span>,   ngi vit nhn c gn 16 ng&agrave;n kt qu tr v t Google, s lng  ln  trong &oacute; l&agrave; c&aacute;c mu tin t&igrave;m ngi g&otilde; Captcha thu&ecirc; ti Vit Nam.  Theo  th&ocirc;ng tin, bn thng c nhn ngay khi li&ecirc;c lc vi ph&iacute;a tuyn  dng  (kh&ocirc;ng cn qua th vic). C&ocirc;ng vic tin h&agrave;nh t xa theo h&igrave;nh thc   online.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid; margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://genk.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/09/Captcha.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Trung b&igrave;nh c g&otilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng 1000  Captcha, ph&iacute;a  tuyn dng cam kt chi tr t 15 n 20 ng&agrave;n ng. Tin  ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n t&iacute;nh  theo u vic thc hin, v&agrave; c thanh to&aacute;n khi t mc  nht nh (v&iacute;  d: 50 ng&agrave;n ng) qua h&igrave;nh thc chuyn khon. Ch&iacute;nh nh  y&ecirc;u cu n  gin, ngh kim tin online n&agrave;y thu h&uacute;t rt &ocirc;ng ngi tham  gia ti Vit  Nam. Mt th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n ca Din &agrave;n tin hc t&acirc;m s: <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">&ldquo;Ngh   g&otilde; Captcha &atilde; c&oacute; t rt l&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n th gii, ti Vit Nam lng ngi   tham gia c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y kh&aacute; nhiu, ch yu l&agrave; c&aacute;c bn hc sinh, sinh   vi&ecirc;n&rdquo;<span style=\"font-style: normal;\">.</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: small;\">C&ocirc;ng vic ca nhng ngi sng v &ecirc;m</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Trong vai k mun th sc vi ngh g&otilde; ph&iacute;m,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GenK.vn</span> c c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n din &agrave;n www. kiemtien... gii thiu n V.H &ndash; nh&acirc;n   vt tng c&oacute; kinh nghim hn mt nm trong ngh g&otilde; Captcha.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Theo V.H, iu u ti&ecirc;n mun nhn nh  l&agrave; ng t  tin v&agrave;o kh nng &aacute;nh m&aacute;y nhanh ca m&igrave;nh. Trong ngh n&agrave;y, k  nng g&otilde; vn  bn cha   &ldquo;n tin&rdquo;. Hu ht c&aacute;c&nbsp;Captcha c to  th&agrave;nh t t hp  ch c&aacute;i, ch s thm ch&iacute; c c&aacute;c k&yacute; t ngu nhi&ecirc;n. Vic  ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh mt  on m&atilde; v&igrave; th &ograve;i hi phi ln m&ograve; kh&aacute; l&acirc;u, kh&ocirc;ng ging  chuyn g&otilde; li  c&aacute;c t c&oacute; ngha.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;<span style=\"font-style: italic;\">Trc  &acirc;y c&ograve;n  d, 2 nm tr li &acirc;y, v&igrave; thng xuy&ecirc;n b vt mt, n&ecirc;n   qu&aacute;i ca c&aacute;c  on m&atilde; ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng tng. C&aacute;c k&yacute; t n hin &aacute;nh  ngi  xem, vic nhm  ln gia c&aacute;c k&yacute; t nh i-l, 0-o... thng xuy&ecirc;n xy ra  vi c&aacute;c tay m  trong ngh. Theo &uacute;ng lut, ch sai mt k&yacute; t, c on  m&atilde; va g&otilde; i  tong&rdquo; - </span>nh&acirc;n vt cho bit th&ecirc;m.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid; margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://genk.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/09/P1020833-copy.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Theo chia s, giai on mi v&agrave;o ngh,  t l g&otilde;  th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ch t v&agrave;i chc Captcha trong mt gi. Quen vic  hn, hiu  qu g&otilde; c&oacute; th n&acirc;ng ti 300 m&atilde;/ gi. Mt ngi c gi  l&agrave;&nbsp;l&agrave;nh ngh&nbsp;c&oacute;  th m bo t l th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng n 400 m&atilde;/ gi hoc&nbsp;thm  ch&iacute; hn. Nh vy,  khi &atilde; c&oacute; kinh nghim, mt ng&agrave;y bn c&oacute; th ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh  t 2000-3000 m&atilde;  (tng ng khong 5-6 gi).</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Tng 1 nm ln ln vi ngh, t tin nm r&otilde; th gii kim tin trc tuyn n&agrave;y, V.H chia s: <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">&ldquo;Ngi   g&otilde; Captcha thu&ecirc;  Vit Nam ch yu hot ng theo hai kiu: h&agrave;nh ngh   t do &ndash; tc l&agrave; l&agrave;m trc tip cho website ca nc ngo&agrave;i nh   www.kolotibab... hoc tham gia v&agrave;o team n&agrave;o &oacute; do ngi trong nc ng   u. Kiu l&agrave;m th hai c chn nhiu hn v&igrave; thun li cho vic nhn   tin c&ocirc;ng&rdquo;<span style=\"font-style: normal;\">.</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Vi h&igrave;nh thc hot ng theo nh&oacute;m,  ngi g&otilde; thu&ecirc;  c tham gia v&agrave;o c&aacute;c d &aacute;n do &ocirc;ng ch ch o (ngi n&agrave;y  ng ra i  din &nbsp;hp&nbsp;ng vi&nbsp;c&aacute;c t chc nc ngo&agrave;i). Trong nh&oacute;m  thng&nbsp;chia  tip ra ngi g&otilde; thu&ecirc;, ngi qun l&yacute; vi mc tr c&ocirc;ng ch&ecirc;nh  lch nhau  kh&ocirc;ng nhiu.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid; margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://genk.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/09/89186f4d9be62.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Thng th&igrave; sau khong&nbsp;thi gian&nbsp;h&agrave;nh  ngh&nbsp;nht  nh, bn s c tr mc tin c&ocirc;ng cao hn ban u (hoc  nhn c&aacute;c khon  hoa hng tng ng). Nhng nhng nh&oacute;m/ t chc &aacute;p dng  c ch n&agrave;y  cng quy nh kht khe v nh lng c&ocirc;ng vic. Buc ngi  tham gia phi  cam kt ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh s lng Captcha ti thiu trong ng&agrave;y.  Nu &iacute;t hn,  tin kh&ocirc;ng c thanh to&aacute;n, hoc chu pht.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&aacute;ng n&oacute;i hn, qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh g&otilde; Captcha  phi tin h&agrave;nh  song song vi hot ng ca chng tr&igrave;nh do hacker iu  khin trc tip.  Do l&agrave;m ch yu vi c&aacute;c t chc nc ngo&agrave;i n&ecirc;n hu ht  d&acirc;n trong ngh   Vit Nam chu cnh &ldquo;lch m&uacute;i gi&rdquo;.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid; margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://genk.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/09/P1020844.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Mt ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vic ca V.H bt u v&agrave;o  l&uacute;c 12  gi&nbsp;&ecirc;m v&agrave; k&eacute;o d&agrave;i n gn s&aacute;ng (c&oacute; khi&nbsp;n 7,8 ting li&ecirc;n  tc)&nbsp;- &acirc;y  cng l&agrave; khung gi m&agrave; d&acirc;n trong ngh hot ng s&ocirc;i ni nht,  do c&aacute;c m&atilde;  Captcha mi tr v nhanh, li&ecirc;n tc. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, &oacute; l&agrave; khi  thun li,  nhng&nbsp;cng nhiu&nbsp;l&uacute;c h thng hot ng thiu n nh.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Nhiu thi im, ch m&atilde;i chng thy  h&igrave;nh nh mi  n&agrave;o xut hin, c&oacute; l&uacute;c li tr v dn dp kh&ocirc;ng x l&yacute; kp,  gp trc trc  trong vic gi li kt qu... cng l&agrave;m gi&aacute;n on &aacute;ng k  c&ocirc;ng vic ca  nhiu ngi m&agrave; V.H&nbsp;c&nbsp;bit.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: small;\">G&otilde; Captcha thu&ecirc;, c chng nhiu m&agrave; mt kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Chng cn th, bn c&oacute; th thy ngay  vi c&ocirc;ng vic  mt ngi g&otilde; Captcha thu&ecirc;&nbsp;ti Vit Nam&nbsp;ang tham gia  th&igrave;&nbsp;sc khe l&agrave; yu  t u ti&ecirc;n b nh hng. Thay i gi gic sinh  hot, l&agrave;m vic ch yu  v &ecirc;m, ngi l trc m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh vi mc  tp  trung cao ... s ph&aacute;t  sinh h&agrave;ng lot bnh l&yacute; v mt, ct sng, thn  kinh... v l&acirc;u d&agrave;i hu qu  thng nghi&ecirc;m trng.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ngo&agrave;i ra, nu th t&iacute;nh tr&ecirc;n mc  l&agrave;m  vic trung  b&igrave;nh (b qua vn  h thng thiu n nh) khong  2000-3000 m&atilde;/ ng&agrave;y  (5-6 ting), bn c nhn t 40 n 60 ng&agrave;n ng/  ng&agrave;y, mt th&aacute;ng thu  nhp v&agrave;o khong 1,2 n 1,8 triu ng.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Con s n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng cao hn ngh gia s  hay bi b&agrave;n m&agrave;  sinh vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; th l&agrave;m  bt c &acirc;u. Thm ch&iacute;, t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n  tr&ecirc;n &atilde; l i  hn chi ph&iacute; tin in, tin internet phi chi tr cho mi  ting l&agrave;m vic  online (kh&ocirc;ng nh).</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Chc hn&nbsp;v&igrave; nhng l&yacute; do  tr&ecirc;n m&agrave; V.H  &atilde; &ldquo;gii  ngh&rdquo; sau hn 1 nm th sc, gn b&oacute; vi ngh kh&aacute; l&acirc;u, anh  chng kin  nhiu bn tr t&igrave;m n ri li ra i v&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng chu ni &aacute;p lc  c&ocirc;ng vic.  Ngh&nbsp;o&nbsp;kim c tin tht, y&ecirc;u cu n gin l&agrave; th nhng  cng khin  ngi ta phi &aacute;nh i qu&aacute; nhiu, &ldquo;g&otilde; Captcha thu&ecirc;&rdquo; vn  chng d n nh  ngi ta vn tng?</span></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>Theo genk</em></span></p>','2011-03-13 19:49:23','admin@jobbid.vn',722,1),(13,'viet-blog-thue-nghe-ban-thoi-gian-cho-teen','Vit blog thu - ngh bn thi gian cho teen','http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/08/03/44c040810DSvietblog01.jpg','Cng vic bn thi gian - vit blog chng bao gi li thi c, khng ch th m n li cng tr nn thng dng v thu ht c nhiu bn tr.','<p class=\"sapo\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">C&ocirc;ng vic vit blog chng bao gi li thi c, kh&ocirc;ng ch th m&agrave; n&oacute; li c&agrave;ng tr n&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng dng v&agrave; thu h&uacute;t c nhiu bn tr.</span></strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"content\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&oacute; l&agrave; quy tr&igrave;nh chung ca vic  thu&ecirc; mt blogger vit vi mc &iacute;ch qung b&aacute;, hoc i s&acirc;u ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch, hoc  ph&ecirc; ph&aacute;n mt sn phm, dch v, hay n gin l&agrave; mt s kin n&agrave;o &oacute;  trong i sng. C&aacute;c teen c&oacute; mun &ldquo;khi nghip&rdquo; bng h&igrave;nh thc vit l&aacute;ch  n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng? D&ugrave; sao, &acirc;y cng l&agrave; bc m  tr th&agrave;nh mt ngi a tin,  hay mt nh&agrave; b&aacute;o trong tng lai.</span></p>\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: small;\">Bt u t vic kim tin</span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: small;\">\n<div><img style=\"margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/08/03/44c040810DSvietblog01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" align=\"center\" /></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: normal;\">Nu vit theo c&aacute;ch suy ngh ca bn th&acirc;n vi ni dung tht din t bit &acirc;u bn s nhn c mt m&oacute;n tin thng nho nh.</span></div>\n</span>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Blog l&agrave; ni ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh c&oacute; th vit ra tt c mi suy  ngh nu mun. Ph&agrave;n n&agrave;n v mt &yacute; tng dch v ti ca&nbsp;mt sn phm  n&agrave;o&nbsp;y&nbsp;hay x&uacute;c ng v mt b phim, ng&uacute;ng nguy vi mt loi sa va  c b&aacute;n ra th trng... &oacute; l&agrave; c hi kim tin ln cho c&aacute;c teen  nc  ngo&agrave;i. Mt teen blogger  <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">M </span>&atilde;&nbsp;tng&nbsp;c mt h&atilde;ng nc gii kh&aacute;t ni ting&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">7Up</span> gi n thng c&ocirc;ng khi g&oacute;p phn &ldquo;khen ngi&rdquo; mt sn phm mi ca h&atilde;ng n&agrave;y.   bit bn y &atilde; bt ng ra sao.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">C&ograve;n i vi nhng bn&nbsp;teen&nbsp; nc&nbsp;ta&nbsp;th&igrave; sao nh? Vi  nhng bn c&oacute; k nng ting Anh v&agrave; kh nng ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch tt, th&igrave; tht  chng c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;o ph&ugrave; hp hn. Ban ng&agrave;y i hc, bui ti c v&agrave;  nghi&ecirc;n cu vit mt blog tht  i, dn dn mi ngi s bit ti bn,  v&agrave; bit &acirc;u y, vi ch&uacute;t may mn, trong t&agrave;i khon s c&oacute; &ldquo;tin &ocirc;&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Vi nhng blogger <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Vit</span>,  th&igrave; i sng c&oacute; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng nhiu iu cho bn kh&aacute;m ph&aacute;. Va  luyn tay  ngh vit l&aacute;ch! Va luyn mt quan s&aacute;t, va luyn kh nng x l&iacute; nhanh!  Th vit v <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">S&agrave;i G&ograve;n </span>v &ecirc;m, hay nh&igrave;n nhn v mt <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">S&agrave;i G&ograve;n</span> c in va b p n&aacute;t, hay v mt <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">H&agrave; Ni </span>chng  c&ograve;n m&agrave;u xa c&hellip; Th&ecirc;m mt v&agrave;i bc nh c th v&agrave; s&aacute;t sao, vy l&agrave; ch&uacute;ng  m&igrave;nh va ghi li c mt khonh khc &ldquo;lch s&rdquo;m&agrave; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n bng cm x&uacute;c  ri&ecirc;ng y nh&eacute;.</span></p>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hay th ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch dch v a  n tn nh&agrave; ca <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">KFC,</span> hay tr t&agrave;i l&agrave;m mt nh&agrave; gi&aacute;m nh sa, hay i post comment gii thiu  sn phm online&hellip; Tt c nhng nhn x&eacute;t hu &iacute;ch ti th trng <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Vit Nam </span>tr&ecirc;n  tt c mi mt h&agrave;ng u c ghi nhn. Vit v n&oacute; bng ch&iacute;nh suy ngh  ca bn s nhanh ch&oacute;ng c &ldquo;truyn ming&rdquo; hn vic xem mt qung c&aacute;o  tr&ecirc;n truyn h&igrave;nh.</span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Cho c&aacute;c Teen ham th&iacute;ch ting Anh v&agrave; kim tin, c&aacute;c bn th v&agrave;o a ch n&agrave;y nh&eacute;: <a href=\"http://www.blog-republic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.blog-republic.com</a> hay <a href=\"https://payperpost.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://payperpost.com</a><a href=\"https://payperpost.com/\">. </a>  &acirc;y tha h c hi cho c&aacute;c bn &ldquo;tung chng&rdquo; ting Anh v&agrave; kh nng ph&acirc;n  t&iacute;ch ca m&igrave;nh. Ch  cn vit rt a dng, t in thoi n du lch,  t sc khe n m&oacute;n n &hellip;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: small;\">V&agrave; kt qu c&ograve;n nhiu hn th</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Vit blog thu&ecirc; s cho ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh nhiu hn l&agrave; nhng  g&igrave; ta tng. Kin thc s mt ng&agrave;y mt lp y l&ecirc;n. S cnh tranh trong  t duy s t khng nh v tr&iacute; ca teen blogger. S cnh tranh y s  gi&uacute;p ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh c&oacute; th&ecirc;m nhiu ngi bn cc cool. Cha ht, nhng phn  hi a chiu t c&aacute;c comment s cho ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh nhiu &yacute; tng v&agrave; c&oacute; khi l&agrave;  &ldquo;git thon th&oacute;t&rdquo; y ch.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">V&agrave; nhiu hn th na. &Yacute; tng dn dn c bt ra  ngay tp t trong u, v&igrave; ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh &atilde; t r&egrave;n luyn c th&oacute;i quen quan  s&aacute;t ri m&agrave;. G&oacute;c nh&igrave;n v s vic, s vt s theo &oacute; m&agrave; sc cnh hn v&agrave;  nhiu mt hn.</span></p>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Nu ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh ham th&iacute;ch, s thy &acirc;y l&agrave; mt dng  thc marketing ni bt b&acirc;y gi, hay n&oacute;i c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c l&agrave; mt h&igrave;nh thc PR c&oacute;  li &ldquo;kh&ocirc;ng tng tng ni&rdquo;. Nu i s&acirc;u v&agrave;o na, s thy nhng loi  h&igrave;nh blog thu&ecirc; kh&aacute;c na, thm ch&iacute; c&oacute; c vic &ldquo;&oacute;ng vai&rdquo; mt nh&acirc;n vt n&agrave;o  &oacute; v&agrave; chm lo tm tt cho blog ca h kia.</span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/08/03/545040810DSvietblog04.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" align=\"center\" /></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-style: italic; font-size: small;\">Vit blog kh&ocirc;ng ch l&agrave; mt ngh thu h&uacute;t c&aacute;c bn tr t rt l&acirc;u, m&agrave; n&oacute; c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng bao gi li thi c.</span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Nhng vit blog th&igrave; phi c&oacute; thi gian v&agrave; cng cn r&egrave;n  gia li l  truyn cm  thu h&uacute;t ngi c n vi &ldquo;t b&aacute;o&rdquo; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n  ca m&igrave;nh na y. Nu h&ocirc;m nay ging vn ca ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh cha  , th&igrave;  hc tp t nhng b&agrave;i b&aacute;o kh&aacute;c s gi&uacute;p &ldquo;tng tr&igrave;nh&rdquo; ngay. Sau mt thi  gian &ldquo;chy nc r&uacute;t&rdquo; vi c&aacute;c deadline ca ngi t h&agrave;ng, ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh tha  h kim so&aacute;t thi gian ung dung m&agrave; chng s &ldquo;vt ch&acirc;n l&ecirc;n c na&rdquo;. Tht  c&oacute; &iacute;ch phi kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bc v&agrave;o mt ngh mi, ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh s kh&ocirc;ng khi vp  phi nhng mt tr&aacute;i ca n&oacute;. Nhng h&atilde;y th xem nh&eacute;, mi th c&ograve;n ch i  trc mt ch&uacute;ng m&igrave;nh m&agrave;, phi kh&ocirc;ng?</span></p>\n</div>','2011-03-14 22:37:55','admin@jobbid.vn',269,1),(15,'mot-cong-viec-part-time-thu-vi!','Mt cng vic part time th v!','http://www2.vietbao.vn/images/viet3/viec_lam/30196146_cheerer2.jpg','Trong cc tr chi truyn hnh, hoc cc s kin vn ha ta thng bt gp hnh nh nhng bn tr c v rt nhit tnh, bi bn v chuyn nghip. H l nhng hot no vin lm part time - nhng ngi truyn la cho cc showgame.','<p><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"Mt c&ocirc;ng vic parttime th&uacute; v\" src=\"http://www2.vietbao.vn/images/viet3/viec_lam/30196146_cheerer2.jpg\" alt=\"Mt c&ocirc;ng vic parttime th&uacute; v\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" /><span style=\"color: #888888;\">Trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; chi truyn h&igrave;nh, hoc c&aacute;c s kin vn h&oacute;a ta thng bt gp h&igrave;nh nh nhng bn tr c v rt nhit t&igrave;nh, b&agrave;i bn v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n nghip. H l&agrave; nhng hot n&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n - nhng ngi &ldquo;truyn la&rdquo; cho c&aacute;c showgame.</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Hai nm tr li &acirc;y c coi l&agrave; s b&ugrave;ng n ca c&aacute;c showgame tr&ecirc;n truyn h&igrave;nh, c&aacute;c s kin do c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty t chc. V&agrave;  cho c&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y thc s s&ocirc;i ng, hp dn, kh&ocirc;ng th thiu c h&igrave;nh nh ca i c v.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"> li n tng cho ngi xem truyn h&igrave;nh trong mi chng tr&igrave;nh, ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;c i chi c&ograve;n l&agrave; h&igrave;nh nh ca nhng kh&aacute;n gi nhit t&igrave;nh ph&iacute;a di h&ograve; reo, tay cm nhng qu b&ocirc;ng lc l theo iu nhc  c v sut bui cho nhng ngi chi truyn h&igrave;nh.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; nhng hot n&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n hay c&ograve;n gi l&agrave;&nbsp;<em>cheerer</em>, nhng ngi \"truyn la\"  to ra kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; vui ti, phn kh&iacute;ch trong c&aacute;c showgame. Hin nay, l&agrave;m hot n&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n cng l&agrave; mt c&ocirc;ng vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m c rt nhiu bn tr la chn.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">n tng ca kh&aacute;n gi khi i xem quay chng tr&igrave;