;u thng, lp i lp li c&acirc;u em y&ecirc;u c&ocirc; nhiu lm v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th sng  thiu c&ocirc;&hellip; khin m&igrave;nh rt ng ng&agrave;ng&rdquo;, Ng&acirc;n k. Sau h&ocirc;m &oacute;, c&ocirc; gia s vn  c gng i dy nhng s hc tr&ograve; nm np, ch mong sao cho nhanh ht  th&aacute;ng  ngh.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">i vi nhiu n sinh  S&agrave;i G&ograve;n, PG (Promotion Girl)  l&agrave; ngh part - time l&yacute; tng. &ldquo;Nguy&ecirc;n tc v&agrave;ng ca ngh l&agrave; lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n  ci d&ugrave; c&oacute; ng 8 ting hay nhn nhng li l tr&ecirc;u chc th&ocirc; thin... c  bit, nhng ngi &agrave;n &ocirc;ng t gi&agrave; n tr u phi gi l&agrave; anh&rdquo;, Ngc,  sinh vi&ecirc;n i hc Khoa hc x&atilde; hi v&agrave; nh&acirc;n vn chia s.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Chng phi ng&agrave;y n&agrave;o cng c&oacute; &ldquo;s&ocirc;&rdquo;  l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m nhng mi  th&aacute;ng, t PG hi ch, PG Game, tip th bia... Ngc cng &atilde; kim th&ecirc;m  khong 3 triu  trang tri cho vic hc. Nhng  c&oacute; c con s n&agrave;y,  c&ocirc; cng &atilde; nhiu ln ri nc mt.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">&ldquo;Mc nhng b trang phc ngn cn trc h&agrave;ng trm con  mt lu&ocirc;n chm ch&uacute; h&igrave;nh v&agrave;o nhng phn nhy cm&hellip; khin m&igrave;nh &ocirc;i khi a  nc mt&rdquo;, c&ocirc; g&aacute;i chia s.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">L&ecirc; Thu, sinh vi&ecirc;n trng Lut TP HCM cng c&oacute; &ocirc;i ln  ri v&agrave;o trng th&aacute;i &ldquo;d ci d kh&oacute;c&rdquo; khi nhn l&agrave;m PG cho mt Game  Online. ang ci ti r&oacute;i, nh&uacute;n nhy theo ting nhc, mt g&atilde; thanh ni&ecirc;n  d&iacute; b mt nham nh v&agrave;o s&aacute;t \"khu vc nhy cm\" ca Thu, li c&ograve;n a tay  vut &ugrave;i c&ocirc; nhng Thu ch \"ch bit cn rng chu ng m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m phn  ph&aacute;o\". C&oacute; ln, c&ocirc; li nhn c mnh giy vi nhng d&ograve;ng ch: \"Xong  chng tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y, i vi anh nh&eacute;, chc chn em s c&oacute; th&ecirc;m nhiu tin\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Vy, sinh vi&ecirc;n i hc Khoa hc T nhi&ecirc;n cho bit, c&oacute;  thi gian c&ocirc; \"ph&aacute;t i&ecirc;n v&igrave; tin nhn in thoi\". Trong mt ln tip th,  c&ocirc; cng gp phi mt kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng \"nham nh\". Chng bit bng c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o,  anh ta c&oacute; c s in thoi v&agrave; li&ecirc;n tc gi c&aacute;c tin nhn bt k ng&agrave;y  &ecirc;m, i loi nh: &ldquo;Em p qu&aacute; cho anh l&agrave;m quen&rdquo;, &ldquo;i vi anh kh&ocirc;ng em&rdquo;,  hay &ldquo;ngc em to qu&aacute;&rdquo;&hellip;</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tuy vy, c&ocirc; n sinh n&agrave;y cng nh&igrave;n nhn, d&ugrave; c&oacute; lm  nhng lo toan v&agrave; nhng vui bun trong c&ocirc;ng vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m, nhng ch&iacute;nh  nhng iu &oacute; s l&agrave; h&agrave;nh trang kin thc, kinh nghim thc t v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng  qu&yacute; b&aacute;u cho c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n trc khi bc v&agrave;o i.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><strong>Minh Th&nbsp;</strong><em> (theo vnexpress.net)</em><strong><br /></strong></p>','2011-03-18 16:37:46','admin@jobbid.vn',323,1),(17,'sinh-vien-tinh-le-khat-viec-lam-them','Sinh vin tnh l kht vic lm thm','http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2011/03/18/IMG_0144.jpg','S tin m gia nh  qu gi ln khng y cho cc khon chi tiu hng thng ti thnh ph, khi m gi c tng ln hng ngy. Khng cn cch no khc nhiu sinh vin (SV) ti tnh l tm vic  lm thm lm bn thi gian nhng qu cht vt','<div class=\"fon33 mt1\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong>(D&acirc;n tr&iacute;) - S tin m&agrave; gia &igrave;nh  qu&ecirc; gi l&ecirc;n  kh&ocirc;ng y cho c&aacute;c khon chi ti&ecirc;u h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng ti th&agrave;nh ph, khi m&agrave; gi&aacute; c  tng l&ecirc;n h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y. Kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n (SV) ti  tnh l t&igrave;m vic  <a title=\"l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m l&agrave;m b&aacute;n thi gian\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m l&agrave;m b&aacute;n thi gian</a> nhng qu&aacute; cht vt&hellip;</strong></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&ldquo; mt&rdquo; t&igrave;m vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m</span>&nbsp;</div>\n<p> chng chi vi cuc sng cht vt ni th th&agrave;nh khi m&agrave; gi&aacute; c  tng, nhiu SV theo hc c&aacute;c trng i hc, Cao ng tr&ecirc;n a b&agrave;n th&agrave;nh  ph Ph L&yacute; (H&agrave; Nam)  x&ocirc; i t&igrave;m vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m  kim tin trang tri  cuc sng v&agrave; hc tp.</p>\n<div>Bn Li Th Tho Vy, SV trng C Ph&aacute;t thanh Truyn h&igrave;nh 1 t&acirc;m s:  &ldquo;Nm ngo&aacute;i tr v trc th&igrave; c&ograve;n  ch k t sau Tt, c bit l&agrave; t h&ocirc;m  xng du tng gi&aacute; th&igrave; mi th u tng theo nh gi&aacute; ph&ograve;ng tr, in  nc &hellip;u tng theo. &ldquo;Lng&rdquo; h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng b m gi l&ecirc;n th&igrave; vn nh trc  n&ecirc;n chi ti&ecirc;u kh&ocirc;ng , em &atilde; t&iacute;nh t&igrave;m vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m nhng  &acirc;y i t&igrave;m  vic l&agrave;m ph&ugrave; hp kh&oacute; qu&aacute;, em t&igrave;m my h&ocirc;m ri vn cha c&oacute; vic g&igrave;&rdquo;.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><img style=\"margin: 5px;\" src=\"http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2011/03/18/IMG_0144.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" align=\"center\" /></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;\">Nhiu SV may mn lm mi t&igrave;m c ch l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m</span>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Kh&aacute;c xa vi H&agrave; Ni v&agrave; mt s th&agrave;nh ph ln kh&aacute;c, SV hc tp  Ph  L&yacute; rt kh&oacute; t&igrave;m cho m&igrave;nh mt c&ocirc;ng vic ph&ugrave; hp  l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m. V mt bun  ru v&agrave; mt mi sau hai ng&agrave;y p xe p rong rui tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ng&otilde; ph  t&igrave;m  vic, bn Trn Phng Ngc, SV C s 2, trng H C&ocirc;ng nghip H&agrave; Ni  n&oacute;i:</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&ldquo;&atilde; hai h&ocirc;m nay em p xe i gn nh khp c&aacute;c con ng tr&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh  ph, v&agrave;o c&aacute;c qu&aacute;n c&agrave; ph&ecirc;, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, qu&aacute;n n  hi nhng tt c u  kh&ocirc;ng tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n na. Mt lm, ng&agrave;y mai em i th&ecirc;m h&ocirc;m na m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng  t&igrave;m c th&igrave; th&ocirc;i&rdquo;.</div>\n<p>&ldquo;Trc &acirc;y, mi th&aacute;ng gia &igrave;nh gi cho 1,3 - 1,6 triu ng, chi ti&ecirc;u  tit kim h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng cng tm . Nhng gn &acirc;y gi&aacute; c mi th u tng  n&ecirc;n d&ugrave; tit kim th n&agrave;o cng kh&ocirc;ng . M&agrave; c xin th&ecirc;m b m th&igrave; cng  kh&oacute;, v&igrave; ho&agrave;n cnh gia &igrave;nh  qu&ecirc; cng kh&oacute; khn. C&aacute;ch tt nht l&agrave; phi i  l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m&rdquo;, &oacute; l&agrave; t&acirc;m s chung ca rt nhiu SV.</p>\n<div>Cha bao gi  th&agrave;nh ph Ph L&yacute; li c&oacute; nhiu SV i t&igrave;m vic l&agrave;m  th&ecirc;m nh hin nay. Va ct tm bng hiu vit my ch s s&agrave;i th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o  tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n qun &aacute;o, b&agrave; Phm Th Trung - mt ch ca h&agrave;ng shop  qun &aacute;o tr&ecirc;n ng L&ecirc; C&ocirc;ng Thanh, th&agrave;nh ph Ph L&yacute; n&oacute;i:</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&ldquo;T&ocirc;i mi ng bin tuyn nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n cha c mt ng&agrave;y &atilde; c&oacute; my  chc em SV n hi vic. T&ocirc;i cn tuyn c&oacute; hai ngi n&ecirc;n &atilde;  t h&ocirc;m  qua, nhng bn qu&aacute; cha ct c bin th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o n&ecirc;n mi s&aacute;ng sm nay &atilde;  c&oacute; my em qua hi ri, b&acirc;y gi phi ct i kh&ocirc;ng mt c&ocirc;ng th&ecirc;m nhiu  ngi v&agrave;o hi&rdquo;.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div><img src=\"http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2011/03/18/IMG_0004.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" align=\"center\" /></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; font-size: 10pt;\">Gi&aacute;&nbsp;c tng khin nhiu&nbsp;SV rt cht vt.</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Nai lng l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m nhng&hellip;nhn lng &ldquo;b&egrave;o&rdquo;</span></p>\n<div>C&ocirc;ng vic d t&igrave;m v&agrave; ph&ugrave; hp nht ca SV &oacute; l&agrave; i gia s, nhng   Ph L&yacute; c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y rt &iacute;t. Quanh i qun li th&igrave; SV cng ch c&oacute; th  l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m nhng vic nh b&aacute;n qu&aacute;n c&agrave; ph&ecirc;, phc v nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, qu&aacute;n n; ca  h&agrave;ng qun &aacute;o. &atilde; th mc lng cng kh&aacute; b&egrave;o bt v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng xng &aacute;ng vi  sc lc, thi gian m&agrave; nhng SV n&agrave;y b ra.</div>\n<p>V Th Tho, SV trng C Thu li Bc B i l&agrave;m cho mt nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng n  tr&ecirc;n ng Nguyn Vit Xu&acirc;n t&acirc;m s: &ldquo;Em l&agrave;m ca t 13h -22h, mi th&aacute;ng  c 600.000. C&ocirc;ng vic t bng b&ecirc; cho n ra b&aacute;t em u c&oacute; phn. &atilde;  th nhng l&uacute;c m au t xut xin ngh nhng ch qu&aacute;n kh&ocirc;ng cho v&agrave; nu  c&oacute; th&igrave; c&ograve;n b tr lng na. N&oacute;i chung l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; th&aacute;ng n&agrave;o c nhn   600.000 c&rdquo;.</p>\n<div>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng phi SV n&agrave;o t&igrave;m c vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m cng bt vt v  hn, m&agrave; vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m li nh hng rt ln n qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh hc tp. Nhng  SV i l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m dng nh phi cng sc ra  vt qua.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Nhiu khi thi kho&aacute; biu thay i, nhiu SV &agrave;nh phi chp nhn  ngh hc  i l&agrave;m cho &uacute;ng lch kh&ocirc;ng ngi ta li cho ngh vic. &oacute; l&agrave;  cha k nhng SV n l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m ti c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng thng gp nhiu chuyn  phin phc. Nhng l&uacute;c nh th cng &agrave;nh chp nhn kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m ph&agrave;n n&agrave;n nu  kh&ocirc;ng mun ngh vic.</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Nguyn Hi - Duy Tuy&ecirc;n </span><em>(theo dantri.com.vn)</em><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><br /></span></p>','2011-03-21 22:29:51','admin@jobbid.vn',266,1),(18,'nghe-pa-cho-nguoi-khuyet-tat','Ngh PA cho ngi khuyt tt','http://222.255.28.57:2020/Upload/Image/2011/3/8/08032011160220.jpg','Cc bn sinh vin, c sc khe, lm vic nghim tc, hiu v quyn sng c lp ca ngi khuyt tt (NKT) v tham gia cc t tp hun ca Trung tm Sng c lp H Ni, nu mun s c trong tay mnh c hi  tr thnh mt PA vi mc lng t 1,3 triu  2,6 triu ng/thng.','<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"Ngh PA cho ngi khuyt tt\" src=\"http://222.255.28.57:2020/Upload/Image/2011/3/8/08032011160220.jpg\" alt=\"Ngh PA cho ngi khuyt tt\" width=\"300\" height=\"232\" /></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #888888;\">C&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n, c&oacute; sc khe, l&agrave;m vic nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c, hiu v quyn sng c lp ca ngi khuyt tt (NKT) v&agrave; tham gia c&aacute;c t tp hun ca Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp H&agrave; Ni, nu mun s c&oacute; trong tay m&igrave;nh c hi  tr th&agrave;nh mt PA vi mc lng t 1,3 triu &ndash; 2,6 triu ng/th&aacute;ng.</span></strong><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><br />Ngh PA</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">PA (Personal Assistance - Ngi tr  gi&uacute;p c&aacute; nh&acirc;n) l&agrave; mt ngh ti Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp c&oacute; nhim v gi&uacute;p  NKT h&ograve;a nhp cng ng. PA kh&aacute;c vi nhng t&igrave;nh nguyn vi&ecirc;n nh th&ocirc;ng  thng ta vn thy. T&igrave;nh nguyn vi&ecirc;n l&agrave;m vic tr&ecirc;n tinh thn t nguyn  kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ch . PA cng kh&ocirc;ng hn l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic chm s&oacute;c ngi bnh nh  nhng ngi gi&uacute;p vic trong bnh vin hay l&agrave;m m&agrave; l&agrave; mt c&ocirc;ng vic ho&agrave;n  to&agrave;n kh&aacute;c. PA ti Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp H&agrave; Ni l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng vic gi&uacute;p   cho c&aacute; nh&acirc;n NKT trong vic sinh hot h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y nh i li, v sinh, thay  qun &aacute;o, nu n... c bit, PA kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m vic nh&agrave; thng xuy&ecirc;n cho c  gia &igrave;nh m&agrave; l&agrave; ngi h tr c&aacute; nh&acirc;n NKT  h c&oacute; th t ch, t quyt  trong cuc sng v&agrave; thc hin c quyn con ngi ca m&igrave;nh.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Gi&aacute;m c D &aacute;n Sng c lp, ch  Nguyn Hng H&agrave; cho bit, t khi ra i nm 2009 n nay, &atilde; c&oacute; tr&ecirc;n 80  bn sinh vi&ecirc;n ng k&yacute; tham gia l&agrave;m PA cho Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp H&agrave; Ni.  Theo ch H&agrave; th&igrave; &acirc;y l&agrave; mt c&ocirc;ng vic rt ph&ugrave; hp vi c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n  v&igrave; thi gian l&agrave;m vic rt linh ng, c&oacute; th <a title=\"l&agrave;m vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">l&agrave;m vic b&aacute;n thi gian</a> (<a title=\"part-time\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">part-time</a>) vi c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n ang i hc hoc l&agrave;m c ng&agrave;y  (full-time) vi nhng sinh vi&ecirc;n mi tt nghip nhng cha xin c vic  ph&ugrave; hp vi ng&agrave;nh hc ca m&igrave;nh. &ldquo;Sinh vi&ecirc;n l&agrave; nhng ngi tr tui n&ecirc;n  rt nng ng v&agrave; hot b&aacute;t, th&iacute;ch kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; v&agrave; giao lu. C&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y l&agrave;m  tng c hi tri nghim cuc sng. Bn sinh vi&ecirc;n n&agrave;o theo c ngh PA  th&igrave; kinh nghim thc t cng nh s r&egrave;n luyn trong ngh n&agrave;y s rt  thun li cho cuc sng v sau n&agrave;y ca h&rdquo;. Ch H&agrave; chia s v ngh PA.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Trnh Duy Thun, qu&ecirc; Thanh H&oacute;a l&agrave; mt  PA &atilde; c&oacute; gn mt nm kinh nghim. Thun t&acirc;m s l&agrave; bn mi tt nghip  Khoa Sa cha &ocirc; t&ocirc; ti Trung t&acirc;m Dy ngh Thanh Xu&acirc;n v&agrave; hin ang l&agrave;m  marketing cho mt c&ocirc;ng ty n&ecirc;n bn kh&aacute; rnh ri v thi gian. T&igrave;nh c qua  ngi bn th&acirc;n, Thun bit ti c&ocirc;ng vic PA ti Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp  H&agrave; Ni s 42 Kim M&atilde; Thng, H&agrave; Ni n&ecirc;n gi n tham gia. Sau khi tri  qua c&aacute;c kh&oacute;a hun luyn, &agrave;o to ca trung t&acirc;m, Thun c c l&agrave;m PA cho  bn Ph&iacute; Quang Huy  ph Khng Thng, H&agrave; Ni. Thun cho bit, ban u  bn cng cm thy s s khi ln u tip x&uacute;c vi NKT. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, sau mt  thi gian Thun &atilde; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n thay i quan nim &oacute; v&agrave; tr th&agrave;nh mt  ngi bn t&acirc;m u &yacute; hp vi Huy t l&uacute;c n&agrave;o kh&ocirc;ng hay. &ldquo;Nhng NKT h cng  c&oacute; m c, c&oacute; kh&aacute;t khao nh bao ngi b&igrave;nh thng kh&aacute;c, sng c&ugrave;ng vi  h thi gian qua, ngo&agrave;i vic c hng lng 1,3 triu ng/th&aacute;ng m&igrave;nh  c&ograve;n hc hi c t h rt nhiu kinh nghim, l&yacute; tng cho cuc sng ca  m&igrave;nh sau n&agrave;y. V&agrave; iu &aacute;ng qu&yacute; nht l&agrave; m&igrave;nh hiu c t&acirc;m t, suy ngh  v cuc sng ca NKT hn&rdquo;. Thun bc bch.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Qua t&igrave;m hiu ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i  nhn thy hu ht nhng ngi tham gia c&ocirc;ng vic PA u l&agrave; c&aacute;c bn sinh  vi&ecirc;n ang hc ti c&aacute;c trng c&oacute; tr s ti H&agrave; Ni nh: i hc  KHXH&amp;NV, i hc Lao ng x&atilde; hi, Hc vin B&aacute;o ch&iacute; v&agrave; Tuy&ecirc;n truyn,  i hc C&ocirc;ng nghip... B&igrave;nh thng, nu c nhn v&agrave;o l&agrave;m PA ti Trung  t&acirc;m Sng c lp, c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n s c tr 10.000 ng/gi vi hai  th&aacute;ng th vic u v&agrave; 13.000 ng/gi sau khi c k&yacute; hp ng ch&iacute;nh  thc. Thi gian l&agrave;m vic part-time ti a l&agrave; 4 ting/ng&agrave;y v&agrave; 8  ting/ng&agrave;y vi full-time. Nh vy, mt th&aacute;ng l&agrave;m vic b&aacute;n thi gian mt  PA thu nhp c hn 1,35 triu ng, c&ograve;n i vi nhng ngi l&agrave;m vic  c ng&agrave;y s l&agrave; 2,7 triu ng/th&aacute;ng, mt s tin kh&ocirc;ng nh i vi c&aacute;c  bn sinh vi&ecirc;n.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Trng th&agrave;nh t ngh PA</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> </span></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"2\" width=\"285\" align=\"right\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td bgcolor=\"#fffcc0\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>Ch Nguyn Hng H&agrave; &ndash;  Gi&aacute;m c Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp: &ldquo;&atilde; c&oacute; nhiu &yacute; kin trong mt cuc hi  tho ca ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c x&atilde; hi  ngh c&ocirc;ng nhn PA l&agrave; mt ngh chuy&ecirc;n  nghip, ging nh ngh c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c x&atilde; hi. Thc cht ngh n&agrave;y  c&aacute;c nc  ti&ecirc;n tin nh Anh, M, Nht Bn, H&agrave;n Quc &atilde; c c&ocirc;ng nhn t rt l&acirc;u  ri. Nhu cu cn c h tr  sng c lp vi NKT nc ta l&agrave; ch&iacute;nh  &aacute;ng n&ecirc;n sp ti &acirc;y s l&agrave; mt ngh rt ph&aacute;t trin&rdquo;.</em></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> Ch Nguyn Hng H&agrave; &ndash; Gi&aacute;m c D &aacute;n Sng c lp cho bit, iu kin   tr th&agrave;nh mt PA h tr NKT rt n gin. Ngo&agrave;i nhng iu kin nh &atilde;  n&oacute;i  phn u, ch cn mang k&egrave;m theo nhng iu kin &oacute; l&agrave; mt b s  yu l&yacute; lch c&oacute; du x&aacute;c nhn ca ch&iacute;nh quyn a phng (trong trng hp  l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; th d&ugrave;ng giy gii thiu ca nh&agrave; trng v&agrave; th sinh  vi&ecirc;n  thay th) mang n tr s ca Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp H&agrave; Ni l&agrave;  mi c&ocirc;ng vic gn nh ho&agrave;n tt.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Theo chia s ca bn Nguyn Th L&acirc;m,  sinh vi&ecirc;n nm cui Trng i hc KHXH&amp;NV, thu nhp hn 1  triu/th&aacute;ng t ngh PA i vi bn l&agrave; kh&aacute; cao. Nhng &oacute; kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave;  mc &iacute;ch ch&iacute;nh ca L&acirc;m khi quyt nh chn ngh PA v&agrave; gn b&oacute; vi n&oacute; 9  th&aacute;ng nay. Mc ti&ecirc;u cao c m&agrave; L&acirc;m v&agrave; hu ht c&aacute;c bn tr hng ti ch&iacute;nh  l&agrave; c c tri nghim thc t cng hc hi c rt nhiu kinh  nghim sng&nbsp;th&ocirc;ng qua c&ocirc;ng vic v&agrave; c&aacute;c kh&oacute;a hun luyn k nng c t  chc li&ecirc;n tc ca Trung t&acirc;m Sng c lp H&agrave; Ni. &ldquo;Rt nhiu ngi bn  ca em vn trc &acirc;y c b m chiu chung n&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng phi ng tay v&agrave;o  bt c c&ocirc;ng vic g&igrave;. Vy m&agrave; ch sau mt thi gian l&agrave;m PA &atilde; bit nu  n, thm ch&iacute; nu n ngon l&agrave; ng kh&aacute;c. Bi v&igrave; khi l&agrave;m PA, c&aacute;c bn y  c hc dy nu n, k nng giao tip, k nng h tr, c&aacute;ch kim ch  bn th&acirc;n, c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m cho ngi kh&aacute;c h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng v&agrave; v&ocirc; s k nng b &iacute;ch kh&aacute;c  n&ecirc;n ch trong mt thi gian ngn hu ht bn n&agrave;o cng trng th&agrave;nh v&agrave;  chng chc hn l&ecirc;n&rdquo;. L&acirc;m chia s.</span></p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(theo </span>nongnghiep.vn)</em></p>','2011-03-22 23:06:58','admin@jobbid.vn',218,1),(20,'tuyen-dung-sinh-vien-ngay-tai-truong','Tuyn dng sinh vin ngay ti trng','http://phienbancu.tuoitre.vn/Tianyon/Cache/Image/999/486999.jpg','Sng 15-3, by doanh nghip trn a bn TP.HCM, Bnh Dng, ng Nai  n Trng H Ngoi ng - tin hc (HUFLIT)  tuyn dng sinh vin trong ngy hi vic lm Sinh vin HUFLIT v cc nh tuyn dng Nht Bn do trng phi hp cng T chc Pht trin quc t ca Nht Bn (JODC) t chc.','<p class=\"pHead\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong>TT - S&aacute;ng 15-3, by doanh nghip tr&ecirc;n a b&agrave;n TP.HCM,  B&igrave;nh Dng, ng Nai &atilde; n Trng H Ngoi ng - tin hc (HUFLIT)   tuyn dng sinh vi&ecirc;n trong ng&agrave;y hi vic l&agrave;m &ldquo;Sinh vi&ecirc;n HUFLIT v&agrave; c&aacute;c  nh&agrave; tuyn dng Nht Bn&rdquo; do trng phi hp c&ugrave;ng T chc Ph&aacute;t trin quc  t ca Nht Bn (JODC) t chc.</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"pHead\">&nbsp;</p>\n<table class=\"tLegend\" style=\"border-collapse: separate;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"40\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img class=\"lImage\" src=\"http://phienbancu.tuoitre.vn/tianyon/ImageView.aspx?ThumbnailID=486999\" border=\"1\" alt=\"\" hspace=\"0\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>C&ocirc;ng ty Digital Works Vietnam phng vn trc tip ng vi&ecirc;n cho v tr&iacute; th&ocirc;ng dch vi&ecirc;n ting Nht - nh: H&Agrave; B&Igrave;NH</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"pBody\">Ti bui tuyn dng, c&aacute;c doanh nghip &atilde; tip nhn h  s, ng thi trc tip phng vn c&aacute;c ng vi&ecirc;n l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n sp tt  nghip v&agrave;o c&aacute;c v tr&iacute; nh nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n k to&aacute;n, th k&yacute; vn ph&ograve;ng, th&ocirc;ng  dch vi&ecirc;n ting Nht, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh, c&ocirc;ng ngh th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; qun  tr kinh doanh. C&oacute; 20 v tr&iacute; l&agrave;m vic to&agrave;n thi gian v&agrave; mt s v tr&iacute;  l&agrave;m <a title=\"vic b&aacute;n thi gian\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">vic b&aacute;n thi gian</a> &atilde; c tuyn dng.</p>\n<p class=\"pAuthor\">H&Agrave; B&Igrave;NH (theo<em> tuoitre.com.vn</em>)</p>','2011-03-25 15:50:26','admin@jobbid.vn',210,1),(21,'nu-sinh-lam-nguoi-yeu-thue','N sinh lm ngi yu thu','http://ngoisao.net/news/thoi-cuoc/2011/03/163113-nu-sinh-lam-nguoi-yeu-thue/anh-2.jpg','Nhm i nhm li nhng thng tin v gia nh khch hng, Hng va ngh xem mai nn mc g, trang im th no, thm ch ni ci ra sao  khng b h. Ngy mai, c s nhp vai em gi ngi yu ca mt gim c v thm nh \'anh r\'.(cng vic bn thi gian cho hot girl)','<h2 class=\"Lead\" style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\">Nhm i nhm li nhng th&ocirc;ng tin v gia &igrave;nh kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, Hng va ngh xem mai n&ecirc;n mc g&igrave;, trang im th n&agrave;o, thm ch&iacute; n&oacute;i ci ra sao  kh&ocirc;ng b h. Ng&agrave;y mai, c&ocirc; s nhp vai em g&aacute;i ngi y&ecirc;u ca mt gi&aacute;m c v thm nh&agrave; \'anh r\'.</span></h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Tng nhn hp ng l&agrave;m ngi tr&ograve; chuyn v&agrave; i ung c&agrave; ph&ecirc; c&ugrave;ng mt doanh nh&acirc;n &atilde; v&agrave;o tui bm, cha ngi y&ecirc;u nhng ln n&agrave;y vi Hng qu l&agrave; \"ca\" kh&oacute;. V kh&aacute;ch va c&atilde;i nhau vi bn g&aacute;i trong khi anh n&agrave;y li tr&oacute;t ha s mang n&agrave;ng v ra mt gia &igrave;nh. Anh ch&agrave;ng &agrave;nh n&oacute;i di ngi th&acirc;n rng bn b m v&agrave; tc tc i thu&ecirc; ngi &oacute;ng th gi l&agrave;m em g&aacute;i thay \"ch\" v thm hi gia &igrave;nh anh r tng lai. Tn dng mi kinh nghim t cuc t&igrave;nh va qua, Hng v&agrave;o vai tht ngt v&agrave; khp duy ch c&oacute; mt s c khin c&ocirc; kh&ocirc;ng th n&agrave;o qu&ecirc;n...</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><img src=\"http://ngoisao.net/news/thoi-cuoc/2011/03/163113-nu-sinh-lam-nguoi-yeu-thue/anh-2.jpg\" border=\"1\" alt=\"\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" align=\"center\" /></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Image\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: none;\">Dch v ngi &oacute;ng th rt ph bin  c&aacute;c nc nhng mi xut hin  Vit Nam hai nm.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>nh minh ha.</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Ngi &oacute;ng th hay l&agrave;m ngi y&ecirc;u thu&ecirc;, mt c&ocirc;ng vic c&ograve;n xa l v&agrave; kh&aacute; mi m nhng li c&oacute; sc h&uacute;t mnh vi gii tr hin nay c bit l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n. Ra trng, Hng cng n&ocirc;n n&oacute;ng l&ecirc;n mng t&igrave;m vic v&agrave; t&igrave;nh c c c mu qung c&aacute;o tuyn cng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n ca c&ocirc;ng ty Vinamost chuy&ecirc;n cho thu&ecirc; ngi &oacute;ng th c&aacute;c vai trong cuc sng u ti&ecirc;n  Vit Nam. Mt phn mun t&iacute;ch ly kinh nghim, c&aacute;c mi quan h x&atilde; hi trc khi xin v&agrave;o l&agrave;m &uacute;ng chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng ca m&igrave;nh, mt phn cng v&igrave; t&ograve; m&ograve;, c&ocirc; np h s ri tr&uacute;ng tuyn.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Hp ng u ti&ecirc;n ca Hng nm trong g&oacute;i c&agrave; ph&ecirc; @ v&agrave; nhim v ca c&ocirc; ch vic n mc p i ung nc c&ugrave;ng kh&aacute;ch, lng nghe h t&acirc;m s v&agrave; thnh thong ci tht ti. Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca c&ocirc; l&agrave; mt doanh nh&acirc;n tr b gia &igrave;nh gic ci v. Anh n&agrave;y mun c&oacute; nhng bui c&agrave; ph&ecirc; c&ugrave;ng c&ocirc; g&aacute;i tr, p  chia s cuc sng ngo&agrave;i kinh doanh v&agrave; bit &acirc;u s b&eacute;n duy&ecirc;n. Vn kh&eacute;o l&eacute;o v&agrave; bit c&aacute;ch n n&oacute;i, thi sinh vi&ecirc;n tng l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m nhiu c&ocirc;ng vic n&ecirc;n Hng bo dn v&agrave; tr&ocirc;ng gi&agrave; dn hn so vi c&aacute;i tui 23 ca m&igrave;nh.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Cuc gp u ti&ecirc;n din ra nh nh&agrave;ng bi ch  ch xoay quanh vic \"m anh th&iacute;ch i ch&ugrave;a; em c&oacute; th&iacute;ch i ch&ugrave;a kh&ocirc;ng?\". Ch vi 2h ngi c&agrave; ph&ecirc; c&ugrave;ng kh&aacute;ch, Hng kim c hn 250 ngh&igrave;n ng. C&ocirc;ng vic n gin, thu nhp tt, c&ocirc; tip tc nhn hp ng tip theo, gi l&agrave;m em g&aacute;i ngi y&ecirc;u ca mt gi&aacute;m c tr theo \"anh r tng lai\" v thm gia &igrave;nh. Do c&oacute; ngoi h&igrave;nh v&agrave; nhiu im ging vi bn g&aacute;i anh ta n&ecirc;n Hng &atilde; c \"chm\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">C&ocirc; sinh vi&ecirc;n trng Kinh t Quc d&acirc;n k: \"V&igrave; &oacute;ng l&agrave; em g&aacute;i ca ngi y&ecirc;u n&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh cng kh&ocirc;ng phi din c&aacute;c pha t&igrave;nh cm nhng vn run lm v&igrave; bit nhiu h h&agrave;ng nh&agrave; anh y ang ch i  nh&igrave;n thy mt c&ocirc; em g&aacute;i ca ngi y&ecirc;u con trai m&igrave;nh. Mi c ch, li n&oacute;i s b ch&uacute; &yacute;, ch cn nhm ch&uacute;t th&ocirc;ng tin s khin m&igrave;nh l&uacute;ng t&uacute;ng\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Mc d&ugrave; trc l&uacute;c v&agrave;o vai, c&ocirc; &atilde; gp kh&aacute;ch  nm r&otilde; tiu s, th&ocirc;ng tin cn thit v ngi th&acirc;n cng nh \" kh&oacute;\" ca b m \"anh r\", Hng vn kh&ocirc;ng khi ngi ng&ugrave;ng khi phi theo ngi l v gp g v&agrave; n&oacute;i nhng c&acirc;u chuyn \"nh tht\". Nh&agrave; gi&aacute;m c c&aacute;ch H&agrave; Ni c&oacute; 35 c&acirc;y s, c&oacute; mt ch g&aacute;i &atilde; lp gia &igrave;nh v&agrave; sng gn b m. V&igrave; ng xa, li i bng xe m&aacute;y n&ecirc;n c&ocirc; kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m mc qu&aacute; cu k v&agrave; trang im im n tng  b ch&uacute; &yacute;. Dc ng i, hai ngi c&ugrave;ng nhau \"&ocirc;n luyn\" c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin. V kh&aacute;ch nh c th tr&uacute;t bu t&acirc;m s v x&iacute;ch m&iacute;ch vi ngi y&ecirc;u v&agrave; cng l&agrave;  Hng nm t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh r&otilde; hn. Bui &oacute;n tip din ra tht m c&uacute;ng v&agrave; su&ocirc;n s khi mi c&acirc;u hi ph&iacute;a ngi th&acirc;n \"anh r\" u c Hng tr li tr&ocirc;i chy v&agrave; y cm x&uacute;c. n phn gp g bn b&egrave;, c&ocirc; n&agrave;ng su&yacute;t b l v&igrave; b c&aacute;c bn ca anh n&agrave;y \"hi xo&aacute;y\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">\"Mt ngi bn ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng hi:<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>Em l&agrave; ngi Ba V&igrave; &agrave;?<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></em>M&igrave;nh bo<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>v&acirc;ng.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></em>Sau &oacute; anh n&agrave;y bo mun nghe em n&oacute;i ging a phng. M&igrave;nh bi ri mt l&uacute;c v&igrave; cha tng nghe ging n&oacute;i  &oacute; bao gi. Chc anh y nghi ng v&igrave; m&igrave;nh n&oacute;i ging H&agrave; Ni kh&ocirc;ng pha. Nu l&uacute;c &oacute; m&agrave; gii thiu qu&ecirc; Ngh An chc m&igrave;nh l mt\", c&ocirc; n&agrave;ng sinh nm 1988 ph&aacute; l&ecirc;n ci khi nh li k nim y.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Kt th&uacute;c mt ng&agrave;y &oacute;ng th, Hng nhn c th&ugrave; lao 500.000 ng v&agrave; c th&ecirc;m c mt ngi bn. Sau gn hai th&aacute;ng b \"th th&aacute;ch\" vi v tr&iacute; cng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n, hin Hng mi c nhn v&agrave;o l&agrave;m nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh thc chuy&ecirc;n sp xp c&aacute;c cuc gp cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng n&agrave;o c&oacute; nhu cu c&agrave; ph&ecirc;. C&ocirc; t&acirc;m s th&ecirc;m, c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y c&ograve;n mi  Vit Nam, li kh&aacute; nhy cm n&ecirc;n d b hiu nhm l&agrave; mt dch v tr&aacute; h&igrave;nh. Mc d&ugrave; c ph&iacute;a c&ocirc;ng ty h tr c&aacute;c \"nghip v\" ph&ograve;ng v v&agrave; chc chn v  tin cy ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng nhng \"c&ocirc;ng ty ch m bo mc  an to&agrave;n khong 80% n 90 % c&ograve;n li 10 % l&agrave; t m&igrave;nh phi bo v m&igrave;nh\". T ra t tin song Hng vn kh&ocirc;ng khi e ngi khi phi tit l vi ngi th&acirc;n hay bn b&egrave; v c&ocirc;ng vic ang l&agrave;m.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">\"Kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t ngi nghi ng dch v l&uacute;c nghe n&oacute;i ti ngi y&ecirc;u thu&ecirc; hay &oacute;ng gi l&agrave;m bn g&aacute;i. M&igrave;nh cha c&oacute; bn trai n&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng s b bt gp hay ghen tu&ocirc;ng nhng cng kh&ocirc;ng mun  bn b&egrave;, ngi th&acirc;n bit m&igrave;nh l&agrave;m vic n&agrave;y  tr&aacute;nh b hi han hay nhng suy ngh kh&ocirc;ng &uacute;ng\", c&ocirc; th&agrave;nh tht.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Cng ging Hng, Minh, sinh vi&ecirc;n i hc Lao ng X&atilde; hi H&agrave; Ni, t&ograve; m&ograve; vi c&ocirc;ng vic &oacute;ng th khi c c th&ocirc;ng tin tuyn dng ca mt c&ocirc;ng ty cho thu&ecirc; ngi y&ecirc;u. Ging n&oacute;i nh nh&agrave;ng, cun h&uacute;t, n sinh nm nht tit l: \"Mi u em ngh ngi &oacute;ng th chc ging cascadeur &oacute;ng phim v&agrave; thc s kh&ocirc;ng h&igrave;nh dung c c&ocirc;ng vic. Sau khi nghe anh gi&aacute;m c gii th&iacute;ch, em hiu ngay m&igrave;nh phi l&agrave;m g&igrave;\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Tng l&agrave;m ngi mu nh, Minh t tin v&agrave; bo dn khi tip x&uacute;c vi ngi l. Gia &igrave;nh kinh doanh bt ng sn, thng xuy&ecirc;n phi tip c&aacute;c v kh&aacute;ch VIP v&agrave; gii kinh doanh n&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng vic \"lng nghe v&agrave; tr&ograve; chuyn\" kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; kh&oacute; khn vi c&ocirc;. Mi &acirc;y c&ocirc; va nhn hp ng i n ti vi mt doanh nh&acirc;n min Trung ti mt kh&aacute;ch sn sang trng. &Ocirc;ng kh&aacute;ch &atilde; ln tui, mun c&oacute; mt ngi n ti c&ugrave;ng khi ra Bc c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c. Cuc gp kh&aacute; gp g&aacute;p, 18h30 nhn cuc gi, 19h c&ocirc; &atilde; phi ti ch hn. Do c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; ngi min trong n&ecirc;n c&ocirc; cng d d&agrave;ng tip chuyn kh&aacute;ch hn.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">\"Ln &oacute; em phi chun b qun &aacute;o v&agrave; trang im gp g&aacute;p. Kh&ocirc;ng th chn trang phc x&igrave; tin, nh&iacute; nhnh c bi kh&aacute;ch &atilde; c&oacute; tui n&ecirc;n em chn v&aacute;y v&agrave; trang im tht nh nh&agrave;ng. Trong cuc tr&ograve; chuyn, em cng kh&ocirc;ng cn n&oacute;i nhiu, ch nghe v&agrave; gt u hng ng. &Ocirc;ng y rt vui nh gp ngi quen v&agrave; c&ograve;n k cho em nghe nhiu v nhng ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave; ca m&igrave;nh\", Minh k.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Theo &ocirc;ng Dng Ngc To&agrave;n, Gi&aacute;m c c&ocirc;ng ty VinaEscort chuy&ecirc;n cung cp ngi &oacute;ng th, cho thu&ecirc; ngi y&ecirc;u, bn g&aacute;i i d tic hoc th k&yacute; gi&aacute;m c..., dch v l hin rt hot. Phn ln c&aacute;c cng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n ca c&ocirc;ng ty u c&ograve;n l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n tr trung, ngoi h&igrave;nh cao r&aacute;o, xinh p c&oacute; th &aacute;p ng c&aacute;c n t h&agrave;ng l&agrave;m PG, &oacute;ng l&agrave;m ngi y&ecirc;u, bn g&aacute;i, th k&yacute; hay nhp bt c vai din n&agrave;o. &Ocirc;ng To&agrave;n cho bit, vi mc &iacute;ch gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&oacute; cuc sng th&uacute; v ngo&agrave;i c&ocirc;ng vic, c&oacute; ngi s chia v&agrave; t&acirc;m s, c&aacute;c cng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n c hun luyn nhiu k nng n&oacute;i chuyn, giao tip, thm ch&iacute; c c&aacute;ch t v trong c&aacute;c trng hp bt ng. Ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;c c&ocirc; g&aacute;i, kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t c&aacute;c nam sinh cng ng k&yacute; <a title=\"c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian n&agrave;y\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian n&agrave;y</a>. Mc th&ugrave; lao cho mt cuc hn s ph thuc v&agrave;o \"chiu cao v&agrave; nhan sc\" ca ngi &oacute;ng th.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\">Trong nhng ng&agrave;y l, Tt, lng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng t&igrave;m n dch v ca c&ocirc;ng ty tr&ecirc;n kh&aacute; &ocirc;ng. \"Ng&agrave;y quc t ph n, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &atilde; nhn c hn 15 n t h&agrave;ng c&agrave; ph&ecirc; @. Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng phn ln l&agrave; nam gii mun t&igrave;m mt ngi bn g&aacute;i ngi tr&ograve; chuyn vi m&igrave;nh. Mc gi&aacute; khong 800 ngh&igrave;n ng mt cuc hn\".</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; color: #000000; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; line-height: 19px;\"><strong>B&igrave;nh Minh </strong><em>(ngun ngoisao.net)</em><strong><br /></strong></p>','2011-03-28 15:03:14','admin@jobbid.vn',324,1),(22,'lao-dong-tre-vua-lam-vua-hoc','Lao ng tr va lm va hc','http://nongnghiep.vn/Upload/Image/2011/3/15/15032011122949.JPG','Tim viec ban thoi gian -  gim bt gnh nng v ti chnh cho gia nh v theo ui c m hc hnh, nhiu lao ng tr t nng thn ra thnh ph tm vic  chn hng i va hc, va lm.','<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"tim viec ban thoi gian\" src=\"http://nongnghiep.vn/Upload/Image/2011/3/15/15032011122949.JPG\" alt=\"tim viec ban thoi gian\" width=\"310\" height=\"232\" /><span style=\"font-size: small; color: #888888;\"> gim bt g&aacute;nh nng v t&agrave;i  ch&iacute;nh cho gia &igrave;nh v&agrave; theo ui c m hc h&agrave;nh, nhiu lao ng tr t  n&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;n ra th&agrave;nh ph t&igrave;m vic &atilde; chn hng i va hc, va l&agrave;m.</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Theo ui gic m ging ng</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Tt nghip THPT loi kh&aacute; nhng do ho&agrave;n  cnh gia &igrave;nh kh&oacute; khn n&ecirc;n Nguyn Th Huyn (qu&ecirc; H&agrave; Tnh) phi g&aacute;c li  gic m v&agrave;o i hc  bc v&agrave;o cuc sng mu sinh nng nhc. Sau tt  T&acirc;n M&atilde;o, Huyn v&agrave;o B&igrave;nh Dng kim vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m v&agrave; tip tc p  c m  l&agrave;m c&ocirc; gi&aacute;o t ng&agrave;y b&eacute;. &ldquo;Em va c nhn v&agrave;o l&agrave;m ti mt c&ocirc;ng ty ch  to linh kin in t ca H&agrave;n Quc trong KCN Vit Hng vi mc lng  2,2 triu ng/th&aacute;ng. Tr chi ph&iacute; n , nh&agrave; tr, nu sng tn tin em  cng c&ograve;n ch&uacute;t d  i hc &ocirc;n ti trung t&acirc;m luyn thi i hc, cao ng  B&igrave;nh Dng&rdquo;, Huyn t&acirc;m s. Sau gi tan ca, Huyn v&agrave; hai ngi bn c&ugrave;ng  ph&ograve;ng tr li mang cp s&aacute;ch n lp hc &ocirc;n.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Thi rt i hc, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; iu kin    nh&agrave; &ocirc;n thi, Trn Vn Vnh (