"http://www.jobbid.vn\">c&ocirc;ng vic part-time</a>.</p>\n<p>\"Tng lp mt club d d&agrave;ng, ai ng gp qu&aacute; nhiu kh&oacute; khn, c&oacute; l&uacute;c  tng chng nh sp . Ai d&aacute;m theo mt sinh vi&ecirc;n nm th nht nh  m&igrave;nh?\", Long nh li.</p>\n<p>Gi &acirc;y, sau gn 2 nm, t mt nh&oacute;m bn chi th&acirc;n, ClubVieclam.com &atilde;  tr th&agrave;nh t chc hot ng hiu qu. &acirc;y cng l&agrave; mt trong s &iacute;t nhng  c&acirc;u lc b sinh vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; ngun thu ln v t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh.</p>\n<p>ClubVieclam.com hin thu h&uacute;t s quan t&acirc;m ca h&agrave;ng trm sinh vi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n  a b&agrave;n H&agrave; Ni. Vi s quyt t&acirc;m c&ugrave;ng am m&ecirc; kinh doanh ch&aacute;y bng, Li  Th Long v&agrave; nh&oacute;m bn ang bin ClubVieclam.com tr th&agrave;nh h&igrave;nh mu &aacute;ng  hc hi cho sinh vi&ecirc;n c&aacute;c trng i hc, cao ng.</p>\n<p>Theo <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">SVVN</span></p>','2011-04-04 10:42:32','admin@jobbid.vn',224,1),(25,'sinh-vien-duoc-va-mat-voi-cong-viec-ban-thoi-gian','Sinh vin c v mt vi cng vic bn thi gian','http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2011/04/01/10/20110401103737_can%20phai%20co%20su%20can%20nhac%20ki%20cang%20khi%20quyet%20dinh%20lam%20freelance.jpg','Cong viec ban thoi gian - Freelancer (lao ng t do) l thut ng quen thuc song cng kh l lm vi khng t sinh vin. Freelancer c th d dng kim c vi trm  mi thng nhng nhng kh khn, vt v h gp phi l khng h nh.','<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Freelancer (lao ng t do) l&agrave; thut ng quen thuc song cng kh&aacute; l lm vi kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t sinh vi&ecirc;n. Freelancer c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng kim c v&agrave;i trm &ocirc; mi th&aacute;ng nhng nhng kh&oacute; khn, vt v h gp phi l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng h nh.</strong></span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">c nhiu tin v&agrave; kinh nghim</strong><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Nhng ngi va tip cn freelance hn s rt ng ng&agrave;ng khi bit c gi&aacute; tr ca cht x&aacute;m m&agrave; c&aacute;c freelancer b ra. Vi mi c&ocirc;ng vic, c&aacute;c freelancer c&oacute; th nhn c v&agrave;i chc n v&agrave;i trm, thm ch&iacute; h&agrave;ng ngh&igrave;n &ocirc; t c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng. i tng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng rt a dng, c&oacute; th l&agrave; c&aacute;c lao ng b&igrave;nh thng hay sinh vi&ecirc;n, nghi&ecirc;n cu sinh v&agrave; thm ch&iacute; c nhng ngi c&oacute; hc v cao hn.<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Nguyn Th&agrave;nh Trung, sinh vi&ecirc;n Khoa C&ocirc;ng ngh Th&ocirc;ng tin, i hc C&ocirc;ng ngh H&agrave; Ni, vn l&agrave; mt freelancer l&acirc;u nm. Trung t h&agrave;o cho bit v khon tin m&igrave;nh kim c t c&ocirc;ng vic: \"Mi mt th&aacute;ng m&igrave;nh kim c xp x 1000 &ocirc;. C&ocirc;ng vic thng l&agrave; gii b&agrave;i tp cho c&aacute;c sinh vi&ecirc;n nc ngo&agrave;i. T&ugrave;y v&agrave;o  phc tp ca b&agrave;i tp, m&igrave;nh thng ly t 30-50 &ocirc;. Thnh thong m&igrave;nh cng nhn c&aacute;c project (d &aacute;n) v&agrave;i trm &ocirc;. Va c&oacute; nhiu tin, va c l&agrave;m quen vi &aacute;p lc c&ocirc;ng vic, va to c ting tm, ti g&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m.\"<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /></p>\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<table class=\"image center\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse; background-color: #eeeeee; width: 480px; color: #004488;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"400\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-width: 0px; max-width: 480px;\" src=\"http://imgs.vietnamnet.vn/Images/2011/04/01/10/20110401103737_can%20phai%20co%20su%20can%20nhac%20ki%20cang%20khi%20quyet%20dinh%20lam%20freelance.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<td class=\"image_desc\" style=\"padding: 5px; margin: 0px; text-align: center; color: #004488; background-color: #eeeeee; border-collapse: collapse;\">Cn c&acirc;n nhc trc khi quyt nh tr th&agrave;nh freelancer</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p>Theo Trung, i tng m&agrave; c&aacute;c freelancer sinh vi&ecirc;n n&ecirc;n hng n ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; c&aacute;c sinh vi&ecirc;n  c&aacute;c trng quc t. C&oacute; rt nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n \"u rng t&uacute;i dy\" hoc kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; thi gian l&agrave;m b&agrave;i tp s ng y&ecirc;u cu l&ecirc;n c&aacute;c trang web freelance. C&aacute;c freelancer ch vic accept (chp nhn), gii b&agrave;i tp, gi cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; nhn tin qua t&agrave;i khon.&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Hi ng, sinh vi&ecirc;n i hc B&aacute;ch khoa H&agrave; Ni, l&agrave; mt \"chuy&ecirc;n gia freelancer\" v lp tr&igrave;nh m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh. Kh&ocirc;ng u t nhiu thi gian cho c&ocirc;ng vic freelance nhng bn cng kim v v&agrave;i trm &ocirc; mi th&aacute;ng. i vi bn, &acirc;y l&agrave; mt c&ocirc;ng vic cc k&igrave; n gin v&agrave; cng d kim tin: \"Code (vit m&atilde; lp tr&igrave;nh) 6 d&ograve;ng c 10 bng, tin ni kh&ocirc;ng?\"<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />ng c&ograve;n bt m&iacute; v nhng c&aacute;ch \"c&acirc;u tin\" ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng \"g&agrave;\": \"C&oacute; nhng b&agrave;i tp d t nhng m&igrave;nh c n&oacute;i l&agrave; rt kh&oacute;, rt phc tp. Th l&agrave; \"con g&agrave;\" cung qu&iacute;t tng tin l&ecirc;n ngay!\"<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Mt thi gian v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng sc</strong><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />i vi sinh vi&ecirc;n, c&ocirc;ng vic ch&iacute;nh vn l&agrave; hc. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, vi khon thu hp dn kh&ocirc;ng kh&oacute; g&igrave; c&oacute; c, nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n &atilde; lao v&agrave;o l&agrave;m freelancer nh mt c&ocirc;ng vic full time.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Quang Ph&uacute;c, sinh vi&ecirc;n Khoa Vt l&iacute; k thut, i hc C&ocirc;ng ngh H&agrave; Ni kh&ocirc;ng kh&aacute;c g&igrave; mt \"con thi&ecirc;u th&acirc;n\" ca c&ocirc;ng vic freelance. Mi bc v&agrave;o ngh c v&agrave;i th&aacute;ng m&agrave; khon thu nhp ca Ph&uacute;c &atilde; l&ecirc;n n hn mt ng&agrave;n &ocirc;. L&agrave;m vic qu&ecirc;n n, qu&ecirc;n ng, v&agrave; ng nhi&ecirc;n c qu&ecirc;n hc na. Ngi Ph&uacute;c gy rc i tr&ocirc;ng thy. Bn b&egrave; khuy&ecirc;n bo th&igrave; Ph&uacute;c gt i, cho rng bn b&egrave; \"ghen t\" khi thy m&igrave;nh c&oacute; nhiu tin v&agrave; hi vng ti chic xe m&aacute;y xn v&agrave; chic laptop Vaio mi, thay cho chic laptop &atilde; bn tui ca m&igrave;nh. Nhng c&oacute; l, iu bn n&ecirc;n hi vng b&acirc;y gi l&agrave; vic vt qua k&igrave; thi hc k&igrave; sp ti!<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Hi Yn, n lp tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n tng lai ki&ecirc;m freelancer ang hc ti i hc FPT,&nbsp; l&agrave; nn nh&acirc;n trong mt c&uacute; la au n. V&igrave; qu&aacute; c tin, sau khi l&agrave;m xong project c giao, bn &atilde; gi thng c source (file ngun) cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng. Kt qu, 1000 &ocirc; m&agrave; bn t quyt t&acirc;m gi&agrave;nh c my tun nay &atilde; b kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng n  \"b&ugrave;ng\". H&oacute;a ra, bn vi kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tha thun ri&ecirc;ng s chuyn khon Paypal, kh&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;ng qua website  tr&aacute;nh mt ph&iacute; nhng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &atilde; \"im thin th&iacute;t v&agrave; ln mt tm\".<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Kh&ocirc;ng giu ni s m c, Yn cho bit: \"T gi m&igrave;nh phi chn nhng kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&oacute; nhiu review (nhn x&eacute;t) tt v&agrave; phi nhn tin qua web freelance. &aacute;ng l m&igrave;nh phi gi bn demo (bn th nghim)  kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng duyt v&agrave; gi tin trc ch kh&ocirc;ng gi thng c source nh th\".<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Cn c&acirc;n nhc gia c v&agrave; mt</strong><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />Kh&ocirc;ng th ph nhn nhng gi&aacute; tr m&agrave; c&ocirc;ng vic freelance mang li, song vi sinh vi&ecirc;n, c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y cn mt s sp xp hiu qu sao cho kh&ocirc;ng nh hng ti hc tp v&agrave; sinh hot ca m&igrave;nh. Freelance kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave; mt c&ocirc;ng vic n nh, l&uacute;c c&ocirc;ng vic ngp u, l&uacute;c li ngi chi xi nc. V&igrave; th cn phi c&oacute; s c&acirc;n nhc k c&agrave;ng gia vic theo ui freelance vi vic tp trung hc tp  c&oacute; mt c&ocirc;ng vic n nh sau khi ra trng.<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /></p>\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<table class=\"quote center\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #d6dce8; background-color: #eeeeee;\" width=\"400\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 3px 5px; margin: 0px; color: black; text-align: justify;\">\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Freelancer l&agrave; ngi lao ng c lp, kh&ocirc;ng chu s qun l&iacute; ca bt k&igrave; ch lao ng n&agrave;o. C&aacute;c lnh vc trong Freelance gm: b&aacute;o ch&iacute;, xut bn, vit vn, trang im, bi&ecirc;n tp, lp k hoch s kin, qun l&iacute; s kin, lp tr&igrave;nh m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh, thit k web, thit k  ha, ph&aacute;t trin website, bi&ecirc;n dch, hng dn vi&ecirc;n...<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />C&aacute;c trang web freelance l&agrave; trung gian ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; freelancer. Tin ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng gi cho freelancer s c website khu tr  l&agrave;m ph&iacute; ph&aacute;t trin web. Ngo&agrave;i khon thu ca website, freelancer c&ograve;n phi chu khon ph&iacute; chuyn t&agrave;i khon quc t. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, hai mc ph&iacute; n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;ng k, ch khong v&agrave;i % tin c&ocirc;ng ca c&ocirc;ng vic<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" /><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> Quang </strong><em><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">(theo vietnamnet.vn)</strong></em><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></strong><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"></strong><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><br /></strong></p>','2011-04-05 08:46:47','admin@jobbid.vn',336,1),(26,'hieu-qua-san-giao-dich-viec-lam-khong-nhu-mong-doi','Hiu qu sn giao dch vic lm khng nh mong i','http://vneconomy1.vcmedia.vn/ThumbImages/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/09/09/sangiaodich_260.gif','Thng tin u thu - Nhiu sn giao dch vic lm c nm ch hot ng mt ln, cn nhng sn hot ng kh u n th ch mang tnh hnh thc...','<div class=\"w_260 f_l \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 260px; border-right: 30px solid #ffffff; border-bottom: 30px solid #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"w_260 f_l\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 260px;\"><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /><img style=\"border-width: 0px;\" title=\"Hiu qu s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m kh&ocirc;ng nh mong i\" src=\"http://vneconomy1.vcmedia.vn/ThumbImages/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/09/09/sangiaodich_260.gif\" alt=\"picture\" width=\"260\" /></div>\n<div class=\"w_260 f_l\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; width: 260px;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: Arial; font-size: x-small;\">Hot ng tuyn dng ti mt s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"divBodyTinChiTiet\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt; color: #888888;\">Nhiu s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m c nm ch hot ng mt ln, c&ograve;n nhng s&agrave;n hot ng kh&aacute; u n th&igrave; ch mang t&iacute;nh h&igrave;nh thc...</span><br style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Nhng nhn nh n&agrave;y &atilde; c ra ti hi ngh &aacute;nh gi&aacute; hiu qu hot ng ca c&aacute;c s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m giai on 2006 - 2010 v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c d b&aacute;o nhu cu nh&acirc;n lc, din ra s&aacute;ng 9/9 ti H&agrave; Ni.<br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />&Ocirc;ng Nguyn i ng, Cc trng Cc Vic l&agrave;m, B Lao ng - Thng binh v&agrave; X&atilde; hi cho bit, &yacute; tng x&acirc;y dng cu ni gia doanh nghip v&agrave; ngi lao ng, hay n&oacute;i c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c gia cung v&agrave; cu lao ng hot ng t nm 1990, th&ocirc;ng qua c&aacute;c hi ch vic l&agrave;m. Sau n&agrave;y m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y c ph&aacute;t trin th&agrave;nh s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m.<br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />&Ocirc;ng ng cho rng, mc &iacute;ch ca ng&agrave;nh lao ng t ra  m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh s&agrave;n giao giao dch vic l&agrave;m kh&aacute;c vi hi ch vic l&agrave;m l&agrave; t chc hot ng thng xuy&ecirc;n, chuy&ecirc;n nghip v&agrave; hiu qu hn, c&oacute; th hot ng nhiu ln trong mt th&aacute;ng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, thc t, hiu qu ca c&aacute;c s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m kh&ocirc;ng c nh mong i.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Theo b&aacute;o c&aacute;o ca B Lao ng - Thng binh v&agrave; X&atilde; hi, hin nay hu ht c&aacute;c tnh, th&agrave;nh tr&ecirc;n c nc u c&oacute; c&aacute;c s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m. Trong &oacute;, c&oacute; 44 s&agrave;n ang hot ng nh k, thng xuy&ecirc;n vi tn sut 1 phi&ecirc;n/th&aacute;ng, nhiu trung t&acirc;m t chc s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m vi tn sut 2 phi&ecirc;n/th&aacute;ng.<br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Mc u t cho mt s&agrave;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m khong t 5 n 7 t ng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, t l t&igrave;m vic qua trung t&acirc;m mi ch t 14%; t l ngi s dng lao ng qua trung t&acirc;m cng mi ch t 16,4%.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />B&aacute;o c&aacute;o t c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m gii thiu vic l&agrave;m ca c&aacute;c a phng cng cho thy hiu qu cung ng lao ng th&ocirc;ng qua c&aacute;c s&agrave;n hin vn thp.<br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />C th, ti phi&ecirc;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m ln th 19 hi th&aacute;ng 4 ca t&igrave;nh B&igrave;nh Dng, c&oacute; 317 doanh nghip ng k&yacute; tuyn dng vi hn 20.000 ch l&agrave;m trng nhng ch c&oacute; hn 1.000 lao ng ti tham gia tuyn dng trc tip. Tnh Vnh Ph&uacute;c t u nm n nay cng &atilde; t chc 6 phi&ecirc;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m vi nhu cu cn tuyn dng khong 12.000 lao ng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, s lao ng c tuyn cng ch &aacute;p ng c khong 10%.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Ti Trung t&acirc;m Gii thiu vic l&agrave;m H&agrave; Ni, &ocirc;ng V Trung Ch&iacute;nh, Gi&aacute;m c Trung t&acirc;m cho bit, t nm 2007 n th&aacute;ng 6/2010,&nbsp; ni n&agrave;y &atilde; t chc 56 phi&ecirc;n giao dch vi 4.868 n v doanh nghip tham gia. S ngi n phi&ecirc;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m 150.800 ngi, b&igrave;nh qu&acirc;n gn 2.700 ngi/phi&ecirc;n; s ngi c c&aacute;c nh&agrave; tuyn dng phng vn trc tip v&agrave; tip nhn h s ti c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m l&agrave; 116.135 lt lao ng; trung b&igrave;nh mi phi&ecirc;n giao dch vic l&agrave;m c&oacute; 1.874 ngi c phng vn v&agrave; tip nhn h s.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, vi nhng con s xem ra rt &ldquo;ho&agrave;nh tr&aacute;ng&rdquo; tr&ecirc;n, &ocirc;ng Ch&iacute;nh vn tha nhn, kh nng &aacute;p ng cu lao ng ca s&agrave;n cha cao, s lng mi ch &aacute;p ng c khong 20% nhu cu ca c&aacute;c doanh nghip.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Ti hi ngh, b&agrave; Nguyn Hi V&acirc;n, Ph&oacute; cc trng Cc Vic l&agrave;m, Gi&aacute;m c Trung t&acirc;m quc gia D b&aacute;o v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng tin th trng lao ng cng a ra nhn nh, h thng dch v vic l&agrave;m hin thi ch yu t chc c&aacute;c hot ng nh k ca s&agrave;n giao dch, mi ch &aacute;p ng c khong 10 - 15% nhu cu thc t v t vn v&agrave; gii quyt vic l&agrave;m.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" /><br style=\"font-size: 11pt;\" />Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n ca s k&eacute;m n&oacute;i tr&ecirc;n, theo b&agrave; V&acirc;n, l&agrave; do c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch th&ocirc;ng tin th trng lao ng c&ograve;n nhiu hn ch, cha c&oacute; &aacute;nh gi&aacute; s&acirc;u v th trng lao ng ti c&aacute;c a phng. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, mt s a phng s dng vn u t cha &uacute;ng mc &iacute;ch; i ng c&aacute;n b thuc lnh vc n&agrave;y thiu c v s lng v&agrave; s chuy&ecirc;n nghip.</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt;\"></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 11pt;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial;\">Ngun </span>vneconomy.vn</em></div>','2011-04-06 10:47:09','admin@jobbid.vn',160,1),(27,'kinh-nghiem-tim-viec-cho-nguoi-moi-dinh-cu','Kinh nghim tm vic cho ngi mi nh c','http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/84/4b/top.jpg','cong viec part time - cong viec ban thoi gian - Cc k nng v kinh nghim  tm kim vic lm l mt trong nhng k nng quan trng nht cn c ca bt c ai nh c ti vng t mi.','<h2 class=\"Lead\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11pt; color: #5f5f5f; font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"padding: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"cong viec part time\" src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/84/4b/top.jpg\" alt=\"cong viec part time\" width=\"250\" height=\"195\" />C&aacute;c k nng v&agrave; kinh nghim  t&igrave;m kim vic l&agrave;m l&agrave; mt trong nhng k nng quan trng nht cn c&oacute; ca bt c ai nh c ti v&ugrave;ng t mi.</h2>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">Ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c anh, ch tr&ecirc;n din &agrave;n Ngi Vit Nm Ch&acirc;u ca b&aacute;o<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>VnExpress</em>.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">C&aacute;c k nng v&agrave; kinh nghim  t&igrave;m kim vic l&agrave;m l&agrave; mt trong nhng k nng quan trng nht cn c&oacute; ca bt c ai nh c ti v&ugrave;ng t mi. Trong b&agrave;i vit n&agrave;y, t&ocirc;i mong mun c&oacute; s chia s v&agrave; &oacute;ng g&oacute;p ca nhiu anh, ch c&ugrave;ng tham gia  g&oacute;p phn to ra mt cm nang cho cng ng ngi Vit trong vic t&igrave;m kim vic l&agrave;m, n nh cuc sng.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">Di &acirc;y l&agrave; nhng kinh nghim v&agrave; tri thc m&agrave; t&ocirc;i c&oacute; c ti Canada, xin chia s vi c&aacute;c anh, ch v&agrave; hy vng c&oacute; th&ecirc;m nhiu &yacute; kin &oacute;ng g&oacute;p b &iacute;ch kh&aacute;c:</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">1. T&igrave;m hiu th&ocirc;ng tin, x&aacute;c nh mc &iacute;ch</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- X&aacute;c nh r&otilde; nhng vic bn c&oacute; th l&agrave;m: nhng vic l&agrave;m fulltime, c&aacute;c vic l&agrave;m b&aacute;n thi gian ph thuc v&agrave;o nng lc, s th&iacute;ch v&agrave; iu kin ca bn th&acirc;n. C&oacute; nhng l&uacute;c cn phi ly ngn nu&ocirc;i d&agrave;i bng c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vic n gin v&agrave; b&aacute;n thi gian khi mi to lp cuc sng. i vi vic l&agrave;m b&aacute;n thi gian cng rt a dng, v&igrave; Canada tr lng theo gi (l&agrave;m gi n&agrave;o t&iacute;nh tin gi &oacute;), n&ecirc;n c&aacute;c &ocirc;ng ch khi thu&ecirc; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n cng kh&aacute; linh hot v thi gian, thm ch&iacute; l&agrave;m ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng cng c&oacute; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n l&agrave;m <a title=\"c&ocirc;ng vic part time\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">c&ocirc;ng vic part time</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- T&igrave;m hiu th&ocirc;ng tin qua c&aacute;c website ca ch&iacute;nh ph d&agrave;nh cho ngi mi ti:  hiu r&otilde; nhng dch v ca ch&iacute;nh ph cung cp cho ngi mi ti, c&aacute;c quyn li v&agrave; ngha v li&ecirc;n quan.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- T&igrave;m hiu v xu hng ph&aacute;t trin c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh ngh: c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh ngh ang thiu nh&acirc;n lc ti li&ecirc;n bang v&agrave; ti a phng, iu kin v bng cp v&agrave; tr&igrave;nh  cn thit i vi tng ngh th&ocirc;ng qua c&aacute;c d liu thng k&ecirc; ca ch&iacute;nh ph, qua website hng dn ca ch&iacute;nh ph.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Mua tp ch&iacute; d&agrave;nh cho ngi mi ti ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh nh k, &acirc;y l&agrave; tp ch&iacute; hng dn rt cn thit v&agrave; c&oacute; nhiu th&ocirc;ng tin b &iacute;ch  to lp cuc sng mi  Canada. Rt nhiu kinh nghim phong ph&uacute; ca nhng ngi nh c th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng trong vic to lp cuc sng mi m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; th hc tp.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">2. Tham gia v&agrave;o c&aacute;c cng ng ngh nghip</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Tham gia v&agrave;o c&aacute;c forum tr&ecirc;n mng: c&aacute;c din &agrave;n n&agrave;y s cung cp c&aacute;c c&acirc;u hi v&agrave; nhng t&igrave;nh hung rt thc t ca nhng ngi c&ugrave;ng ngh nghip v&agrave; c&ugrave;ng mi quan t&acirc;m vi bn. D liu c lu tr t qu&aacute; kh ti hin ti v&agrave; c&oacute; th tham khao online bt c thi gian n&agrave;o.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- To ra c&aacute;c quan h h tr cho ph&aacute;t trin ngh nghip ca bn</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ Quan h vi cng ng ngi Vit: nhng ngi c&ugrave;ng ng&ocirc;n ng, vn h&oacute;a v&agrave; &atilde; nh c l&acirc;u nm ti nc s ti, h c&oacute; nhiu kinh nghim  chia s t c&aacute;ch kim vic, kinh doanh v&agrave; kinh nghim sng.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ Tham gia c&aacute;c c&acirc;u lc b d&agrave;nh cho ngi mi ti: c&aacute;c c&acirc;u lc b n&agrave;y thng do ch&iacute;nh ph a phng to ra nhm to m&ocirc;i trng giao lu cho nhng ngi mi ti. Bng c&aacute;ch tham gia c&aacute;c c&acirc;u lc b n&agrave;y bn s c&oacute; nhiu bn b&egrave; hn v&agrave; c&oacute; th&ecirc;m nhhng kinh nghim ca nhng ngi c&ugrave;ng cnh ng, c&aacute;ch thc v&agrave; c&aacute;c b&agrave;i hc m&agrave; nhng ngi &oacute; &atilde; tri qua.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Tham gia v&agrave;o c&aacute;c c&acirc;u lc b ngh nghip, gp g nhng ngi c&oacute; kinh nghim trong lnh vc bn mun l&agrave;m, ng thi c&oacute; th qua trung t&acirc;m h tr ngi mi ti, h c&oacute; th t&igrave;m kim nhng ngi c&oacute; kinh nghim trong lnh vc bn la chn ngh nghip  hn gp v&agrave; chia s kinh nghim cho bn. &acirc;y l&agrave; nhng ngi l&agrave;m vic h&ograve;an to&agrave;n thin nguyn.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Tham gia v&agrave;o c&aacute;c cng ng v&agrave; hot ng x&atilde; hi kh&aacute;c nhau nu bn cm thy hp vi s th&iacute;ch v&agrave; c&oacute; li cho ph&aacute;t trin mi quan h v&agrave; ngh nghip sau n&agrave;y.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">3. X&acirc;y dng k hoch hc tp</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Hc tp fulltime hay b&aacute;n thi gian: T&ugrave;y theo iu kin kinh t v&agrave; ho&agrave;n cnh tng ngi  ng k&yacute; hc fulltime hay hc b&aacute;n thi gian. Ti Canada c&oacute; rt nhiu kh&oacute;a hc kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; th la chn thi gian (c&oacute; nhng bui hc v&agrave;o bui ti, v&agrave;o ch nht, th by...) v&agrave; c&aacute;ch thc hc ph&ugrave; hp vi m&igrave;nh. Kh&ocirc;ng nht thit l&uacute;c n&agrave;o cng phi c&oacute; mt tr&ecirc;n lp, ch cn l&agrave; vt qua y  c&aacute;c k thi l&agrave; c cp bng (c&oacute; nhiu ngi ch ly t&agrave;i liu v t hc, thi gian l&ecirc;n lp cng rt &iacute;t).</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- i vi nhng ngi &atilde; c&oacute; bng cp v&agrave; kinh nghim l&agrave;m vic ti Vit Nam th&igrave; n&ecirc;n tn dng n&oacute;, ng t ti rng c&aacute;c bng cp v&agrave; kinh nghim n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr, C th nu bn tng hc i hc ti Vit Nam th&igrave; khi hc li i hc b&ecirc;n Canada c&ugrave;ng ng&agrave;nh s kh&ocirc;ng phi chu nhiu iu kin v&agrave; hc nhiu m&ocirc;n hc nh ngi cha tng hc ng&agrave;nh &oacute;. Hoc c&oacute; nhiu doanh nghip khi h cn ngi l&agrave;m, nu bn c&oacute; bng cp ti Vit Nam s c u ti&ecirc;n tuyn dng hn l&agrave; ngi kh&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kinh nghim v&agrave; ch doanh nghip s &agrave;o to b sung th&ecirc;m k nng cn thit  l&agrave;m tt <a title=\"c&ocirc;ng vic part time\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">c&ocirc;ng vic part time</a>. Ti Canada cng c&oacute; mt dch v nhm &aacute;nh gi&aacute; tr&igrave;nh  v&agrave; k nng ca ngi nhp c, so s&aacute;nh vi ti&ecirc;u chun ngh nghip ca Canada, sau &oacute; t vn cho ngi nhp c b xung th&ecirc;m nhng kin thc, k nng ph&ugrave; hp, kh&ocirc;ng nht thit hc li ht t u.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Hc thc t</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ Tr th&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trc khi l&agrave;m nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n. V&iacute; d bn mun v&agrave;o l&agrave;m vic trong ng&agrave;nh ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng th&igrave; trc ti&ecirc;n n&ecirc;n tr th&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng. Ch cn vi mt s tin nh  m t&agrave;i khan th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th s dng rt nhiu c&aacute;c dch v kh&aacute;c nhau, qua &oacute; bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n hiu c kh&aacute; nhiu v c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vic sau n&agrave;y bn s phi l&agrave;m v&agrave; t&acirc;m l&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng khi m&agrave; bn &atilde; tng s dng thc t sn phm ca ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ L&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c thin nguyn trc khi i l&agrave;m. Trc khi bt tay v&agrave;o mt ngh n&agrave;o &oacute;, nu c&oacute; c hi l&agrave;m thin nguyn th&igrave; bn n&ecirc;n xung phong l&agrave;m. &acirc;y l&agrave; c&aacute;ch rt tt  hc, t&iacute;ch ly kinh nghim thc t v&agrave; m rng quan h bn b&egrave;.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Hc c&aacute;c k nng l&agrave;m vic cn thit</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ K nng giao tip trong doanh nghip</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ Ting Anh.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ K nng vit n xin vic</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ K nng phng vn</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">+ C&aacute;c quyn v&agrave; ngha v ca ngi lao ng</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">Nhng k nng n&agrave;y ti Canada c &agrave;o to min ph&iacute; cho ngi mi ti n&ecirc;n bn ch cn t&igrave;m nhng kh&oacute;a hc v&agrave; ng k&yacute; hc.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">4. T&igrave;m kim vic l&agrave;m</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- C&aacute;c website v&agrave; dch v h tr t&igrave;m kim vic l&agrave;m (ngi lao ng c min ph&iacute;).</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- S dng c&aacute;c mi quan h &atilde; c&oacute; c do bn t to ra trc &oacute; (Ti Canada nhiu c&ocirc;ng vic qua bn b&egrave; v&agrave; ngi th&acirc;n quen gii thiu).</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Tham gia c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y hi ngh nghip: l&agrave; c hi  trao i vi c&aacute;c doanh nghip c&oacute; nhu cu tuyn dng ti a phng. T&ocirc;i &atilde; tham gia c&aacute;c hi ch nh n&agrave;y v&agrave; thu c rt nhiu th&ocirc;ng tin. C&aacute;c doanh nghip kh&aacute; nhit t&igrave;nh gii th&iacute;ch cn k v&agrave; a nhng th&ocirc;ng tin chi tit cho bn v nhng v tr&iacute; h cn, c&ocirc;ng vic m nhn, bng cp cn, gii thiu v doanh nghip ca h.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\">- Trc tip truy cp v&agrave;o website ca c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty m&agrave; bn quan t&acirc;m xem h c&oacute; nhu cu tuyn dng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n hay kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 11.8pt; color: #000000;\"><strong>Nguyn Hng Hi (</strong><em>ngun vnexpress.net</em><strong>)<br /></strong></p>','2011-04-08 15:44:06','admin@jobbid.vn',204,1),(28,'nhung-dieu-co-ban-cua-mot-bien-tap-vien','Nhng iu c bn ca mt bin tp vin','http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2011/04/07/8b7615-job.jpg','Cong viec part time - Thong tin dau thau - Trc s pht trin rm r ca cc hng truyn thng, bo i,, ngh bin tp vin  tr nn c gi hn bao gi ht. Nu bn c  nh bc chn vo lnh vc ny, hy tham kho 7 b quyt di y, chng s gip bn nhanh chng thnh cng hn.','<p>Trc s ph&aacute;t trin rm r ca c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng truyn  th&ocirc;ng, b&aacute;o &agrave;i,&hellip;, ngh bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n &atilde; tr n&ecirc;n c&oacute; gi&aacute; hn bao gi ht.  Nu bn c&oacute; &yacute; nh bc ch&acirc;n v&agrave;o lnh vc n&agrave;y, h&atilde;y tham kho 7 b&iacute; quyt  di &acirc;y, ch&uacute;ng s gi&uacute;p bn nhanh ch&oacute;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng hn.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1. ng k&iacute; v&agrave;o c&aacute;c kh&oacute;a hc vit</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">Mt  bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n gii s c&oacute; kh nng vit tt. H&atilde;y tham gia v&agrave;o mt v&agrave;i  lp hc vit v&agrave; th t tay son ra nhng on vn &yacute; ngha. Bn cn phi  nhn thc c ng ph&aacute;p, c&acirc;u c&uacute; ph&ugrave; hp, v&agrave; kim so&aacute;t c ng&ocirc;n ng m&agrave;  bn vit ra. Tht kh&oacute;  tr th&agrave;nh mt ngi bi&ecirc;n tp gii nu nhng c&acirc;u  n gin bn cng kh&ocirc;ng vit c.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><img src=\"http://dantri.vcmedia.vn/Uploaded/2011/04/07/8b7615-job.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2. Li&ecirc;n h vi b&aacute;o a phng </span></div>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">Ngay  c khi bn c&oacute; th tr th&agrave;nh bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n thi gian, th&igrave; mt ch&uacute;t  kinh nghim thu thp c cng rt hu &iacute;ch. Cng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; hi g&igrave; khi n&oacute;i  chuyn vi bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n ca t b&aacute;o n&agrave;o &oacute;  t&igrave;m hiu c&ocirc;ng vic chi  tit ra sao. Bn c&oacute; th hc c nhiu iu m&igrave;nh cha bit v&agrave; bn c&ograve;n c&oacute;  th bit c &acirc;y liu c&oacute; phi vic m&igrave;nh thc s mun l&agrave;m hay kh&ocirc;ng.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3. c tht nhiu</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">Cng  kh&ocirc;ng bt ng khi ch&uacute;ng ta thng xuy&ecirc;n ph&aacute;t hin c&aacute;c li sai lt vt  tr&ecirc;n nhng mu tin, qung c&aacute;o, v&agrave; &ocirc;i khi c trong tiu thuyt. L&agrave;m mt  bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n &ograve;i hi bn phi c nhiu v&agrave; nhanh. Bn c&agrave;ng c nhiu,  th&igrave; c&agrave;ng d ph&aacute;t hin li sai m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn mt c ng&agrave;y c i c li  mt mu tin.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4. Li&ecirc;n h vi c&aacute;c tp ch ang tuyn bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">T&ugrave;y thuc v&agrave;o loi tp ch&iacute; m&agrave; bn t&igrave;m vic, bn c&oacute; th nhn c mt <a title=\"c&ocirc;ng vic part time\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn\">c&ocirc;ng vic part time</a> hoc to&agrave;n thi gian.&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5. Th hin nim y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m bi&ecirc;n tp</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">Bn  phi th hin mt ch&uacute;t am m&ecirc; khi ng k&iacute; v&agrave;o v tr&iacute; bi&ecirc;n tp. Nu bn  tng c&oacute; kinh nghim trc &oacute;, h&atilde;y nhn mnh iu n&agrave;y vi nh&agrave; tuyn dng   h c&oacute; th bit c. Bn c&agrave;ng th hin m&igrave;nh am m&ecirc; bao nhi&ecirc;u, th&igrave; nh&agrave;  tuyn dng s c&agrave;ng  &yacute; n bn by nhi&ecirc;u.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6. C&oacute; bng li&ecirc;n quan n b&aacute;o ch&iacute;, vn hc, hoc ting anh</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">Ch  cn c&oacute; mt trong ba bng li&ecirc;n quan n c&aacute;c lnh vc tr&ecirc;n s gi&uacute;p bn d  d&agrave;ng tin gn n ngh bi&ecirc;n tp hn v&igrave; hin nay vic khai th&aacute;c tin tc  nc ngo&agrave;i rt ph bin tr&ecirc;n hu ht c&aacute;c b&aacute;o.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">7. C&oacute; kinh nghim l&agrave;m nh&agrave; vn</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">C&aacute;ch  tt nht  tr th&agrave;nh mt bi&ecirc;n tp vi&ecirc;n gii l&agrave; phi c&oacute; kinh nghim  vit l&aacute;ch, cho d&ugrave; l&agrave; &iacute;t hay nhiu. Cng ging nh vic c nhiu, vit  nhiu s gi&uacute;p bn c&oacute; c nn tng ca ng&ocirc;n ng vit v&agrave; d d&agrave;ng bi&ecirc;n tp  c&aacute;c mu tin vit.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Nguyn Th&uacute;y</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 15pt; text-align: right;\">Theo <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">AWT</span></p>','2011-04-13 15:18:53','admin@jobbid.vn',234,1),(29,'biet-can-bang-de-lam-part-time-cuu-canh-cho-nhan-vien-thoi-buoi-nay','Bit cn bng  lm part-time, cu cnh cho nhn vin thi bui ny','http://atpvietnam.com/Library/Images/dangers-of-social-networking.jpeg','cong viec part time - viec lam ban thoi gian - Trong nhng nm 80, cc chng trnh v cc b phim truyn hnh ni v kh nng cn bng cng vic ca nhng b m va lo i lm kim tin, va chm lo tt vic nh  thu ht c s ch  ca c nc M','<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-&nbsp;</span><span><span style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Trong  nhng nm 80, c&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; c&aacute;c b phim truyn h&igrave;nh n&oacute;i v kh  nng c&acirc;n bng c&ocirc;ng vic ca nhng b&agrave; m va lo i l&agrave;m kim tin, va  chm lo tt vic nh&agrave; &atilde; thu h&uacute;t c s ch&uacute; &yacute; ca c nc M. </span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 115%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://atpvietnam.com/Library/Images/dangers-of-social-networking.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /><br /></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Kh&ocirc;ng  th ng rng nhng ngi ph n &oacute; &atilde; c&acirc;n bng c c&ocirc;ng vic b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i  vi tr&aacute;ch nhim gia &igrave;nh. L&uacute;c n&agrave;y, dng nh mi ngi hay &iacute;t nht l&agrave;  c&aacute;c v ch doanh nghip &atilde; nhn ra rng rt kh&oacute; khn cho nhng ngi  c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n khi h phi c&acirc;n bng cuc sng ni c&ocirc;ng s v&agrave; cuc sng ri&ecirc;ng  t ca m&igrave;nh.<br /><br /><strong>Cn c&oacute; nhiu tin</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Trong mt  kho s&aacute;t ca Career Builder u nm 2010, 19% nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; xu hng t&igrave;m  th&ecirc;m cho m&igrave;nh mt c&ocirc;ng vic th 2 trong nm nay  c&oacute; c nhiu tin  hn. Nhng bn hp ng l&agrave;m vic t do v&agrave; nhng c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian  kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p h kim th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c khon thu nhp ph tr cn thit   trang chi cuc sng h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y na.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Chuy&ecirc;n  gia truyn th&ocirc;ng Laura Lang &atilde; iu h&agrave;nh tt c&ocirc;ng ty chuy&ecirc;n v lnh vc  quan h c&ocirc;ng ch&uacute;ng v&agrave; tip th trong sut 20 nm qua, trc khi s suy  tho&aacute;i kinh t nh hng kh&ocirc;ng tt ti c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ca c&ocirc;. Th&aacute;ng 3 va  qua, Lang t&igrave;m c cho m&igrave;nh mt c&ocirc;ng vic d ph&ograve;ng, v&agrave; ri n&oacute; &atilde; tr  th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng vic c nh l&acirc;u d&agrave;i ca c&ocirc;.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Lang  n&oacute;i rng &ldquo;Hin ti t&ocirc;i ang l&agrave;m c hai c&ocirc;ng vic c&ugrave;ng mt l&uacute;c v&agrave; t&ocirc;i  ang c gng t&igrave;m c&aacute;ch tho&aacute;t khi t&igrave;nh trng t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh hin ti th&ocirc;ng qua  c&ocirc;ng vic c nh mi ca m&igrave;nh&rdquo;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n  c&acirc;n bng c hai l&agrave; vic  kh&ocirc;ng h d d&agrave;ng v&agrave; c&ocirc; y &atilde; quyt nh dn dn s b hn c&ocirc;ng vic  trc kia.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">&ldquo;Rt  kh&oacute;  c&oacute; th a ra mt quyt nh, nhng t&ocirc;i &atilde; chn s t b ho&agrave;n  to&agrave;n c&ocirc;ng vic tip th by l&acirc;u nay ca t&ocirc;i.  sng s&oacute;t trong nn kinh  t hin nay qu tht rt kh&oacute; khn, t&ocirc;i cn s n nh. V&agrave; hin nhi&ecirc;n c&aacute;c  c&ocirc;ng ty ln hn c&oacute; th &aacute;p ng c iu &oacute;&rdquo;, c&ocirc; n&oacute;i.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Tuy  nhi&ecirc;n, i vi mt s nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n mt c&ocirc;ng vic duy nht kh&ocirc;ng   trang  tri cuc sng. Jessica Ayers cho rng l&agrave;m 2 c&ocirc;ng vic c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c l&agrave; cn  thit  c&oacute; th kim  tin. Mt tun c&ocirc; phi mt &iacute;t nht 40h/tun   l&agrave;m vic cho mt c&ocirc;ng ty quan h c&ocirc;ng ch&uacute;ng v&agrave; l&agrave; l t&acirc;n b&aacute;n thi gian  ti mt c&acirc;u lc b th thao. Mc d&ugrave; vic c&acirc;n bng c 2 c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y  khin c&ocirc; phi thc dy l&uacute;c 4:30 s&aacute;ng 2 ln/ tun  bt u mt ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m  vic, v&agrave; ch c ngh duy nht ng&agrave;y th 7, th&igrave; Ayers vn cho rng s  hi sinh n&agrave;y l&agrave; cn thit.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Nhng bt li v&agrave; thun li ca vic c&acirc;n bng nhiu c&ocirc;ng vic </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Deanna  Miller cng i mt vi mt t&igrave;nh hung tng t. Trong khi t&igrave;m mt c&ocirc;ng  vic to&agrave;n thi gian, c&ocirc; &atilde; chp nhn l&agrave;m mt c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian 25  ting mt tun v&agrave; dn m nhim th&ecirc;m vai tr&ograve; mt nh&agrave; b&aacute;o t do. Hn th  na, c&ocirc; &atilde; bt u mt c&ocirc;ng vic th hai - to&agrave;n thi gian vi hp ng  l&agrave;m vic 20h/ tun. Tht may mn, cui c&ugrave;ng c&ocirc; cng &atilde; t&igrave;m c mt c&ocirc;ng  vic c nh, tuy nhi&ecirc;n Miller vn tip tc c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian kia  ca m&igrave;nh, iu &oacute; c&oacute; ngha l&agrave; c&ocirc; y thng xuy&ecirc;n phi l&agrave;m vic c 7  ng&agrave;y mt tun.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Miller  n&oacute;i rng &ldquo;Kh&oacute; khn ln nht ca t&ocirc;i l&agrave; t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute;  thi gian cho  gia &igrave;nh, bn b&egrave; v&agrave; t&ocirc;i cn phi sp xp li thi gian ca m&igrave;nh. Nh  th&aacute;ng 8 va qua t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng ch l&agrave;m vic ti 40h t th 2 ti th 6 m&agrave; c&ograve;n  l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m 14h v&agrave;o hai ng&agrave;y cui tun, v&agrave; nhn th&ecirc;m mt d &aacute;n vit b&aacute;o t  do, c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y ngn cu t&ocirc;i ti 30h mt th&aacute;ng. Thi gian qua, t&ocirc;i  va n&oacute;i vi bn b&egrave; v&agrave; gia &igrave;nh l&agrave; t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; thi gian rnh trong  th&aacute;ng 8 v&agrave; h&atilde;y ki&ecirc;n nhn. V&igrave; v chng t&ocirc;i cha c&oacute; con, n&ecirc;n chng t&ocirc;i v&agrave;  t&ocirc;i ch qun qu&yacute;t b&ecirc;n nhau khi ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th, tuy nhi&ecirc;n ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i  bit rng iu n&agrave;y s kh&ocirc;ng m&atilde;i l&agrave; cuc sng ca ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Mc  d&ugrave; chng ca Miller ang t&igrave;m kim mt c&ocirc;ng vic n nh, nhng h vn  thy c mt tt ca vic cn c&oacute; hai vic l&agrave;m mt l&uacute;c. Miller cho bit  &ldquo;Tht s, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i va tr xong khon n cui c&ugrave;ng v&agrave; vn tip tc l&agrave;m  nhng vic vt, nhng vic l&agrave;m t do  c&oacute; th c&oacute;  tin  mua nh&agrave; v&agrave;  nu&ocirc;i dy con c&aacute;i sau n&agrave;y&rdquo;. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Gi&aacute; tr ca vic &ldquo;l&agrave;m nhiu vic mt l&uacute;c&rdquo; </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Nu  nh bn ang  trong t&igrave;nh trng gp g ng nghip c&ograve;n nhiu hn c gp  con th&igrave; vic lng nghe nhng mt t&iacute;ch cc ca vic l&agrave;m nhiu vic mt  l&uacute;c kh&ocirc;ng phi l&agrave; iu bn quan t&acirc;m. Mc d&ugrave; i vi nhiu ngi, phi  l&agrave;m hai n ba c&ocirc;ng vic mt l&uacute;c l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th&iacute;ch hp cho lm, nhng  Denise Beeson li ngh rng &oacute; l&agrave; c&aacute;ch th&ocirc;ng minh  l&agrave;m n. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Beeson  cho bit &ldquo;Hin ti t&ocirc;i c&oacute; 3 c&ocirc;ng vic: T&ocirc;i dy cho c&aacute;c lp hc nh v  qun l&yacute; kinh doanh ti mt trng cao ng ti a phng, t vn v  tip th v&agrave; nhu cu t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh cho c&aacute;c doanh nghip nh, v&agrave; cui c&ugrave;ng l&agrave;  b&aacute;n c&aacute;c chng tr&igrave;nh vay vn thng mi. Vi 3 ngun thu nhp, t&ocirc;i nhn  ra rng khi t&ocirc;i mt mt vic, hai c&ocirc;ng vic c&ograve;n li vn c&oacute; th gi&uacute;p t&ocirc;i  sng tt&rdquo;.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">S  tht l&agrave; Beeson tin c&acirc;u thn ch&uacute; ca c&ocirc;&nbsp;&ldquo;L&agrave;m th n&agrave;o  sng nu kh&ocirc;ng  c&oacute; vic l&agrave;m&rdquo; &atilde; chun b tinh thn cho c&ocirc;  &oacute;n nhn nhng xu hng  vic l&agrave;m sp ti.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Nn  kinh t kh&oacute; khn cng khin cuc sng ca c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n gp tr ngi.  Nu nh bn c&oacute; th t&igrave;m thy mt mt t&iacute;ch cc ca vn  n&agrave;y, th&igrave; c&oacute; l  ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; th thy c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n khe nh th n&agrave;o, v&agrave; kh nng ca h  l&agrave; g&igrave;. <br /><br />H c&oacute; th iu hng ngh nghip  chun b mi th cho ch&iacute;nh h trong trng hp mt mt vic l&agrave;m trong tng lai.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>Lan Anh</strong> </span><em><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(Ngun CBS, MSN)</span></em></p>','2011-04-16 19:42:24','admin@jobbid.vn',317,1),(30,'viec-lam-ban-thoi-gian-xau-hoc-thue','Vic lm bn thi gian xu: Hc thu','http://www.svvn.vn/Controls/ThumbnailSizeOrigin.aspx?swidth=200&sheight=0&imageurl=upload/20101012/Hoc.jpg','viec lam ban thoi gian - tim viec ban thoi gian - 50.000 ng/bui hc, 200.000 ng/bui thi - nhng khon tin ny hin ang l lng part-time ca nhiu sinh vin khi i hc thu ti cc lp lin thng, ti chc. Vn  khng mi nhng vn din ra, ti sao?','<p><span class=\"tomtat\" style=\"font-family: tahoma; font-weight: bold; text-align: justify;\">(SVVN)50.000 ng/bui hc, 200.000 ng/bui thi - nhng khon tin n&agrave;y hin ang l&agrave; &ldquo;lng&rdquo; part-time ca nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n khi i hc thu&ecirc; ti c&aacute;c lp li&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng, ti chc. Vn  kh&ocirc;ng mi nhng vn din ra, ti sao?</span></p>\n<p><strong><br />Ngh &ldquo;h&aacute;i ra tin&rdquo;</strong><br />ang hc li&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng ti trng H Lao ng - X&atilde; hi, H. cho bit, trong<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>lp<span id=\"link0\" class=\"VietAdTextLink\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; display: inline; border-bottom: 1px solid #2b9900; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #006400; background-color: transparent; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>thnh thong li c&oacute; nhng gng mt &ldquo;l&rdquo;. C&ograve;n tr, li mau mn n&ecirc;n H. thng xuy&ecirc;n c c&aacute;c bc anh ch nh t&igrave;m ngi hc h. Mi bui hc k&eacute;o d&agrave;i 2 &ndash; 3 ting, sinh vi&ecirc;n hc thu&ecirc; s c &ldquo;ch&rdquo; tr 30.000 ng. Theo H., &acirc;y l&agrave; mc th&ugrave; lao &ldquo;b&egrave;o&rdquo; nht trong c&aacute;c trng. &ldquo; trng H<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>Kinh t<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>hay Hc vin Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng, th&ugrave; lao phi l&agrave; 50.000 ng/bui&rdquo; &ndash; H. cho bit.</p>\n<p>Tip x&uacute;c vi T., mt sinh vi&ecirc;n c&oacute; &ldquo;th&acirc;m ni&ecirc;n&rdquo; trong &ldquo;ngh&rdquo; hc h, T. cng cho hay, c&ocirc; ang hc gi&uacute;p mt ch &ldquo;bu b&iacute;&rdquo; ti Hc vin Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng. Tin c&ocirc;ng  &acirc;y l&agrave; 50.000 ng/bui hc v&agrave; 200.000 ng/bui thi. Kh&ocirc;ng ch c&oacute; lp T. ang &ldquo;din th ch&acirc;n&rdquo; mi c&oacute; hin tng n&agrave;y m&agrave; ti lp kh&aacute;c ca Hc vin Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng cng din ra t&igrave;nh trng tng t. Mt ln v&agrave;o &ldquo;nhm lp&rdquo;, T. &atilde; &ldquo;ng&rdquo; phi mt sinh vi&ecirc;n kh&aacute;c cng i hc thu&ecirc;. T. bo, c&ocirc;ng vic hc h rt n gin, ch vic n &ldquo;im danh&rdquo; ri ngi &ldquo;ng&aacute;p&rdquo; hoc &ldquo;ng&rdquo; l&agrave; &atilde; c tin. Mi tun hc 3 bui, tr&ograve;m tr&egrave;m mi th&aacute;ng thu nhp ca T. t c&ocirc;ng vic &ldquo;tay tr&aacute;i&rdquo; n&agrave;y cng kh&ocirc;ng n ni n&agrave;o. &ldquo;Hc thu&ecirc; nh th n&agrave;y m&igrave;nh c hng 100% c&ocirc;ng sc b ra. L&agrave;m gia s, va vt v, va mt li c&ograve;n b tr u tr u&ocirc;i cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty m&ocirc;i gii&rdquo; &ndash; T. ging gii. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vy,  to &ldquo;c&ocirc;ng n vic l&agrave;m&rdquo; cho c&aacute;c bn kh&aacute;c, mi ln c&oacute; ch n&agrave;o &oacute; trong lp cn ngi hc h l&agrave; T. gii thiu ngay.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br /><strong><br />Chuyn d&agrave;i nhiu tp</strong><br /><br />Hc h nh&agrave; trng c&oacute; bit kh&ocirc;ng? T. khng nh l&agrave; trng c&oacute; bit nhng ch ngi i thu&ecirc; mi b &ldquo;x l&yacute;&rdquo; c&ograve;n ngi hc thu&ecirc; th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng vn  g&igrave;. c bit, hin nay c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c qun l&yacute; sinh vi&ecirc;n ti c&aacute;c lp ti chc, li&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng  c&aacute;c trng u bng h&igrave;nh thc im danh v&agrave; kim tra th. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, thi gian hc din ra bui ti n&ecirc;n ngi hc thu&ecirc; c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng i ph&oacute;. Kh&ocirc;ng nhng th, k c  nhng bui thi, ngi hc thu&ecirc; ch cn vin l&yacute; do &ldquo;qu&ecirc;n th&rdquo; l&agrave; vn c&oacute; th thay vai tr&oacute;t lt.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br /><br />Tt nhi&ecirc;n, kh&ocirc;ng phi lp hc n&agrave;o cng lng lo. H. cho bit, nm ngo&aacute;i, ti lp li&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng ca c&ocirc;  trng H Lao ng - X&atilde; hi &atilde; c&oacute; mt v&agrave;i ngi b &igrave;nh ch hc do b nh&agrave; trng ph&aacute;t hin thu&ecirc; ngi hc h. Kh&ocirc;ng nhng th, i vi nhng ngi hc h cng b trng gi c&ocirc;ng vn th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v trng v&agrave; v tn a phng. Nm nay, trc t&igrave;nh trng hc k mi bt u c hn mt th&aacute;ng nhng trong lp &atilde; ph&aacute;t hin ngi ang hc h, nh&agrave; trng &atilde; cnh b&aacute;o s tin h&agrave;nh kim tra gt gao hn.</p>\n<p><br /><br /></p>\n<div><img src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/upload/20101012/Hoc%20thue.JPG\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Hoc thue.JPG\" width=\"450\" height=\"211\" /></div>\n<div><br /><br />&nbsp;</div>\n<p><strong>Biu hin lch lc ca x&atilde; hi s&iacute;nh bng cp</strong><br /><br />&Ocirc;ng Nguyn ng Dng, Trng ph&ograve;ng &agrave;o to, trng H Lao ng &ndash; X&atilde; hi cho bit, v&agrave;o u mi nm hc, trng thng ph bin rt k cho sinh vi&ecirc;n c&aacute;c lp li&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng, ti chc nm c ni quy, quy ch, trong &oacute; c&oacute; vn  hc h, hc thu&ecirc;. C&aacute;c bui hc, ngo&agrave;i ging vi&ecirc;n ng lp, c&aacute;c lp c&ograve;n c&oacute; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ca Ph&ograve;ng &agrave;o to tham gia gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t. Nu ph&aacute;t hin trng hp n&agrave;o hc h, trng s &igrave;nh ch hc tp i vi ngi thu&ecirc; hc. C&ograve;n ngi hc thu&ecirc;, trng s gi th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v a phng hoc trng ni ngi n&agrave;y ang theo hc  x l&yacute;.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br /><br />Bin ph&aacute;p m&agrave; &ocirc;ng Dng n&ecirc;u ra ph&aacute;t huy hiu qu n &acirc;u, chc bn c cng &atilde; r&otilde;. C&oacute; &ldquo;cung&rdquo; th&igrave; tt s c&oacute; &ldquo;cu&rdquo;. Nhiu chuy&ecirc;n gia gi&aacute;o dc nhn x&eacute;t, chuyn thu&ecirc; hc - hc thu&ecirc; cng ging chuyn bng tin s... mua  nc ngo&agrave;i, u l&agrave; nhng biu hin ca t s&iacute;nh bng cp. Vy n&ecirc;n chng n&agrave;o bng cp c&ograve;n c coi l&agrave; ti&ecirc;u chun tuyn dng, ct nhc (thay v&igrave; ch n&ecirc;n c xem nh ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute; tham kho), chng &oacute;, vn s c&ograve;n ngi c thu&ecirc; hc v&agrave; phn khi coi &oacute; nh mt part-time hp dn.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><br /><strong><br /></strong><em><strong>&Ocirc;ng Ng Duy Anh</strong>, V trng V C&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c Hc sinh, sinh vi&ecirc;n (B GD &ndash; T) cho bit: &acirc;y l&agrave; iu &aacute;ng tr&aacute;ch. Mn kin thc ca ngi kh&aacute;c  &aacute;nh b&oacute;ng t&ecirc;n tui ca m&igrave;nh l&agrave; iu kh&ocirc;ng th chp nhn c. B GD - T khuyn c&aacute;o c&aacute;c c s &agrave;o to kim tra ngi hc mt c&aacute;ch nghi&ecirc;m ngt  l&agrave;m sao ngn chn t&igrave;nh trng n&agrave;y, lp hc i theo &uacute;ng hng, ngi hc i hc mt c&aacute;ch nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c. Ngi i thu&ecirc; ngi kh&aacute;c hc h &atilde; c&oacute; ch t&agrave;i x l&yacute; nh &igrave;nh ch hc tp hay buc th&ocirc;i hc, c&ograve;n ngi hc thu&ecirc; cng phi x l&yacute; nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c. Ngn chn t&igrave;nh trng n&agrave;y phi xut ph&aacute;t t ch&iacute;nh c&aacute;c thy ng lp. C&aacute;c thy kh&ocirc;ng th n lp dy m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng bit ngi ngi nghe l&agrave; ai. B phn qun l&yacute; lp cng phi gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t cht ch, kh&ocirc;ng th d d&atilde;i.<br /><br /><strong>Nguyn Thu Nga</strong>, mt sinh vi&ecirc;n trng H C&ocirc;ng o&agrave;n cho rng, hc tp l&agrave; mt c&ocirc;ng vic &ograve;i hi t&iacute;nh nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c, kh&ocirc;ng th thu&ecirc; hay nh ngi kh&aacute;c l&agrave;m thay. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; th, mc d&ugrave; i hc thu&ecirc; c&oacute; th gi&uacute;p Nga nhn c mc th&ugrave; lao cao hn so vi c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vic part-time kh&aacute;c (m&agrave; li nh&agrave;n hn) nhng bn s kh&ocirc;ng bao gi chp nhn mt &ldquo;li  ngh khim nh&atilde;&rdquo; nh vy. Nga mong c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n d&ugrave; c&ograve;n kh&oacute; khn h&atilde;y dng cm n&oacute;i &ldquo;kh&ocirc;ng&rdquo; vi t nn hc thu&ecirc;!</em><br /><br /></p>\n<div><strong>H&agrave; Vi </strong>(ngun svvn.vn)</div>','2011-04-20 15:32:37','admin@jobbid.vn',377,1),(31,'part-time-sau-0h','Part-time sau 0h','http://www.svvn.vn/Controls/ThumbnailSizeOrigin.aspx?swidth=200&sheight=0&imageurl=upload/20100914/Da%20Nang.JPG','cong viec part time - viec lam ban thoi gian  -  Nng 24h m. Ging ng vng lng. KTX im ng. Nhng u  trong thnh ph vn cn nhng sinh vin khoc ln mnh chic o xanh cng nhn thc trng m  kim thm thu nhp, trang tri cho cuc sng ','<p><span class=\"tomtat\"><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"c&ocirc;ng vic part time\" src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/Controls/ThumbnailSizeOrigin.aspx?swidth=200&amp;sheight=0&amp;imageurl=upload/20100914/Da%20Nang.JPG\" alt=\"cong viec part time\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong>(SVVN)&agrave; Nng 24h &ecirc;m. Ging ng vng lng. KTX im  ng. Nhng &acirc;u &oacute; trong th&agrave;nh ph vn c&ograve;n nhng sinh vi&ecirc;n kho&aacute;c l&ecirc;n  m&igrave;nh chic &aacute;o xanh c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n thc trng &ecirc;m  kim th&ecirc;m thu nhp, trang  tri cho cuc sng&hellip; </strong></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Nhng gic ng kh&ocirc;ng tr&ograve;n</strong></p>\n<p>Nm  tr&ecirc;n qun Li&ecirc;n Chiu, TP. &agrave; Nng, Khu c&ocirc;ng nghip H&ograve;a Kh&aacute;nh l&agrave; ni  ang thu h&uacute;t nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n n np h s xin vic, c bit l&agrave; 3 c&ocirc;ng  ty: Mabuchi Motor, in t Vit Hoa v&agrave; Maxtris.</p>\n<p>Do  ban ng&agrave;y phi c&oacute; mt  ging ng n&ecirc;n hu ht sinh vi&ecirc;n khi i l&agrave;m  c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n u ng k&yacute; ca &ecirc;m (Mabuchi Motor v&agrave; Maxtris bt u t 22h  n 6h s&aacute;ng h&ocirc;m sau; in t Vit Hoa t 18h n 6h s&aacute;ng h&ocirc;m sau). V&igrave;  l&agrave;m vic  khong thi gian nh th n&ecirc;n sinh vi&ecirc;n thng chp nhn \"hy  sinh\" gic ng, thi gian sinh hot theo &oacute; cng b x&aacute;o trn.</p>\n<p>H.  T. Anh (lp 09CTL, trng H S phm) t&acirc;m s: \"u nm, b&agrave;i v &iacute;t n&ecirc;n  m&igrave;nh tranh th i l&agrave;m kim th&ecirc;m thu nhp, ban ng&agrave;y i hc n&ecirc;n phi l&agrave;m  ca &ecirc;m, l&agrave;m ca &ecirc;m lng cng cao hn (2,4 triu ng/th&aacute;ng). L&uacute;c u  th&igrave; hay mt ng, gi quen ri, rnh l&uacute;c n&agrave;o th&igrave; m&igrave;nh phi c m&agrave; ng,  kh&ocirc;ng ng th&igrave; chng c&oacute; sc m&agrave; i l&agrave;m\". \"Ng ng&agrave;y c&agrave;y &ecirc;m\" n&ecirc;n nu lch  hc  trng c ng&agrave;y th&igrave; qu l&agrave; &aacute;c mng. Gii ph&aacute;p tm thi m&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n  l&agrave;m &ecirc;m chn l&agrave; c&uacute;p tit (nu kh&ocirc;ng im danh)   nh&agrave; ng b&ugrave;&hellip;</p>\n<p><strong>L&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng d</strong></p>\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng cn ngoi h&igrave;nh p, k nng giao tip hay tr&igrave;nh  ngoi ng. Mt giy kh&aacute;m sc khe, <span id=\"link2\" class=\"VietAdTextLink\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; white-space: nowrap;\">tt nghip</span> <span id=\"link1\" class=\"VietAdTextLink\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; white-space: nowrap;\">lp</span> 9 tr l&ecirc;n,  tui t 19 n 29 l&agrave;  iu kin l&agrave;m ti khu c&ocirc;ng  nghip. Nhng kh&ocirc;ng phi v&igrave; th m&agrave; ngh rng l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n l&agrave; mt  part-time \"d xi\". Theo kinh nghim ca nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n th&igrave; c&ocirc;ng vic  thng y&ecirc;u cu nhng phm cht t m, chu kh&oacute; v&agrave; ki&ecirc;n nhn.</p>\n<p>L.  T. Diu, mt sinh vi&ecirc;n nm th 2, nhn dp bush (mt kh&acirc;u chun b linh  kin  lp r&aacute;p) ti Mabuchi Motor chia s: \"C&ocirc;ng vic kh&ocirc;ng kh&oacute; nhng  phi ch&uacute; &yacute; xem ngi ta hng dn ri l&agrave;m cho &uacute;ng, khi l&agrave;m phi cn  thn, sai l&agrave; b t trng, ch qun mng lin. M&igrave;nh mi v&agrave;o l&agrave;m n&ecirc;n c  xp b&ecirc;n c ng, c y&ecirc;u cu g&igrave; th&igrave; l&agrave;m ny, chy i chy li mt  lm!\".</p>\n<p>Do l&agrave;m trong mt b phn ca mt d&acirc;y  chuyn li&ecirc;n tc n&ecirc;n \"nhanh\" l&agrave; y&ecirc;u cu bt buc v&agrave; cng l&agrave; &aacute;p lc thc  s: \"Nu mt &ecirc;m ngi ta giao cho m&igrave;nh 10.000 n v h&agrave;ng th&igrave; phi chy  cho ht, kh&ocirc;ng  h&agrave;ng s b vit giy cnh c&aacute;o, ng&agrave;y h&ocirc;m sau phi chy  th&ecirc;m s lng v&agrave;o cho  h&agrave;ng, nu kh&ocirc;ng cui th&aacute;ng s b&nbsp; tr lng\" -  Thanh Chi (c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n ng m&aacute;y, d&aacute;n h&agrave;ng nh&agrave; m&aacute;y nha Maxtris) cho bit.</p>\n<p>Khu  c&ocirc;ng nghip H&ograve;a Kh&aacute;nh l&agrave; m&ocirc;i trng ch d&agrave;nh cho nhng ngi c&oacute; sc  khe thuc v&agrave;o loi \"khng\". Thc khuya li&ecirc;n tc, ng mt ch nguy&ecirc;n  &ecirc;m (b&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng on), m&ocirc;i trng bao quanh l&agrave; in, m&aacute;y lnh, ting n  m&aacute;y m&oacute;c, bi vi, h&oacute;a cht&hellip; gp li   thy sc khe s b t&agrave;n ph&aacute;  kh&ocirc;ng thng tic nh th n&agrave;o.</p>\n<p><strong>Tri nghim v&agrave; thu hiu</strong></p>\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng  phi c&ocirc;ng vic phc v cho chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh hc tp, c&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng phi c&ocirc;ng  vic ca nim am m&ecirc;, thm ch&iacute; l&agrave; rt vt v nhng l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n cng  mang li cho sinh vi&ecirc;n nhiu tri nghim kh&aacute;c bit. \"C&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y cha  hn gi l&agrave; th th&aacute;ch bn th&acirc;n, n gin l&agrave; tri nghim m&agrave; th&ocirc;i. Mt  tht, nhng nh n&oacute; m&igrave;nh hiu hn c rt nhiu iu v cuc sng. M&igrave;nh  nhn ra, ngh n&agrave;o cng &aacute;ng qu&yacute; c, bi trc &acirc;y m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng coi trng  ngi lao ng ch&acirc;n tay, nhng khi i l&agrave;m m&igrave;nh hc c  c&aacute;c c&ocirc;, c&aacute;c  ch rt nhiu iu nh s ki&ecirc;n nhn, kh nng chu ng&hellip;\" - Thanh Chi  (H &agrave; Nng) k v nhng ngi bn c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n ln tui ca m&igrave;nh.</p>\n<p>C&ugrave;ng tri nghim nh Chi, Ho&agrave;i Xu&acirc;n (nm th 3, trng C <span id=\"link3\" class=\"VietAdTextLink\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px; white-space: nowrap;\">Kinh t</span> - K hoch) l&yacute; gii: \"T&ugrave;y ho&agrave;n cnh m&agrave; bit c&aacute;ch th&iacute;ch nghi, ng&agrave;y trc  th&igrave; c&nbsp; cho rng m&igrave;nh l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n, l&agrave; ngi \"c&oacute; ch\" n&ecirc;n chm t&iacute; l&agrave; t  &aacute;i lin, nhng  &acirc;y, m&igrave;nh phi r&egrave;n t&iacute;nh chu ng\".</p>\n<p>C&ograve;n  vi &ocirc;ng (nm th 2, khoa Ng vn, trng H S phm), sau hai th&aacute;ng  th sc, bn &atilde; hc c k nng l&agrave;m vic nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c, nhanh nhn: \"L&agrave;m  ra l&agrave;m, chi ra chi, l&uacute;c n&agrave;o cng phi hc hi bi c&ocirc;ng vic ca m&igrave;nh  &ograve;i hi phi bit nhiu c&ocirc;ng on. i l&agrave;m mi bit thng ba m. Th&iacute;ch  nht khi cm nhng ng tin lng tr&ecirc;n tay do th&agrave;nh&nbsp; qu lao ng em  li, cm gi&aacute;c m&igrave;nh l&agrave; mt ngi trng th&agrave;nh\".</p>\n<p>Khi  c hi c&oacute; d nh l&agrave;m l&acirc;u d&agrave;i  Maxtris kh&ocirc;ng, Ho&agrave;i Xu&acirc;n (c&oacute; thu nhp  2,5 triu ng/th&aacute;ng) khuy&ecirc;n: \"Lng cao, nhng m&igrave;nh ngh sinh vi&ecirc;n  kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n ham kim tin m&agrave; b&aacute;m tr c&ocirc;ng vic n&agrave;y l&acirc;u. Thc khuya l&agrave;m  vic nhiu s rt nh hng n vic hc. C&oacute; v&agrave;i ln mt qu&aacute;, chu kh&ocirc;ng  ni, m&igrave;nh phi c&uacute;p tit  nh&agrave; ng b&ugrave;. M&igrave;nh ch l&agrave;m khong na th&aacute;ng na  th&ocirc;i, t&iacute;ch  tin hc ph&iacute; s xin ngh\".</p>\n<p>C&oacute;  l, khi ang c&ograve;n l&agrave; sinh vi&ecirc;n, \"ngh\" c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n ch n&ecirc;n l&agrave; mt part  -time thi v, bi bn s chng th ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh tt vic hc nu lu&ocirc;n   trong t&igrave;nh trng \"s&aacute;ng ng ging ng - ti l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m\".</p>\n<p>(ngun www.svvn.vn)</p>','2011-04-23 09:22:35','admin@jobbid.vn',482,1),(32,'cong-tac-vien-bao--part-time-hot-cua-teen-trong-mua-he-','Cng tc vin bo  Part time hot ca teen trong ma h ','http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/06/21/22610DSbao.jpg','cong viec part time - thng tin u thu- Qua nhng bi phng vn, nhng bui chp hnh, nhng bi phng s, cc teen c dp tr chuyn vi c nhng nhn vt ni ting. Nht l khi lm CTV ca cc t bo gii tr th chuyn gp cc Star l bnh thng nh cm ba.','<p class=\"sapo\">Qua nhng b&agrave;i phng vn, nhng bui chp h&igrave;nh, nhng b&agrave;i  ph&oacute;ng s, c&aacute;c teen c&oacute; dp tr&ograve; chuyn vi c nhng nh&acirc;n vt ni ting.  Nht l&agrave; khi l&agrave;m CTV ca c&aacute;c t b&aacute;o gii tr&iacute; th&igrave; chuyn gp c&aacute;c &ldquo;Star&rdquo; l&agrave;  &ldquo;b&igrave;nh thng nh cm ba&rdquo;.</p>\n<div class=\"content\">\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Mt part-time kh&ocirc;ng b&oacute; buc thi gian</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bn  rn vi vic hc, nhiu teen kh&ocirc;ng th d&agrave;nh qu&aacute; nhiu thi gian cho  vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m. Vy th&igrave; &acirc;y thc s l&agrave; mt part-time hot cho teen trong  m&ugrave;a h&egrave; n&agrave;y. C&ocirc;ng vic Cng T&aacute;c Vi&ecirc;n (CTV) cho nhng t son b&aacute;o kh&ocirc;ng  tn qu&aacute; nhiu thi gian, ch cn teen c&oacute; kh nng vit l&aacute;ch kh&aacute; mt  ch&uacute;t, kh&ocirc;ng hn l&agrave; phi xut sc &acirc;u nh&eacute;.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">iu  quan trng ca mt CTV l&agrave; c&oacute; kh nng nm bt tin tc mt c&aacute;ch nhanh  ch&oacute;ng, tng hp tin v&agrave; a ra nhng sn phm &uacute;ng thi im. Ngo&agrave;i ra,  nu c&oacute; kh nng vit ph&oacute;ng s tt, c&aacute;c teen c&ograve;n c&oacute; iu kin th hin v&agrave;  ph&aacute;t huy kh nng ca m&igrave;nh na &oacute;! c bit, nhng sn phm b&agrave;i vit do  teen to ra kh&ocirc;ng g&ograve; b&oacute; v thi gian (tr nhng tin n&oacute;ng). C&aacute;c teen c&oacute;  th thoi m&aacute;i vit sau thi gian hc tp v&agrave; vui chi. So vi nhng  part-time kh&aacute;c th&igrave; tht thoi m&aacute;i v gi gic phi kh&ocirc;ng?</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2010/06/21/22610DSbao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br /><span style=\"font-style: italic;\">Bn cn c&oacute; kh nng vit l&aacute;ch kh&aacute; n khi mun cng t&aacute;c vit b&agrave;i nh&eacute;! (nh minh ha)</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Gi&uacute;p teen m rng mi quan h</span>&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi  tr th&agrave;nh CTV ch&iacute;nh thc ca bt k&igrave; t b&aacute;o n&agrave;o th&igrave; chc chn c&aacute;c teen  s c&oacute; dp m rng nhng mi quan h ca m&igrave;nh rt nhiu, bi &oacute; k nng  ngh nghip m&agrave; c&aacute;c CTV c &agrave;o to. Nht l&agrave; nhng mi quan h vi bn  b&egrave;  nhng ni kh&aacute;c, hay trng kh&aacute;c.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Thanh Tho</span>, 17 tui cho bit: <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">&ldquo;M&igrave;nh  l&agrave; CTV ca mt t b&aacute;o teen cng c my th&aacute;ng th&ocirc;i, nhng c&aacute;c anh ch  trong t&ograve;a son hng dn m&igrave;nh rt nhiu. M&igrave;nh c&oacute; nhng bui phng vn,  t&igrave;m hiu v th gii hc ng ca c&aacute;c bn teen. Qua &oacute;, m&igrave;nh c&ograve;n quen  th&ecirc;m c mt s thy c&ocirc; gi&aacute;o th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch &ldquo;c b&rdquo;, th&iacute;ch lm y&rdquo;.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay  qua nhng b&agrave;i phng vn, nhng bui chp h&igrave;nh, nhng b&agrave;i ph&oacute;ng s, c&aacute;c  teen c&ograve;n c&oacute; dp tr&ograve; chuyn vi c nhng nh&acirc;n vt ni ting. Nht l&agrave; khi  l&agrave;m CTV ca c&aacute;c t b&aacute;o gii tr&iacute; th&igrave; chuyn gp v&agrave; tr&ograve; chuyn vi c&aacute;c  &ldquo;Star&rdquo; l&agrave; &ldquo;b&igrave;nh thng nh cm ba&rdquo;. Ngo&agrave;i ra, c&aacute;c teen c&ograve;n c hng  dn c&aacute;ch giao tip khi bc ra x&atilde; hi. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt bc bt cn thit khi  i l&agrave;m. Tht tuyt vi phi kh&ocirc;ng?</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Lng thng hp dn</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh&aacute;c  hn c&aacute;c part-time kh&aacute;c, part-time n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; lng, thng t&iacute;nh theo  thi gian m&agrave; theo cht lng v&agrave; kh nng l&agrave;m vic.  c&oacute; nhng b&agrave;i b&aacute;o  hay, nhng teen CTV cn l&agrave; nhng ngi cn mn. C&oacute; nhiu b&agrave;i vit m&agrave;   thc hin c th&igrave; kh&aacute; vt v &ograve;i hi phi c&oacute; c&aacute;i t&acirc;m vi ngh. Nhng s  vt v y cng s nhanh ch&oacute;ng c n b&ugrave; bi lng thng cho nhng  b&agrave;i b&aacute;o xut sc v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng hp dn.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mt  s t&ograve;a son c&ograve;n tr nhun b&uacute;t theo cht lng b&agrave;i vit. B&agrave;i vit c&agrave;ng  n&oacute;ng, c&agrave;ng c quan t&acirc;m th&igrave; nhun b&uacute;t c&agrave;ng cao (ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c do c  thng th&ecirc;m n&ecirc;n cao). Ngo&agrave;i ra, khi c&oacute; nhiu b&agrave;i b&aacute;o xut sc, c&aacute;c teen  c&ograve;n c&oacute; c hi th sc vi nhng vai tr&ograve; v&agrave; v tr&iacute; cao hn trong t&ograve;a son  b&aacute;o na y.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh cu bn t&ecirc;n <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Thanh Hi,</span> 17 tui, ch sau 3 th&aacute;ng chm ch mit m&agrave;i vi c&ocirc;ng vic ca mt cng  t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n, cu &atilde; d&agrave;nh dm  tin  t t chc mt c&aacute;i sinh nht cc n  v&agrave; &aacute;ng nh c&ugrave;ng bn b&egrave;. Ai cng trm tr khi cu c&ocirc;ng t 17 tui kh&ocirc;ng  xin gia &igrave;nh 1 ng khi t chc bui sinh nht n&agrave;y.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phn  thng ln nht ca mt nh&agrave; b&aacute;o, hay 1 CTV gii kh&ocirc;ng ch l&agrave; s tin m&agrave;  teen kim c c&ograve;n l&agrave; danh ting ca teen trong ngh, v&agrave; nhng c hi  th sc ngh nghip mi.  la tui i hc m&agrave; c&oacute; iu kin  ph&aacute;t trin  ngh nghip v&agrave; nh hng cho tng lai th&igrave; tht tuyt vi nh?</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">R&egrave;n luyn t&iacute;nh c&aacute;ch</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khong  thi gian mi tr th&agrave;nh CTV, c&aacute;c teen chc chn s phi tht cn mn v&agrave;  chm ch, &ograve;i hi c&aacute;i t&acirc;m. Tt c nhng th&ocirc;ng tin  vit b&agrave;i u t  m&igrave;nh i t&igrave;m hiu, chp h&igrave;nh, vit b&agrave;i, l&agrave;m sao gi i cho kp  b&agrave;i b&aacute;o  c&ograve;n n&oacute;ng. Th nhng nhng b&agrave;i vit ban u ca c&aacute;c teen thng vp phi  nhiu li, n&ecirc;n c&oacute; khi teen vit nhng kh&ocirc;ng l&ecirc;n trang, l&ecirc;n b&agrave;i. c  bit, nhng th&ocirc;ng tin n&oacute;ng th&igrave; cn c b&iacute;-mt ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n. N&oacute; cng gi&uacute;p  teen tp t&iacute;nh ki&ecirc;n tr&igrave; v&agrave; kh nng gi b&iacute; mt cc tt.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Tho Anh</span> (CTV ca mt t b&aacute;o online) cho bit: <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">&ldquo;C&ocirc;ng  vic CTV b&aacute;o ch&iacute; gi&uacute;p m&igrave;nh cn thn hn. C&oacute; th n&oacute;i l&agrave;&hellip; cn thn n  tng vn, tng ch. Nh khi m&igrave;nh vit mt b&agrave;i ph&oacute;ng s chng hn. Nu  m&igrave;nh vit sai, d&ugrave; ch 1 c&acirc;u t, cng c&oacute; th khin ngi c hiu sai &yacute;  ngi vit, n&ecirc;n tt c m&igrave;nh u trau chut tng li, tng t&iacute; mt&rdquo;.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ki&ecirc;n  tr&igrave;, nhn ni, chm ch, phn ng t&igrave;nh hung nhanh, gi b&iacute; mt tt l&agrave;  nhng t&iacute;nh c&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh m&agrave; part-time n&agrave;y s em li cho c&aacute;c bn y. Va  kim c tin ti&ecirc;u vt, va to c cho ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh nhng c hi ngh  nghip, li r&egrave;n luyn c t&iacute;nh c&aacute;ch ca bn th&acirc;n th&igrave; tht &yacute; ngha phi  kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o? Vy c&aacute;c teen nh&agrave; m&igrave;nh c&ograve;n ch g&igrave; na m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th sc vi  part-time n&agrave;y nh?</div>\n</div>','2011-04-27 11:01:43','admin@jobbid.vn',830,1),(33,'luong-part-time-tang-nguoi-lam-them-van-chat-vat-','Lng part-time tng, ngi lm thm vn cht vt ','http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/95/7d/gia-su.jpg','thng tin u thu - tim viec ban thoi gian - Th lao cho nhng cng vic bn thi gian u  tng so vi trc nhng vn khng thm vo u so vi s leo thang ca gi sinh hot khin ngi lm thm phi vt v xoay s.','<h4 class=\"Lead\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\">Th&ugrave; lao cho nhng c&ocirc;ng vic b&aacute;n thi gian u &atilde; tng  so vi trc nhng vn kh&ocirc;ng thm v&agrave;o &acirc;u so vi s leo thang ca gi&aacute;  sinh hot khin ngi l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m phi vt v xoay s.</span><br /><a class=\"Lead\" href=\"http://vnexpress.net/gl/kinh-doanh/2011/04/gia-ca-tang-cao-quan-an-binh-dan-tim-ke-giu-khach/\"></a></h4>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Mi tun, Hng Ngc (sinh vi&ecirc;n H Giao th&ocirc;ng vn ti)  i dy th&ecirc;m 3 bui cho mt hc sinh tiu hc nh&agrave;  ng Th&aacute;i Thnh (H&agrave;  Ni). Vi th&ugrave; lao 60.000 ng mt bui, mt th&aacute;ng, Ngc c nhn khong  hn 700.000 ng. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, theo c&ocirc;, s tin n&agrave;y vn kh&ocirc;ng   trang  tri chi ph&iacute; sinh hot ng&agrave;y mt t .</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngc t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n, mt th&aacute;ng, c&oacute; 700.000 ng tin lng  dy th&ecirc;m, cng th&ecirc;m s tin 800.000 ng b m chu cp, th&igrave; va xon cho  c&aacute;c sinh hot ph&iacute; h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y. Chi ph&iacute; c nh mi th&aacute;ng c&ocirc; sinh vi&ecirc;n n&agrave;y  phi d&ugrave;ng l&agrave; 600.000 ng tin thu&ecirc; nh&agrave;, 80.000 ng tin nc, t  120.000 ng n 150.000 ng tin in. C&ograve;n li khong 700.000 ng  Ngc d&ugrave;ng trong vic n ung, i li.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C&ocirc; sinh vi&ecirc;n n&agrave;y cho hay b&igrave;nh thng m&ugrave;ng 10 h&agrave;ng  th&aacute;ng b&agrave; ch mi n thu tin nh&agrave;, nhng nu th&aacute;ng n&agrave;o b thu sm hn  th&igrave; chc chn phi vay mn  chi ti&ecirc;u na th&aacute;ng cui. \"V&igrave; thng th&igrave;  15 h&agrave;ng th&aacute;ng, ph huynh hc sinh mi tr tin dy na th&aacute;ng u\", Ngc  k. C&ocirc; cng th&ocirc;ng tin, trc kia, thng th&igrave; cui th&aacute;ng mi lnh lng  dy th&ecirc;m t ph huynh. Nhng hin ti, cuc sng kh&oacute; khn, t&uacute;i lu&ocirc;n  trong t&igrave;nh trng \"vi&ecirc;m m&agrave;ng\", n&ecirc;n  xut ph huynh hc sinh na th&aacute;ng  cho lnh tin mt ln.</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" width=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"http://vnexpress.net/Files/Subject/3b/a2/95/7d/gia-su.jpg\" alt=\"Gi&aacute; c tng cao, nhiu c&ocirc;ng vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m cng c&acirc;n nhc tng mc lng, thng, th&ugrave; lao. nh minh ha: Tu Minh\" width=\"350\" height=\"539\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"Image\">Gi&aacute; c tng cao, nhiu c&ocirc;ng vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m cng c&acirc;n nhc tng mc lng, thng, th&ugrave; lao. nh minh ha: <em>Tu Minh</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ghi nhn ca <em>VnExpress.net</em>, t ng&agrave;y gi&aacute; tng,  nhng c&ocirc;ng vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m d&agrave;nh cho sinh vi&ecirc;n nh gia s, tip th hay  nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n ph&aacute;t t ri, sn phm khuyn mi&hellip; cng c&oacute; mc th&ugrave; lao cao hn.  Hin ti, lng gia s dy c&aacute;c lp tiu hc cng tng khong  10.000-15.000 ng, l&ecirc;n 50.000-60.000 ng mt ca so vi trc. Tin  c&ocirc;ng ph&aacute;t t ri v&agrave; sn phm khuyn mi nh sa, giy n,&hellip; ti c&aacute;c si&ecirc;u  th, trng hc cng dao ng 100.000-150.000 ng mt ca, t&ugrave;y sn phm.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, s tin n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng thm g&igrave; so vi mc tng  ca tt c c&aacute;c h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, dch v thit yu. Hn na nm trc, lng dy  th&ecirc;m ch 50.000 ng mt ca. Vi 50.000 ng n&agrave;y c&oacute; th mua c gn 6  kg go b&igrave;nh thng loi 9.000 ng mt kg. Nhng hin ti, th&ugrave; lao gia  s tng th&ecirc;m 10.000 ng, th&igrave; 6 kg go cng kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n gi&aacute; 9.000 ng mt  kg na m&agrave; tng l&ecirc;n 11.000-12.000 ng.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ho&agrave;ng Hi, sinh vi&ecirc;n H Quc gia H&agrave; Ni ang l&agrave;m nh&acirc;n  vi&ecirc;n phc v b&agrave;n mt qu&aacute;n n tr&ecirc;n ng Kim M&atilde; cho hay, mi th&aacute;ng, lng  l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m ca cu cng c 2,3 triu ng. So vi c&aacute;ch &acirc;y na nm, mc  n&agrave;y &atilde; tng th&ecirc;m 300.000 ng. Song d&ugrave; vi s tin nhiu hn, vn phi  cht vt lm cu mi  tin trang tri cuc sng  tr ch kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute;  chuyn  d&agrave;nh c tin nh nm ngo&aacute;i.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Hi than th, tin nh&agrave; mi tng t 1 triu l&ecirc;n 1,2  triu ng mt th&aacute;ng. Nc 60.000 ng, in 4.000 ng mt s. T&iacute;nh ra  mi th&aacute;ng, khon tin d&agrave;nh cho thu&ecirc; nh&agrave;, in, nc cng ht khong 1,6  triu ng. Th&ecirc;m chi ph&iacute; xng xe, n ung v&agrave; in thoi ng&oacute;t ngh&eacute;t  600.000 ng na l&agrave; gn nh cn s tin lng l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m. \"Nm ngo&aacute;i,  lng ch 2 triu nhng mi th&aacute;ng m&igrave;nh vn tit kim c khong v&agrave;i  trm ngh&igrave;n ng, v&igrave; gi&aacute; c c&aacute;i g&igrave; cng d chu ch kh&ocirc;ng n mc phi  nga c k&ecirc;u tri nh nm nay\", Hi n&oacute;i.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><strong><span style=\"color: #4f4f4f;\">Trong xu th gi&aacute; c h&agrave;ng  h&oacute;a, dch v leo thang, hu ht c&aacute;c im gii thiu vic l&agrave;m part-time  cng chn c&aacute;ch iu chnh mc lng, thay v&igrave; bt mi hay ct gim nh&acirc;n  lc.</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Anh Thnh, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n m&ocirc;i gii mt trung t&acirc;m gia s ti  ph Mai Dch (H&agrave; Ni) cho bit, t khi gi&aacute; c&aacute;c mt h&agrave;ng thit lp mt  mt bng mi, phn ln c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m gia s cng phi iu chnh tng  th&ugrave; lao cho ngi dy. Mc tng ph bin t 10.000 ng n 30.000 ng  mt ca, t&ugrave;y  tui hc sinh. C&agrave;ng c&aacute;c lp tiu hc mc tng c&agrave;ng thp,  c&ograve;n nhng bc kh&aacute;c nh trung hc c s hay trung hc ph th&ocirc;ng, th&igrave; tng  nhiu hn.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Anh B&igrave;nh l&agrave;m  trung t&acirc;m gia s tr&ecirc;n ph Trn Quc  Ho&agrave;n cng cho hay, trung t&acirc;m n&agrave;y mi  xut vi c&aacute;c ph huynh c&oacute; nhu  cu tuyn gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n dy th&ecirc;m mc th&ugrave; lao mi. So vi mc c, ph&iacute; hc mi  ca tng th&ecirc;m khong 10.000-20.000 ng.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Anh B&igrave;nh k trc &oacute;, rt nhiu ngi sau khi n tham  kho th&ugrave; lao dy th&ecirc;m u quay i. Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n gi&aacute; qu&aacute; thp so vi mt  bng thu nhp chung b&acirc;y gi. \"C&oacute; bn c&ograve;n n&oacute;i thng vi t&ocirc;i, lng tr  50.000 ng mt ca 2 ting ri dy hc sinh cp hai. Mt tun dy hai  bui, th&aacute;ng dy  th&igrave; c 400.000 ng, chng  tin nh&agrave;, th&igrave; l&agrave;m sao  tr c  th &ocirc;\", anh B&igrave;nh k.</p>\n<p class=\"Normal\"><strong>Tu Minh </strong>( ngun vnexpress.net)</p>','2011-05-03 19:40:16','admin@jobbid.vn',318,1),(34,'doi-thoai-part-time-mua-he-lam-them','i thoi part-time: Ma h lm thm','http://www.svvn.vn/upload/20100521/Nha%20thiet%20ke%20tre%20Ha%20%20Duy.jpg','thng tin u thu - cong viec part time - Vi cc bn sinh vin, mt ma h th v s l: i du lch, v thm gia nh, tham gia tnh nguyn, i hc thm chng ta c rt nhiu la chn','<p><span class=\"tomtat\"><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" title=\"c&ocirc;ng vic part time\" src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/Controls/ThumbnailSizeOrigin.aspx?swidth=200&amp;sheight=0&amp;imageurl=upload/20100521/1.jpg\" alt=\"cong viec part time\" width=\"200\" height=\"110\" /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong>(SVVN) Vi c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n, mt m&ugrave;a h&egrave; th&uacute; v s  l&agrave;: i du lch, v thm gia &igrave;nh, tham gia t&igrave;nh nguyn, i hc th&ecirc;m&hellip;  ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; rt nhiu la chn! Nhng c&oacute; mt m&ugrave;a h&egrave; va th&uacute; v, li b  &iacute;ch: M&ugrave;a h&egrave; part &ndash; time! Bui i thoi Part-Time ca b&aacute;o Sinh Vi&ecirc;n Vit  Nam &atilde; c t chc v&agrave;o 18-20h, th 4 (19/5/2010) ti tng 7 To&agrave; son  b&aacute;o SVVN, s 5 Ho&agrave; M&atilde;, HN cng kh&ocirc;ng nm ngo&agrave;i ch  n&agrave;y </strong></span