  t, Ebay, adnet&hellip;). C&ocirc; cho bit, nhng m&ugrave;a h&egrave;  li l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m &atilde; gi&uacute;p c&ocirc;  trng th&agrave;nh hn rt nhiu. Ngo&agrave;i chia s kinh nghim bn th&acirc;n, Hng  cho bit c&ocirc; c&oacute; nhng c hi l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m ti Ch in t cho c&aacute;c bn sinh  vi&ecirc;n.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>V&agrave; cui c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; c&ocirc; g&aacute;i c bit n nh mt PG ni ting ca gii sinh vi&ecirc;n, <strong>Nguyn Th Hng</strong> - 1 trong 25 chuy&ecirc;n vi&ecirc;n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng cao cp ca Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng Techcombank.  Sut nhng nm H c&ocirc; kh&ocirc;ng phi xin tin gia &igrave;nh m&agrave; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n t lp.  Mi tt nghip ra trng c&ocirc; c nhn v&agrave;o l&agrave;m vic ti ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng  Techcombank. Nhng nhng tri nghim Part &ndash; time c&ograve;n mang n cho c&ocirc;  nhiu hn th.</p>\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra chng tr&igrave;nh c&ograve;n c&oacute; s tham gia &ocirc;ng o ca c&aacute;c bn sinh vi&ecirc;n n t c&aacute;c trng H, C trong c nc.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/upload/20100521/Cac%20ban%20sv%20giao%20luu%20voi%20khach%20moi%20trong%20buoi%20doi%20thoai.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Cac ban sv giao luu voi khach moi trong buoi doi thoai.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"289\" /> <br /> <em>C&aacute;c bn SV giao lu vi kh&aacute;ch mi ca chng tr&igrave;nh</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Chng tr&igrave;nh l&agrave; nhng tri nghim, nhng c&acirc;u chuyn, nhng chia s kinh nghim v c&ocirc;ng vic&nbsp;part-time ca c&aacute;c v kh&aacute;ch mi.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/upload/20100521/4.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"4.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"193\" /> <img src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/upload/20100521/2.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"2.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"283\" /> <img src=\"http://www.svvn.vn/upload/20100521/3.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"3.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"202\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>SVVN </strong>(ngun www.svvn.vn)</p>','2011-05-07 11:55:36','admin@jobbid.vn',514,1),(35,'chan-trong-chan-ngoai-kiem-tien-thoi-bao-gia','Chn trong chn ngoi kim tin thi bo gi','http://www.xaluan.com/images/news/Image/2011/05/10/1305016530.img.jpg','tim viec ban thoi gian - cong viec part time - Thu nhp t cng vic chnh ch c 2-3 triu ng mi thng gia thi bui vt gi leo thang, nhiu ngi phi cng ng thm mt vi ngh tay tri, lm bn thi gian  trang tri chi tiu ang khng ngng tng ln','<p class=\"Leadb\">Thu nhp t c&ocirc;ng vic ch&iacute;nh ch c&oacute; 2-3 triu ng mi  th&aacute;ng gia thi bui vt gi&aacute; leo thang, nhiu ngi phi c&aacute;ng &aacute;ng th&ecirc;m  mt v&agrave;i ngh tay tr&aacute;i, l&agrave;m b&aacute;n thi gian  trang tri chi ti&ecirc;u ang  kh&ocirc;ng ngng tng l&ecirc;n.</p>\n<p><br /> <img src=\"http://www.xaluan.com/images/news/Image/2011/05/10/1305016530.img.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Gi&aacute; c leo thang l&agrave; mt trong nhng nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khin cho nhiu ngi n lc chy s&ocirc; l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m  &aacute;nh vt vi cn b&atilde;o gi&aacute;. nh: V L&ecirc;.\" width=\"480\" height=\"342\" /><br /><em>Gi&aacute;  c leo thang l&agrave; mt trong nhng nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khin cho nhiu ngi n  lc chy s&ocirc; l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m  &aacute;nh vt vi cn b&atilde;o gi&aacute;. nh: V L&ecirc;.</em></p>\n<p>Vi nhng ngi l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng n lng, lo  vic h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh  vn ph&ograve;ng, lng ba cc ba ng gia l&uacute;c m rau, k&yacute;  go thi nhau tng  gi&aacute;, th&igrave; vic tht lng buc bng c&agrave;ng tr n&ecirc;n nght  th.</p>\n<p>C mi ngay sau ca trc, anh Ng&ocirc; Trng Ngha (TP HCM)  li tt t n  nh&agrave; mt tim kim  nhn kim ct m&oacute;ng tay v nh&agrave; m&agrave;i  gia. L&agrave; nh&acirc;n  vi&ecirc;n bo v, ng lng eo hp 2,5 triu ng mi th&aacute;ng,  anh Ngha &atilde;  i ph&oacute; vi t&igrave;nh trng gi&aacute; c tng cao t u nm n nay  bng c&aacute;ch t&igrave;m  th&ecirc;m vic l&agrave;m ti nh&agrave;.</p>\n<p>Chia s vi <em>B&aacute;o</em>, anh Ngha tri  l&ograve;ng: \"M&agrave;i c mt chic  kim ct m&oacute;ng tay ngo&agrave;i gi tin c&ocirc;ng l&agrave; 3.000  ng. Ngo&agrave;i ca trc,  trung b&igrave;nh mt ng&agrave;y t&ocirc;i m&agrave;i c 50-100 chic, k  cng c&oacute; th&ecirc;m  150.000-300.000 ng, mt th&aacute;ng &iacute;t nht cng kim th&ecirc;m c  dm ba  triu ng nu mi vic thun li\".</p>\n<p>Theo anh Ngha, vic l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m n&agrave;y cng c&oacute; hn ch l&agrave;  kh&ocirc;ng phi l&uacute;c  n&agrave;o cng c&oacute; kim cho m&igrave;nh m&agrave;i, m&agrave; phi t&ugrave;y thuc v&agrave;o c&ocirc;ng  vic ca c&ocirc;ng  ty c&oacute; rnh ri kh&ocirc;ng. Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute;, sau khi m&agrave;i kim, hai  b&agrave;n tay  thng b y vt xc v&agrave; chai cng, rt kh&oacute; chu. \"Gia l&uacute;c mi  th  u thi nhau tng gi&aacute;, l&agrave;m mt c&ocirc;ng vic kh&ocirc;ng t&agrave;i n&agrave;o  sng n&ecirc;n  t&ocirc;i  phi c. V li, t&ocirc;i &atilde; quen dn vi ngh tay tr&aacute;i n&agrave;y\", anh Ngha  bc  bch.</p>\n<p>Trong khi &oacute;, l&agrave; d&acirc;n ngoi tnh t min Trung v&agrave;o S&agrave;i  G&ograve;n lp  nghip, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n k to&aacute;n Trn Th Tho c&oacute; n hai ngh tay  tr&aacute;i. H&agrave;ng  ng&agrave;y, sau 8 gi ng h &aacute;nh vt vi nhng con s, ch bt  u v&agrave;o ca  &ecirc;m  mt trung t&acirc;m ngoi ng ti qun 10 vi c&ocirc;ng vic nh&acirc;n  vi&ecirc;n ghi  danh. Ng&agrave;y cui tun, n k to&aacute;n n&agrave;y c&ograve;n i b mi vi  ch B&agrave;  Chiu.  Thnh thong c&oacute; li  ngh khai b&aacute;o thu dch v, ch kh&ocirc;ng  qun ngi  thc khuya b&ecirc;n ng s s&aacute;ch ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng  ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng  vic b&aacute;n  thi gian.</p>\n<p>Ch Tho t&acirc;m s: \"Lng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n k to&aacute;n nh t&ocirc;i ch 3  triu ng  mi th&aacute;ng, vy m&agrave; c&ograve;n phi  nh&agrave; thu&ecirc;, lo bao nhi&ecirc;u th chi  ti&ecirc;u cm &aacute;o  go tin, t&iacute;ch ly cho tng lai sau n&agrave;y v&agrave; gi v qu&ecirc; &iacute;t  ng cho b  m vi c&aacute;c em. Nu kh&ocirc;ng chp git l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m  th vic th&igrave;  kh&ocirc;ng th  tr c  S&agrave;i G&ograve;n\".</p>\n<p>Vi c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n, cuc sng thi b&atilde;o gi&aacute; c&agrave;ng bp b&ecirc;nh  gp bi. V  chng ch L&acirc;m Th Th&uacute;y Liu v&agrave; anh La Th&agrave;nh Nam l&agrave;m vic   khu c&ocirc;ng  nghip T&acirc;n B&igrave;nh thu nhp ch c&oacute; 4 triu ng mi th&aacute;ng. Do gi&aacute;  c tng  cao, i sng kh&oacute; khn, anh ch cng ph&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng mi ngi t&igrave;m  th&ecirc;m mt  vic l&agrave;m ngo&agrave;i gi.</p>\n<p>Nh ngi ng hng  S&oacute;c Trng gii thiu, ch Liu  t&igrave;m c ch&acirc;n  ra b&aacute;t  mt qu&aacute;n n gn nh&agrave; tr. Ht gi l&agrave;m, ch chy  vi n qu&aacute;n  cm  ph vic, mi bui l&agrave;m th&ecirc;m n&agrave;y ch c tr 30.000  ng v&agrave; mt  sut n. C&ograve;n anh Nam nhn vic th b&oacute;ng &egrave;n cho mt h&atilde;ng sn  xut   in. C&ocirc;ng vic ca anh sau khi tan ca l&agrave; cm c&acirc;y v&iacute;t th in   kim  tra b&oacute;ng &egrave;n, mi b&oacute;ng th xong anh c tr 100 ng. \"Trung  b&igrave;nh mt  gi ng h t&ocirc;i th c 100 b&oacute;ng &egrave;n, cng kim th&ecirc;m c  10.000 ng  mi gi ng h. V chng c&ugrave;ng c gng n&ecirc;n 2 th&aacute;ng nay ch&uacute;ng  t&ocirc;i mi  tho&aacute;t khi cnh nm np lo thiu ht tin v&agrave;o cui th&aacute;ng\", anh  Nam m  l&ograve;ng.</p>\n<p>Trong t&igrave;nh cnh bp b&ecirc;nh hn c ngi c&oacute; bng cp hoc  t&igrave;m c mt  c&ocirc;ng vic n nh, anh L&ecirc; Hin Lng qu&ecirc; Ph&uacute; Th v&agrave;o S&agrave;i  G&ograve;n lp nghip  ch mi hc ht lp 12 v&agrave; l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng vic bng b&ecirc; phc v  ti mt qu&aacute;n  n ti qun 1. Anh Lng cho bit: \"T&ocirc;i &atilde; n lc l&agrave;m n 2  ca mt ng&agrave;y  n&ecirc;n ky c&oacute;p mi th&aacute;ng c hn 4 triu ng. Nh c&oacute; ch&uacute;t  tin tu&yacute;p  (tin boa), t&ocirc;i mi c&aacute;ng &aacute;ng c c&aacute;c khon chi ti&ecirc;u: tin  nh&agrave;, in,  nc, cm... c thi nhau i l&ecirc;n m&agrave; vn gi v qu&ecirc; cho m v&agrave;  em trai\".</p>\n<p>Anh nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n phc v k th&ecirc;m, vi t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh hin nay,  nu ch l&agrave;m  mt ca th&igrave; tng thu nhp ca anh ch  sng n ng&agrave;y 20  mi th&aacute;ng l&agrave;  c&ugrave;ng. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; th, anh &atilde; n&agrave;i n ngi qun l&yacute; xem x&eacute;t cho  anh l&agrave;m 2  ca mt ng&agrave;y. \" ch t&ocirc;i c&oacute; nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n cng tranh th  thi gian l&agrave;m  th&ecirc;m. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, h c&ograve;n c&oacute; vic hc  m&agrave; hy vng, ch t&ocirc;i  th&igrave; chng  c&oacute; g&igrave; c. Nay mai vt gi&aacute; li leo thang na th&igrave; t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng  bit cuc  sng c&ograve;n kh&oacute; khn n nhng n&agrave;o\", anh Lng th vn than d&agrave;i</p>\n<p><br />Ngun c th&ecirc;m:  <a style=\"color: #003399;\" href=\"http://www.xaluan.com/modules.php?name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=263685#ixzz1LyUY7zbQ\">http://www.xaluan.com/modules.php?name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=263685#ixzz1LyUY7zbQ</a> <br /> <a style=\"color: #003399;\" href=\"http://www.xaluan.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xaluan.com/</a></p>','2011-05-11 01:14:59','admin@jobbid.vn',425,1),(36,'ra-mat-dich-vu-dang-tin-rao-vat-mien-phi-tren-jobbid.vn','Ra mt dch v ng tin rao vt min ph trn Jobbid.vn','http://www.jobbid.vn/upload/images/1300086520_BANNER_QUANG_CAO(200x120).jpg','Nu nh bn c nhu cu cn rao vt bt c g, cc bn c th s dng dch v mi ca chng ti.','<p><img style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; float: left;\" src=\"http://www.jobbid.vn/upload/images/1300086520_BANNER_QUANG_CAO(200x120).jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"120\" />Xin ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n ca <a href=\"../\">Jobbid.vn</a></p>\n<p>Nu nh bn c&oacute; nhu cu cn rao vt bt c g&igrave;, c&aacute;c bn c&oacute; th s dng dch v mi ca ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i.<br /> ng tin rao vt cho bn, vui l&ograve;ng click v&agrave;o n&uacute;t <a title=\"dang_tin_rao_vat\" href=\"http://www.jobbid.vn/raovat/dang_tin_rao_vat\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #